\v 40-41 Asher
\tc2 41,500
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 42-43 Napthali
\tc2 53,400
\p 
\v 44 Israel phung som le ni lamkaiho toh Mose le Aaron in akhumlut u pasal ho cheng hi abonchauva ama ama phung chilhah dungjui cheh a kikhumlut cheh ahiuve.
\v 45 Amaho chu ama ama insung duijui cheh a kikhumlut ahiuve - Israel te pasal kiti pou kum somni apat chunglam gal bolthei jouse hi abonchauva a insung dungjuiya kijihlut cheh ahiuve.
\v 46 Amaho chu agomma 603,550 ahiuve.
\v 47 Ahinlah hiche kisim khomna a hin Levi te vang apang pon ahi.
\v 48 Ajeh chu, Pathen'in Mose kom'ah hiti hin ana seiyin ahi,
\v 49 Min najihlut teng Levi te hi najihlut loubeh ding, Israel mite lah a nasim tha loubeh ding ahi.
\v 50 Kikhop khomna ponbuh le aki mangcha thil ho aboncha a Levi te mopohna napeh ding, nachena chan uva Ponbuh le amanchah chengse aboncha ama hon apoh uva, akimvella ngahmun sem toh thoa alhacha a pang ding ahiuve.
\v 51 Kikhop khomna ngahmun chon phat alhin teng, Levi chapa te chengin aphet lhah diu, hitia chu ngahmun nalhun tengu leh ama hon athah sondoh kit diu, amavang koi hileh phalna beiya kikhop khomna ponbuh ganailut behseh chan chu thi ding ahi.
\v 52 Phung jousen ama ama insung ponlap cheh utoh ngahmun akisem diu ahi.
\v 53 Israel pumpi chunga Pakai lunghan louna dinga Levi chapa ten vang kitepna ponbuh kimvella ngahmun akisem cheh uva avetsui diu ahi. Hitia chu hiche ponbuh ventupna chu Levi te mopohna hi ding ahi.
\v 54 Hiti chun Pathen'in Mose henga athupeh bang tah chun Israel chaten imajouse abol tauvin ahi.
\c 2
\s1 Israel te ngahmun kigontup dan
\p 
\v 1 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron chu thu hicheng ahin hilchahna aneitan ahi:
\v 2 “Israel ten ngahmun asem tengu leh, ama ama phung kai cheh a um ding ahiuve. Aphung phung leh ama ama insung micheng chu ama ama ponbuh noija khosa cheh ding ahiuve. Aphung aphunga kihomtohho chun angahmun cheh uchu kikhop khomna Houbuh pangli kiemvel a akisem dingu ahi, hinlah hichu kikahjep hi ding ahi.
\v 3-4 Kikhop khomna ponbuh niso lama ngahmun sem ding phungho chu Judah, Issachar leh Zebulun hidiu ahi. Anoia ho hi amin kikhum galsat ding jat, aphungmin uleh alamkai hou chu ahiuve.
\s1 Phungmin Lamkai Amijat
\p Judah Amminadab chapa Nahshon 74,600
\p 
\v 5-6 Issachar Zuar chapa Nethanel 54,400
\v 7-8 Zebulun Helon chapa Eliab 57,400
\v 9 Judah phung lamkaina noiya galsat mi ahung kikhom jat chu mihem 186,400 ahi. Israel ten ngahmun thah ajot a asemji tengu leh hiche phung thumho leh alamkai hou hi mapui a pang dingu ahi.
\v 10-11 Reuben, Simeon leh Gad chu kikhop khomna ponbuh lhanglam a ngahmun sem a pang ding phungho chu ahiuvin, aphungjem u noi cheh a um cheh ding ahiuve. Anoiya ho hi galsat dinga amin kikhum jat, aphungmin uleh alamkai hou chu ahiuve.
\s1 Phungmin Lamkai Amijat
\p Reuben Shedeur chapa Elizur 46,500
\p 
\v 11-12 Simeon Zurishaddai chapa Shelumiel 59,300
\p 
\v 14-15 Gad Deuel chapa Eliasaph 45,650
\v 16 Reuben phung lamkaina noija galsat thei aloi loiya kikhomdoh jat chu agom a mihem 151,450 ahi. Israel te ahon a achenna jouseuva hiche phung thum ho hi anina a pang dingu ahi.
\v 17 Chuleh houponbuh Levi ten aput uchu ngahmun lailung apat a hung kipudoh ding ahi. Phung jouse ngahmun ana kison bang cheh u sukeh louhel a ama ama phung jem noicheh a kitol diu ahi.
\v 18-19 Kikhop khomna ponbuh lhumlam a ngahmun sem ding phungho chu Ephraim, Manasseh leh Benjamin hidiu ahin, aphungjem u noi cheh a um cheh ding ahiuve. Anoiya ho hi amin kikhum galsat ding jat, aphungmin uleh alamkai hou chu ahiuve.
\s1 Phungmin Lamkai Amijat
\p Ephraim Ammihud chapa Elishama 40,500
\p 
\v 20-21 Manasseh Pedahzur chapa Gamaliel 32, 200
\v 22-23 Benjamin Gideoni chapa Abidan 35,400
\v 24 Ephriam phung lamkaina noija galsat thei aloi loiya kikhomdoh jat chu agom a mihem 108,100 ahi. Israel te ahon a achenna jouseuva hiche phung thum ho hi athumna a pang ding u ahi.
\v 25-26 Kikhop khomna ponbuh sahlama ngahmun semding phungho chu Dan, Asher leh Naphtali hidiu ahin, aphungjem u noi cheh a um cheh ding ahiuve. Anoiya ho hi amin kikhum galsat ding jat, aphungmin uleh alamkai hou chu ahiuve.
\s1 Phungmin Lamkai Amijat
\p Dan Ammishaddai chapa Ahiezer 62,700
\p 
\v 27-28 Asher Ocran chapa Pagiel 41,500
\v 29-30 Naphtali Enan chapa Ahira 53,400
\v 31 Dan phung lamkaina noija galsat thei aloi loiya kikhomdoh jat chu agom a mihem 157,600 ahi. Israel te ahon a achenna jouseuva aphungjem noi cheh uva hiche phung thum ho hi anukhahpen a pang dingu ahi.
\v 32 Agomlam tah in, aloi loiya um Israel te, a insung cheh uva kon kijihlut ho chu abonchauva gomsoh in mihem 603,550 alhing uve.
\v 33 Pakai thupeh bang chun Levi te vang chu amin u akisim tha tapon ahi.
\v 34 Hiti chun Pakaiyin Mose ana thupeh bang bang chun Israel ten ima jouse abolsohkei tauvin ahi. Pakai thupeh jui in ama ama insung leh phung jem noi cheh a chun akijotji un chuleh ngahmun jong asemji tauve.
\c 3
\s1 Levi te ho natong dinga lhendoh a aumnau
\p 
\v 1 Hiche hi Sinai molchunga Pakaiyin Mose ahoupi lai a ana kijihlut Aaron le Mose insung khanggui thu chu ahi.
\v 2 Aaron chapa te ho min chu Nadab (atah pen), Abihu, Elezear chule Ithamar ahiuve. \x + \xo 3:2 \xt Minbu 26:60\x*
\v 3 Hiche Aaron chapa te ho chengse hin thempu kintheng atoh theina ding uva thao anu uva chule atumbeh a kilhandoh ahiuve.
\v 4 Ahinlah Nadab le Abihu chu Pathen umpet a Sinai gamthip a maicham asemlai uva Pathen thupeh toh kikal a meikong dihlou ahal lhon jeh chun, ani lhonin hiche mun'a chun athilhon tan ahi. Chapa dang anei tahlou jeh in kintheng natong ding chu adalhah lhon Eleazer le Ithamar chutoh apa lhon Aaron chubou ahi tauve. \x + \xo 3:4 \xt Thempu Dan 10:1,2; Minbu 26:61\x*
\p 
\v 5 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseiyin,
\v 6 Levi phung le changho chu koukhom inlang, Aaron kintheng natohga kithopi dingin gapuiyin.
\v 7 Amaho chu Aaron leh mipi jenlea pang dingu, Houbuh leh akimvel a kintheng natonga pang ding ahiuve.
\v 8 Levi te jousen hiche ponbuh theng chu avettup dingu Israel mipite thalhenga ponbuh maicham a chu kintheng na atoh diu ahi.
\v 9 Levi chilhahho jouse chu Aaron leh achapa te vaihomna noiya umsah in. Amaho chu Israel mipi ho jouse lah a konna Aaron le achapa te jenle ding leh kithopi dinga kipedoh ah ahitauvin ahi.
\v 10 Aaron le achapa te ho jouse chun thempu kintheng na atoh ding uvin seipeh in. Koi hijongleh nganse chang louva muntheng ganailut ho chu thitei tei diu ahi.
\v 11 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose kom'a aseijin,
\v 12 “Ven, Levi te hi Israel japi lah a konna Israel chapa te apengmasa jouse thalhenga natong dinga kalhendoh ahitai. Levi te ho jouse keiya ahi.
\v 13 Ajeh chu chapa tahpen jouse keima a ahi. Egypt chapa te lah a apeng masa jouse kana suhgam nikho apatna keima Israel chapa tahpen jouse hi kei dia atumbeh a ka lhendohsa ahin, mihem a hihen gancha a hijongleh amaho jouse chu keiya ahiuve; Keima Pakai chu kahi.”
\s1 Levi te min kikhum
\p 
\v 14 Pakaiyin Sinai molchunga chun Mose hengah thu aseikit in, hiti hin ati,
\v 15 “Levi te chu ama ama insung leh phungkhai lhah in amin u jihlut cheh in. Pasal jouse lhakhat a pat chunglam se jihlut in.”
\p 
\v 16 Hichun Mose chun Pakai thupeh bang chun minho chu ajihlut tan ahi.
\v 17 Levi in chapa thum aneiyin, amaho chu Gershon, Kohath chule Merari ahiuve.
\p 
\v 18 Gershon a konna phungguiho chu ama chilhah te lah a kon a mini min, Libni leh Shimei a kiminsah ahiuve.
\v 19 Kohath akon a phungguiho chu ama chilhah a kon miliho- Amran, Izhar, Hebron chule Uzzeil a kiminsah ahiuve.
\v 20 Merari a konna phungguiho chu ama chilhah te lah a konna mini min, Mahli le Mushi a kiminsah ahiuve.
\p 
\v 21 Gershon chilhah te chu Libni le Shimei phunggui akon ahiuvin ahi.
\v 22 Gershon te phunggui a kon a Pasal kum khat a pat chunglam chu abonchauvin mi 7,500 aum uve.
\v 23 Amaho chu Houbuh akon a lhumlam lang chu angahmun kisahna ding uva kipedoh ahiuve.
\v 24 Gershonte phungho chunga lamkaiya ana pang chu Lael chapa Eliasaph ahi.
\v 25 Hiche phung teni chunga mopohna a um chu ahileh Houbuh avetsui diu, ponbuhtheng leh achunga kidal akhuna chengse ahin, maicham ponbuh lutna phunga kikhai pondal ahin,
\v 26 maicham ponbuh leh maicham phung kimvel a ki-dah pondal chengse ahin, akhaoho ahin, chuleh manchah a kimangcha ding jouse jaona ahiye.
\v 27 Kohath chilhah te chu Amram, Izhar, Hebron chule Uzziel phung a kon ahiuve.
\v 28 Gershonte phunggui a konna pasal kum khat apat chunglam chu abonchauvin mi 8,600 aum uvin, amaho chu muntheng ventup leh vettupna mopoh kipe ahiuvin,
\v 29 chuleh angahmun sahna ding uva Houbuh a konna lhanglam kipe ahiuve.
\v 30 Kohath phungho chunga lamkai a ana pang chu Uzzeil chapa Elizaphan ahi.
\v 31 Hiche phung li ho hin Pathen thingkhong, dokhang, thaomei khom, maicham phungho, Houbuh sunga kimang thil le lo chom chomho, asung dan pondal, chuleh amaho manchah dinga angaicha jouse chunga mopohna anei dingu ahi.
\v 32 Thempupa Aaron chapa Eleazer chu, Levi te ho jouse chunga vaihom pipu anahin, Houbuh sunga nakitong jouse vetup dinga deichom a mopohna kipe ahi
\v 33 Merari chilhah te chu Mushi le Mahli phunga kon ahiuve.
\v 34 Merari phunggui a konna pasal kum khat apat chunglam chu abonchauvin mi 6,200 aum uve.
\v 35 Amaho chu Houbuh akon a sahlam lang chu ngahmun akisahna ding uva kipedoh ahiuve. Merari phungho chunga lamkaiya ana pang chu Abihail chapa Zuriel ahi.
\v 36 Hiche phung teni hin Houbuh thingkol ho, ingolvaiho, akhumho, akhomdouho leh amaho man ding manchah ho jouse avettup diu ahi.
\v 37 Chuleh Houbuh kimvel a palkhomho leh athehho ahin, akikhainaho le khaoho jouse jong avettup dingu ahi.
\v 38 Maicham ponbuh mai lhang, solam niso lamkot lang sese chu Israel mipi ho thalhenga Houbuh munthenga natohna dinga mopohna nunungpen kipe, Mose le Aaron chapa te ponbuh kisahna dinga ana kikoitup a ahi. Koi hijeng jongleh Thempu le Levi te tilou Houbuh muntheng maicham lang hinnai lailut tapou chu tha jeng ding ahi.
\v 39 Mose le Aaron chun Pakai thupeh banga Levi te phunghoa kon'in pasal lhakhatna pat chunglam se chu asim lhonin ahileh mi 22,000 alhing uvin ahi.
\s1 Chapa peng masaho kilhatdohna
\p 
\v 40 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose jah a aseiyin, “Tun nangman Israel te chapa te apeng masa lhakhat lhingtasa apat chunglam jouse amin u jihlut in.
\v 41 Keima Pakai kahin, keima dinga Levi te chu Israel chapa tahpenho thalheng dinga kikoitup teitei ding ahi. Chuleh Israel te pumpi a gancha apengdoh masa ho khel dinga Levi te gancha ho chu kikoitup teitei ding ahi.
\v 42 Hiti chun Mose’n Pathen thupeh bangtah in Israel chapa te lah a atahpen ho chu asimtan ahi.
\v 43 Lhakhat a lhingsa leh achunglam chapa tahpenho chu 22,273 anahiuve.
\v 44 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose jah a aseiyin,
\v 45 “Levi te chu Israel chapa te lah a atahpen ho thalheng chun la in. Chuleh Israel te gancha apeng masa ho khel dinga Levi te gancha ho chu nalah ding ahi. Keima Pakai kahi, Levi te chu keiya ahi bouve.
\v 46 Levi te sang'in Israel chapa te apeng masa mi 273 in atamjo uvin ahi. Amaho lhatdoh a aum theina dingun,
\v 47 mikhat cheh a dinga Sumgoi a Shekel nga nalahkhom ding, hiche shekel chu muntheng laiya shekel ho toh agihdan nakibahsah ding, gerah somnia shekel khat dungjuiya nate ding ahi.
\v 48 Chapa pengmasa avahdoh ho lhatdohna dingin hiche sum chu Aaron le achapa te petan.”
\v 49 Hiti chun Levi te jat sanga hung tamjo Israel chapa tahpen ho lhatdoh a aumna ding uvin Mose’n in sum ho chu achom khom in ahi.
\v 50 Aman Israel chapa te lah a apengmasa ho thalheng chun sum pum 1,365 achomdoh in ahi. Hiche ho khat cheh hi muntheng a Shekel khat cheh toh agihdan kibang cheh ahiuve.
\v 51 Chuin Pathen'in thu apeh bang bang chun, akilhatdoh theina diuvin Mose in hiche sumho chu Aaron le achapa te apetan ahi.
\c 4
\s1 Kohath chapa te mopohna
\p 
\v 1 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron henga thu aseijin,
\v 2 Levi phung sunga konna Kohath insung le chilhah te chu amin hou na jihlut lhon ding ahi.
\v 3 Amaho lah a Houbuh sunglam maicham phunga natong thei dinga lhinna nei, kum somthum apat kum-somnga sungse ho chu abonchan jihlut lhonin.
\v 4 “Kohath hon Houbuh sunga anatoh dingu chu manchah thil athenga umho jouse vettupna chung chang chu ahi.
\v 5 Ama hon ngahmun achon ding teng ule Houbuh maicham sungnung pondal chu Aaron le achaten alahlhah diu kitepna thingkong khuna a anei dingu ahi.
\v 6 Chuteng hiche pondal chu kelcha vun a kisuhtah a atom dingu, hiche ho jouse chu pondum khat seh a apha chansoh dingu ahi. Che ho jouse kichai teng thingkhong chu aputna thinglhon toh asuhto dingu ahi.
\v 7 “Abankit a changlhah umpi jing ahiu melchihna a, hiche changlhah kikoina dokhang chunga pondum khat aphajal dingu ahi. Chuleh hiche pon kipha chunga chu lhengkongho, gimnamtui halna lhengho, khonho, twi lhitthengna, chuleh deisahtah a um jing jeng changlhah ho kikoi ding ahi.
\v 8 Ama hon hiche ho jouse chu ponsan a akhu diu, chutengleh kelchavun thengsel'a hiche ponsan chu kikhuson kit diu ahi. Chujou teng dokhang chu aputna ding thinglhon toh asuhto dingu ahi.
\v 9 Hiche banjom a chu ama hon pondum-eng a chu thaomei khum chu ahin khu a, thaomei semtohna, achoina kong, chuleh Olive thao kikoina khon jong chu akhu khum dingu ahi.
\v 10 Chule ama hon pondum a chu thaomei khom leh athil manchah ho jouse chu kelchavun thengsel'a atom khum uva chuleh hiche alom chu akiputna kolchahna chunga chu akoi dingu ahi.
\v 11 “Chuban leh pondum khat a sana gimnamtui maicham kilhaina chunga aphajal ding u, kelchavun thengsel'a hiche pon chu akhu diu ahi. Chuteng aputna ding thinglhon toh maicham chu asuhto dingu ahi.
\v 12 Maicham kin a dia manchah akigong tuplou laise chu pondum khat a tom ding, kelchavun thengsel khat a hiche pon chu kitomson ding, chuteng aputna kolchah a chu kikoi ding ahi.
\v 13 “Ama hon kilhaina dinga maicham phunga konna vutvam ho chu alodoh diu, chule ponsandup a maicham phung chu atom diu ahi.
\v 14 Maicham thilkeu ho jouse - meihalna kong, thihkhe, leilodohna longkhol, kisilna kongho, chuleh thilkoina ho jouse - pon chunga chu kikoi a, chuleh kelchavun thengsel chu hiche ho chunga chu kiphajal a kikhu ding ahi. Chuteng aputna thingjol chutoh asuhto dingu ahi.
\v 15 Aaron le achapa ten munthengho ahin, athenga um thil le lo ho ahin, ahintom jousoh teng ule ngahmun a konna kitol thei diu ahitai. Kohath chapa ten hiche hi lhunna ding mun chan ahin put diu ahi. Ahivanga thil theng ho chu asuhkhah louhel dingu ahi, achuti louleh thilo ding ahiuve. Hichengse hi Kohath chapa ten Houbuh a konna aput diu ho chu ahi.
\v 16 Aaron chapa Eleazer thempupa mopohna chu thaomei khom a thaotwi ho, gimnamtui ho, niseh a kitoh lhosoh thilto ho, kinu ding thaotwi ho avettup jing ding ahi. Houbuh pumpi leh asunga thil ijakai, muntheng le munthenga kimangcha jouse chu Eleazar vettupna noi a um ding ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron henga thu aseiyin,
\v 18 “Levi te phunga kon'in Kohath chilhah ho mahthah sah hih in.
\v 19 Muntheng pen thil ho ahin nailut teng athilouna diuva nangin hiche hi nabolpeh ding ahi. Aaron le achapa ten aki lhonlutpi jing diu chule amichang cheh a ato ding abol dingu chu napeh cheh ding ahi.
\v 20 Kohath chilhah te chu phat chomcha hijongleh muntheng laiya thil umho vedinga lutlouhel dingu ahiuve, achuti louleh thi tei tei diu ahi.”
\s1 Gerson chapa te mopohna
\p 
\v 21 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga ahin aseijin,
\v 22 Levi phung sunga konna Kohath insung le chilhah te chu aminhou na jihlut ding ahi.
\v 23 Amaho lah a Houbuh sunglam maicham phunga natong thei dinga lhinna nei, kum somthum apat kum-somnga sungse ho chu abonchan jihlut in.
\v 24 Gershon chilhah te chu japi natohna a leh thilgih dom ding ho chunga mopo ding ahiuve.
\v 25 Ama hon Houbuh pondal ho jouse apoh diu, Houbuh jong aki tomna pon puma, kelcha vuntheng sel a akitomna pum a, chuleh Houbuh lutna kotphunga pondal toh ahin pohtha diu ahi.
\v 26 Houbuh polama ahin amalam ahin Houbuh leh maicham phung vel'a pondal ho jouse jong, khaoho ahin, chuleh amaho natoh toh kisaiya amanchah hou jouse ahi. Hiche ho jouse chunga hi Gershon chilhah ten avettup diuva mopohna chang ahiuve
\v 27 Aaron le achapa te mopohna Gershon ten amopohna hou jouse, thil dop le ding hihen, natohna dang dang tohna ding hijongleh Aaron leh achapa ten akomu peh jing diu ahi. Gershon chilhah ten thilgih putna dinga jong ngansena apeh dingu ahi.
\v 28 Hichengse hi Gershon chilhah ten Houbuh sunga atoh diu kipe chu ahin, Ama ho hi Aaron thempupa chapa Ithamar vetsuina noiya um diu ahi.
\s1 Merari chapa te toh ding
\p 
\v 29 Levi phung sunga konna Kohath insung le chilhah te chu amin hou na jihlut ding ahi.
\v 30 Amaho chapa te lah a Houbuh sunglam maicham phunga natong thei dinga lhinna nei, kum somthum apat kum-somnga sungse ho chu abonchan jihlut in.
\v 31 Amaho kin chu Houbuh thil ho dop le ding ho ahi. Houbuh kolchah thingho, agol kamho, khom ho, chuleh ato theh ho adop diu ahi.
\v 32 chukit jongleh houbuh kimvel a pal khomho leh ato theh ho, akikhainaho le khaoho chuleh amaho natoh toh kisaiya amanchah ho jouseu jong avettup dingu ahi.
\v 33 Hichengse hi Merari chilhah ten Houbuh sunga atoh diu kipe chu ahin, amaho hi Aaron thempupa chapa Ithamar vetsuina noiya um diu ahi.
\s1 Levi insung kisim toh
\p 
\v 34 Hichun Mose, Aaron chule phung lamkai hon Kohath insung le chilhah te chu amin hou ana simun ana jihlut tauvin ahi.
\v 35 Hiche min kijihna chun Houbuh sunglam maicham phunga natong thei dinga lhinna nei, kum somthum apat kum-somnga chan ho chu abonchan jihlut cheh ahiuvin,
\v 36 chule amaho chu agom a mi 2,750 ahiuve.
\v 37 Hicheng hi Kohath chilhah ho lah a Houbuh a natong thei cheh dinga lhinna nei ho ahiuve. Pathen'in Mose athupeh bangin Mose le Aaron in jong ajihdoh lhonin ahi.
\p 
\v 38 Gershon chilhah te jong chu hitobang ma chun aphung achang dungjuijin aki sundoh cheh uvin ahi.
\v 39 Hiche min kijihna chun Houbuh sunglam maicham phunga natong thei dinga lhinna nei, kum somthum apat kum-somnga chan ho chu abonchan jihlut cheh ahiuvin,
\v 40 chule amaho agom a mi 2,630 ahiuve.
\v 41 Hicheng hi Gershon chilhah ho lah a Houbuh a natong thei cheh dinga lhinna neiho ahiuve. Pathen'in Mose athupeh bangin Mose le Aaron in jong ajihdoh lhonin ahi.
\p 
\v 42 Merari chilhah te jong chu hitobang ma chun aphung achang dungjuijin aki sundoh cheh uvin ahi.
\v 43 Hiche min kijihna chun Houbuh sunglam maicham phunga natong thei dinga lhinna nei, kum somthum apat kum-somnga chan ho chu abonchan jihlut cheh ahiuvin,
\v 44 chule amaho agom a mi 3,200 ahiuve.
\v 45 Hicheng hi Merari chilhah ho lah a Houbuh a natong thei cheh dinga lhinna neiho ahiuve. Pathen'in Mose athupeh bangin Mose le Aaron in jong ajihdoh lhonin ahi.
\p 
\v 46 Hichun Mose le Aaron chule Israel phung lamkai hon Levi te chu a insung le ama phung dungjui cheh in ana jihlut tauvin ahi.
\v 47 Kum somthum apat somnga chan Houbuh a natong thei leh thil ho po le theija pang thei ding ho chu
\v 48 agom a mi 8,580 ahi.
\v 49 Pathen'in Mose thu apeh dungjuiya aminhou jouse jihlut a aum phat chun, pasal khat cheh chu atoh ding dol cheh uleh apoh ding dol cheh u akipe cheh tauvin ahi.
\p Hiti chun Pathen'in Mose thu apeh bangtah in min kijihlutna natoh chu akichai tai.
\c 5
\s1 Israel ngahmun a thenna
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin thu hichengse hi Mose hilchahna anei e:
\v 2 “Israel mipite lah a koi hijongleh tiphah nei, boina nei, ahilouleh mithilong suhkhah jeh a chonna dan dungjuiya athenglou aum'a ahileh, ngahmun chu adalhah sahna ding uvin thu pen.
\v 3 Hiche thupeh hi numei leh pasal chunga umgel ding ahi. Ngahmun a amaho lah a cheng kahin, asuhboh louna dingun amaho chu koidoh un.”
\v 4 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bang chun Israel mipi ten hitobang ho chu ngahmun a kon'in atoldoh tauve.
\v 5 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseiyin, \x + \xo 5:5 \xt Thempu Dan 6:1-7\x*
\v 6 Anoija hilchahna chengse hi Israel mipite pen: Pasal hihen, numei hihen, koi hijeng jongleh, midang chunga thil phalou bol a Pathen joulhep a chu themmo changa ahitai.
\v 7 Ama hon achonset nau aphondoh teitei diu chuleh athilbol khel cheng chu aboncha a aledit ding ahi. Hiche chungvum a asuhkhelna pa chu asuhkhelna jakhat lah a 20 abelap peh nalai ding ahi.
\v 8 Ahinlah aki suhkhelna pa chu athi tah a, asuhkhel ho ditna ding asopi a-u, a-nao aumtah louva ahile, peh dinga um jouse chu Pathen ding ahitan chuleh thempuho kipe ding ahiuve. Themmona neiho vang chun Pakai henga kilhaina dia kelngoinou ahin kai ding, chuteng suhthenga um diu, Pathen toh kicham diu ahi.
\v 9 Israel ten pumgo thilto ahin poh jouseu aboncha a ama chan ding ahi.
\v 10 Athenga kipehna a hung kitohho jouse aman asan chan chu, ama ama thempu cheh chun akikoi ding ahiye.
\s1 Jineina chunga kitahna hinkho venbitna
\p 
\v 11 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose kom'a aseiyin,
\v 12 “Israel mite chu hiche hilchahna ho hi pen. “Vetsahnan pasal khat ji chu achon chavai tan, chuleh ajipa a dingin kitah louvin aum tan
\v 13 chule pasal dang toh ajong tan, ahin ajipa ahin midang ahin koiman ahedoh tapon ahi. Koimacha ahetoh umlouva, ajonbol pettah a akimat lou jeng vanga, amanu chu ama le ama kisuboh a ahitai.
\v 14 Itiham khat a ajipa chun ajinu chu aginmo a athangthip a, amanu akisuhboh akisuhbohlou hettei ding agot leh,
\v 15 ajipa chun ajinu chu thempu anga ahin puilut ding ahi. Chuleh chang suhbongsa pucha ni chu amanu khel a ahinto ding ahi. Hiche chu Olive thao le gimnamtui toh nahal louding ahi, ajeh chu hiche kilhaina hin a in-neipi chu kisuboh aham, kisubohlou ham ti photchetna dinga thangtomna a kibol ahi.
\p 
\v 16 “Chuteng thempupan numeinu chu Pakai thutanna ang a adinsah ding ahiye.
\v 17 Thempu chun leikhonlen a twitheng themkhat asodoh a Houbuh mai leitol a konna leivui alahdoh chu asunkhum ding ahi.
\v 18 Thempu pan hiche numeinu chu Pathen henga ahin kilahsah teng, amanu sam chu alhaplhah peh ding chule akhut teni chu hettohsah kilhaina a chu akoipeh ding ahi - hichu inneipu ginmona chu atah alhem ahi hettheina dinga kibol ahi. Hiche teng thempu chu numeinu nunglam a ding, athemmo pen pen gaosap channa ding twikha umna leikhonlen chu ahin dop ding ahi.
\v 19 Hiche teng chule thempu pan numeinu kitepna noi a aumsah a, “Najipa thunoiya naum sunga pasal dang toh nana chonset khah louva, nana chon chatvai louva nana kisuhboh louleh, hiche gaosapna twikhatah hi nathoh jou ding himai tahen” tia asei ding ahi.
\v 20 Ahinlah na in-neipu adia kitah joulou jeh a nana chekhel khah tah a, pasal dang toh nana chonset a nana kisuhboh khah tah a ahileh,'
\v 21 “Thempu pan numeinu chu kitepna noi a aum sah ding, hitia hi asei ding ahi, ‘Pakaiyin chanei thei louva nakoi a, nanaobun panna anei louva , nathong apomsah teng mipi jousen Pakai sapsetna na chunga lhung ahitai ti hehen.
\v 22 Tuhin hiche sapsetna twihi nasunga lut henlang, nathong pomsah hen lang, naobu jong panna bei himai tahen.’ Chuleh numeinu chu, ‘Henge, hunglhung tahen’ atisah ding ahi.
\v 23 Chule Thempupa chun hiche sapsetna thucheng ho chu savun chunga ajihdoh a hiche twikha a chu a sop lhah ding ahi.
\v 24 Hiche sapsetna polut twikha chu numeinu adonsah ding ahi. Itiham khat a hiche numei chu themmo chang ahikhah leh twi chun amanu oisung aphah teng, hiche chun khajenjun a athohlelsah ding ahi.
\v 25 Thempu pan hiche thangtom kilhaina chu numeinu khutna kon a alahdoh a, Pakai masanga adopsang ding, chuleh maicham phunga achoi ding ahitai.
\v 26 Thempupa chun hiche changbong khutsip dim khat chu mangmo thilto dinga ahamdoh a maicham phunga ahalvam ding, twi chu numei adonsah teitei ding ahi.
\v 27 Hiche numeinu chu a jipa angsunga kitah joulouva ana kisuhboh khah tah leh, hiche sapsetna po twi chun numeinu chu khajenjun a athohlel sah ding ahi. Athong hung poh ding chule anaobu jong panna bei hi ding, chuteng chuleh amanu min chu amite lah a sapsetna hi ding ahitai.
\v 28 Ahinlah amanu chu ana then jinga kisuboh khalou ahileh, imacha tilou ding, naosen jong anei thei ding ahi.
\v 29 “Hiche hi ginmona thu suhlhapna dinga chonna dan ahi. Numei chu ajipa thuneina noiya aum sunga akisuhboh khah a ana chon chatvai khah tah a,
\v 30 ahilouleh pasal khat chun ajinu chu kitah joulou dinga ahin ginmo khah tah leh, ajipa chun ajinu chu Pakai angsunga apui ding, chuteng thempu chun hiche chonna dan jouse hi abol ding ahi.
\v 31 Hiche thua vang ajipa themmona itobang hijongleh ongthol ding, ajinu vang achonsetna dungjuiya themmo chang ding ahi.”
\c 6
\s1 Nazir te danho
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseyin,
\v 2 “Israel mite chu hiche hilchahna ho hi pen. Mipiho lah a koi hijongleh numei hihen pasal hijongleh atumbeh a Nazir te kitepna a kitem aum a, Pakaiya dia atumbeh a ama leh ama kipedoh aum leh,
\v 3 amaho chun khamnathei juho leh lengpithei twiho don angah dingu ahi. Hitobang miho chun lengpi theitwi ahilouleh adang dang khamnathei a kisem juthuh kilhahna ho chu amanlou dingu ahi. Lengpiga apat a twi kilhi thah jeng jong adonlou ding, lengpi theiga ahin lengpi theiga gopsaho jeng jong aneh uva adonlou dingu ahi. \x + \xo 6:3 \xt Lk 1:15\x*
\v 4 Amaho chu Nazir te kitepna kol sunga aum laise uva lengpigui a konna kisemdoh ho chu aneh diu le adondiu phal ahipoi - Lengpi thei ahoh le amu jeng jong anehlou dingu ahi.
\v 5 “Nazir te tia kitepna kol sunga aum sungse uva chu asam u jong ache louhel diu ahi. Akitep nau suh bulhit a aum phat sungse a chu asam u akihoisao dingu ahi.
\v 6 Chule hiche kitepna kol sunga aum sung sese uva hi thilong umna avel lah a che louding ahiuve.
\v 7 Hiche mithi long chu apenna mong mong pa hihen, anu hihen, asopipa ahilouleh asopinu hijongleh amaho chu kisuboh louding ahiuve, ajeh chu alu uva asam uchu Pathen a dinga kitum lhandoh ahinau lim a um ahi.
\v 8 Pakai kintheng natong dinga lhenchom a aum chan uva hiche kigahna ho hi ajui jing diu ahi.
\v 9 Itiham khat a ama angsunga mikhat chu alhuh a athi jeng tah a ahileh asam kithenso chu kisuboh ahitai. Nikho sagi kho ngai dingu, asam u akivotol dingu ahi. Chuteng amaho chu akisuhbohna uva konna athenga umkit a ahi tauve.
\v 10 Niget lhinni teng vakhu kopkhat ahilouleh in vapalnou ni Houbuh maicham lutna dontah a thempu kom'a ahin choi dingu ahi.
\v 11 Thempu chun vacha teni lah a khat chu chonset kilhaina a atodoh ding, khatpen chu pumgo maicham adia atodoh ding ahi. Hiti dol a chu thempu pan mithi tahsa suhkhah jeh a themmo channa chu asuhtheng ding ahitai. Ama hon akitep nau chu aphudet kit uva, asam u chu akihoisao kit diu ahitai.
\v 12 Amaho aboh a aum masang uva kitepna nikho ajo cheng uchu kisimlou a ahitai. Amaho chu athahbeh a Pakai angsung a Nazir ahinau chu alhumkei a dinga kilhandoh kit dingu chuleh ama cheh in themmo kilhaina thilto dinga kumkhat lhingsa kelngoi achal khat ahin kai ding ahi.
\v 13 “Hiche hi Nazir te chonna dan chu ahi. Nazir adia akilhe khen nau phat nunung lam teng, Houbuh kotphunga chu che diu \x + \xo 6:13 \xt Act 21:23,24\x*
\v 14 chule Pakai anga athilto hou alhantheng diu ahi. Hichu kumkhat lhingsa nolna beihel kelngoichal khat pumgo thilto a ding, kumkhat lhingsa nolna beihel kelngoi anu khat chonset kilhaina ding chuleh nolnabei kelngoi achal lhingset khat hichu chamna maicham ding,
\v 15 cholsolou changlhah pocha khat - hichu akilhengdoh changbong Olive thao toh kimehhel chule changlhah neocha cha a paset a kisem a olive thao kichapkhum- chuleh peh dinga umsa lhosoh thilto leh atwi a kilhaina thilto ho ahiuve.
\v 16 Hiche thilto ho hi Thempu in Pakai angsunga pehdohna anei ding ahi. Amasa penna chonset kilhaina thilto leh pumgo maicham thilto ahin,
\v 17 aban'a chamna maicham dinga kelngoichal lhingsel chu ahin, chuleh cholsolou changlhah pocha khat ahi. Peh dinga umsa lhosoh thilto leh atwi a kilhaina thilto ho jong chu Thempu in Pakai kom'a pehdohna anei ding ahi.
\v 18 “Chuteng Nazir te ho chun Houbuh lutna kotphunga chu asam u akivolhah diu ahi. Chamna maicham kilhaina noiya mei lah a chu ana kikatdohsa asam u chu akoilut diu ahi.
\v 19 Nazir hon asam u akivotol jouteng uleh, thempun amaho cheh dinga akihulminsa kelngoi chal dah chu alah ding, Pocha sunga um cholsolou changlhah leh changlhah neocha cha a paset a kisem chu alah ding ahi. Hichengse chu aman Nazirpa khut tenia akoi ding ahi.
\v 20 Thempun hiche ho chu adopsanga kilhanna thilpeh tumbeh Pakai anga abol ding ahi. Thempupa dinga atheng hung kitohdoh ho chu ahileh, atumbeh a hung kitoh a-omlhang leh thengtah a Pakai anga akitohdoh leh kidomsang amal jaona cheng chu hi ding ahi. Hiche kintheng hi ahung kichai teng Nazirpa chun lengpitwi adon thei ding ahitai.
\v 21 Hicheng hi kilhaina Pathen kom hinlhut dinga kitepna nei Nazir te chonna dan chu ahi. Hiche chungchon a kilhaina apehjou chan uva jong apeh thei u ahi. Chuleh amaho chu Nazir tia lhendoh chom a aum tengu leh khopho tah a hitia akitepna jouseu chu abol dingu ahi.
\s1 Thempu Phattheina
\p 
\v 22 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin,
\v 23 “Aaron le achaten Israel te mipi jouse chu atumbeh a phatthei aboh ding uvin seipeh in:
\p 
\v 24 Pathen'in phatthei naboh uhenlang naveng jing uhen.
\p 
\v 25 Pathen'in lhaisel in nave jing uhenlang nachunga lung lhaisel jing tahen.
\p 
\v 26 Pathen mitvet in lunglhaina changin chule chamna nape hen.
\m 
\v 27 Aaron le achapa ten keimin a Israel te phatthei aboh tengu leh keiman jong amaho chu phatthei kaboh ding ahi.
\c 7
\s1 Thenso dinga kitohdohho
\p 
\v 1 Mose chun Houbuh atundoh ni chun thao anun, atheng in atum koi tai. Aman thilkeo jouse jong thao anun, Houbuh sung manchahho, maicham phung leh athilkeo ho jong atheng in atum koitai.
\v 2 Chuin Israel te lamkai ho akilom a um miho min jihlut a pang phung lamkaiho- ahungun, ama ama thilto ahin polut cheh uvin ahi.
\v 3 Ama hon abonchauvin Sakol kangtalai len tahtah gup toh bongchal som le ni ahin kaiyun ahi. Sakol kangtalai khat chu lamkai ni a ahin, bongchal khat cheh chu lamkai khat cheh a ahi. Hiche ho cheng hi Pakaiya ding Houbuh mai a chun apeuvin ahi.
\v 4 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose kom'a seiyin,
\v 5 “Thilpeh ho chu sang'in, sakol kangtalai leh bongchal ho chu Houbuh pohlena a nanei ding ahi. Levi te chu atoh dungjui cheh un homkhen in.”
\v 6 Hiti chun Mose’n kangtalaiho leh bongchal ho chu Levi te apetan ahi.
\v 7 Mose’n kangtalai ni le bongchal li chu Gershon ten anatohna uva amanchah ding uvin apetan,
\v 8 chuleh kangtalai li le bongchal get chu Meraribten anatohna uva amanchah ding uvin apetai. Na kitong jouse aboncha a thempu Aaron chapa Ithamar vaihomna noiya um sohkei ahi.
\v 9 Ahinlah Houbuh a kimangcha thil theng ho chu alengkou uva apoh dingu ahijeh chun Kohat te vang chu kangtalai ho le bongchal ho imacha apepon ahi.
\v 10 Lamkaiho jousen jong kilhanthengna thilpeh ahin kichoi cheh uvin, kisuhtheng nikho chun maicham phunga akoi cheh tauve.
\v 11 Pakaiyin Mose kom'a aseiyin, “Maicham kithensona dingin lamkai khat in thilpeh khat cheh hintoh hen.”
\b
\p 
\v 12 Nikho masapen tah chu Nahson kiti Aminadab chapa Judah phung lamkai chun maicham a ahin pelut in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 13 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 14 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 15 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 16 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 17 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Amminadab chapa Nahson in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 18 Nikho ni lhinni in Zuar chapa Nethanel, Issachar phung lamkai pan, amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 19 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 20 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 21 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 22 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 23 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi.Hichengse hi Zuar chapa Nethanel in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 24 Anithum lhinnin Helon chapa Eliab, Zebulun te phung lamkai pan jong amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 25 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 26 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 27 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 28 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 29 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi.Hichengse hi Helon chapa Eliab in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 30 Nili lhinnin Sheduer chapa Elizur, Reuben phung lamkai pan jong amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 31 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 32 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 33 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 34 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 35 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Sheduer chapa Elizur in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 36 Ni-nga lhinna in Zurisaddai chapa Shelumiel, Simeon phung lamkai pan jong amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 37 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 38 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 39 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 40 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 41 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Zurishaddai chapa Shelumiel in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 42 Ni-gup lhinnin Deuel chapa Eliasaph, Gad phung lamkai pan jong amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 43 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 44 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 45 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 46 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 47 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi.. Hichengse hi Eliasaph chapa Deuel in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 48 Nisagi lhinna in Ammihud chapa Elishama, Ephraim te phung lamkai pan jong amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 49 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 50 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 51 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 52 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 53 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Ammihud chapa Elishama in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 54 Niget lhinna in Pedahzur Chapa Gamaliel, Manasseh te phung lamkai pan jong amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 55 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 56 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 57 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 58 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 59 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi.Hichengse hi Pedahzur chapa Gamaliel in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 60 Niko lhinna in Gideoni chapa Abidan, Benjamin phunga lamkai pan amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 61 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 62 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 63 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 64 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 65 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Gideoni chapa Abidan in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 66 Nisom lhinna in, Ammishaddai chapa Ahiezer, Dan phung lamkaipan amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 67 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 68 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 69 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 70 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 71 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Ammishaddai chapa Ahiezer in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 72 Nisom le khat lhinna in Ocran chapa Pagiel, Asher phung lamkai pan anoija ho hi maicham a din ahin tohdoh e.
\mi1 
\v 73 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 74 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 75 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 76 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 77 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Ocran chapa Pagiel in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 78 Nisom le ni lhinna in Enan chapa Ahira, Napthali phung lamkaipan amaicham ahin tohdoh in ahi.
\mi1 
\v 79 Ama thilto chu dangka kongtong pound 3 le dangka kong pound 1 a gih (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Hiche kong tenia chang le miim thilto changbong chu Olive thao a kisunou cheh ahi.
\v 80 Aman sana kong dimset gimnamtui ounce li a gih jong ahin choijin ahi.
\v 81 Aman bongla, kelngoi chal, chule kumkhat lhingsa kelnou chal chu pumgo maicham dingin,
\v 82 chule kelcha achal khat chu chonset kithoina maichama pang dingin ahin kai in ahi.
\v 83 Chamna maicham adin bongchal ni, kelngoichal nga, kelchal nga, kelngoi kumkhat lhingsa nga ho chu ahinkai in ahi. Hichengse hi Enan chapa Ahira in kilhaina thilto a ahinto ho chu ahiye.
\b
\p 
\v 84 Israel a phung lamkai hon maicham phung thao ana kinu a kilhandohna maicham dia ahin todoh hou chu: Sum-eng lhengkong len som le ni, Sum-eng kisilna kong som le ni, gimnamtui kikholna sana lhengkong ho ahiuve.
\v 85 Hou-Intheng a shekel kitena a ilep leh sum-eng lhengkong len khat gihdan chu pounds 3 ahin chuleh sum-eng kisilna kong khat gihdan chu pounds 1 ahi. Sum-eng mong mong agihdan chu pounds 60 ahi.
\v 86 Hou-Intheng a shekel kitena a ilep leh Sana lhengkong som le ni khat cheh gimnamtui jaona a agihdan chu ounces 4 (muntheng a thil tena shekel dungjuiya kite) ahi. Sana mong mong agom a agihdan chu pounds 3 ahi.
\v 87 Bongchal anou som le ni, kelngoi achal lhingset som le ni, kum khat lhing cheh kelngoi achal som le ni pumgo thilto a dingin ahung kitoh in, todoh dinga umsa lhosoh maicham jong ahi. Chonset kilhaina maicham dingin kelcha achal som le ni ahung kikailut in ahi.
\v 88 Chamna maicham dingin bongchal somni le li, kelngoi achal lhingset somgup, kelchal somgup, kumkhat lhingsa kelngoi chal somgup ahung kitohdoh in ahi. Hicheng hi maicham phung thao akinu jouva maicham phunga dia hung kitohho ahi.
\v 89 Mose chu Pakai toh kihou dinga Houbuh sunga alutji teng, aman houpina awgin thingkhong akhu themmona a konna themchanna mun - Kitepna thingkhong chunga kinga Cherub teni lailunga kon chun aja jin ahi. Hiche lai mun a konna chu Pakaiyin ama chu ahin houpi ji ahiye.
\c 8
\s1 Thaomeiho kigontupna
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseiyin, \x + \xo 8:1 \xt Potdohbu 25:31-40; 37:17-24\x*
\v 2 “Aaron in hiche hilchahna ho hi pe in: Thaomei khom sagi chu atunna a na tundoh tengleh, amalam a thaomei khom mailah chu asalvah jouna dingin tungdoh in.”
\v 3 Aaron in chuti chun aboltan ahi. Thaomei khom sagiho chun amailam salvahna din Pakaiyin Mose henga asei bang bang chun atungdoh tan ahi.
\v 4 Hiche thaomei khom aboncha a, akhombul apat ajem kisemna chan gei chu sana kikheng a kisemdoh ahi. Hiche hi Pathen'in Mose alim um ding dol avetsah bangtah a kisem'a ahi.
\s1 Levi te kithenso
\p 
\v 5 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin,
\v 6 “Tun Israel mipi adang ho jousea kon'in Levi te tumkhen inlang, chonna dan ngai bangin sutheng sohkei in.
\v 7 Kisuhtheng na twi chu na thinkhum ding, amaho apumpi uva atahsa uva amul jouseu kivoumui diu chule amanchah jingu apon hou akisoptheng diu ahi. Hitia chu aboltengu leh chonna dol a athenga ahi tauve.
\v 8 Bongchal gol khat leh lhosohga maicham a konna changbong Olive thao a kisunom chip chep, chule bongchal golkhat mama toh chonset kilhaina maicham a dinga ahinto dingu ahi.
\v 9 Chuteng Israel nam mite jouse chu nakhop khom a Houbuh kot phunga um dia Levi te chu na pehdoh ding ahi.
\v 10 Pathen na dinga Levi te chu na pehdoh tengleh, Israel miten amaho chunga chu akhut u angap diu ahi.
\v 11 Aaron in akhut teni adopsanga Israel mipite lah a konna Levi te chu Pathen a dinga atumbeh a katdohna anei ding, hitia chu Pathen lhacha natong dinga lhandohna anei ding ahi.
\v 12 Hiche jouteng chule Levi te jousen bongnou achal ni chunga khut ngapna anei diu, bongchal nou khat chule chonset maicham kisem chu pumgo maicham kisemna ding ahin, Pathen henga Levi te chun kisuhthengna anei diu chamdel a um diu ahiye.
\v 13 Aaron le achaten Levi te chu amaho masanga adinsah uva, akhut u adopsang jou tengu leh Pathen masanga loupi tah a maicham asempeh diu ahi.
\v 14 Levi te chu Israel mipi te lah a konna natum khandoh diu, ajeh chu amaho keija um jing diu ahi.
\v 15 Hichengse kichai teng, Houbuh sunga chu lut diu anatoh diu ijakai ajom thei diu ahitai. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin amaho chu asuhthenga na pehdoh ahitan nangma henga loupi tah a na pehdoh ahitai.
\v 16 Israel mipite dingin Levi te hi keima dinga kikoisa ahi. Amaho hi Israel te chilhah apeng masa pen jouse khel'a kangeh ahin. Amaho khel'a Levi te kakilah ahitai.
\v 17 Israel mipite lah a peng masapen mihem pasal ahin gancha hijongleh keima a ahi sohkeiyin, Egypt mite pasal chapa masapen jouse kana suhmang nia pat chun keima dinga kana gontupsa ahitai. \x + \xo 8:17 \xt Potdohbu 13:2\x*
\v 18 Levi te phung hi keiman Israel te lah a chapa peng masa penna kakoi ahitai.
\v 19 Aaron le achate ho hi Levi te vetup dinga kisem ahitai. Israel te thakhel a maicham Houbuh a kintheng natong ding ahiuvin, pumgo maicham a kisuhthengna kin thenga ana tong le ding mong mong ahiuve.
\v 20 Chuti chun Mose, Aaron chule Israel mipi jousen Levi te chu alhengdoh un Pathen'in amaho thu apeh dungjuijin abol tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Levi ten achonset nau chu aki soptheng uvin chule aponsil ho jong aki noilhah un Pathen masanga loupi tah in maicham asempeh tai. Aaron in amaho chu athenselna ding uvin maicham abolpeh in ajeh chu Pathen toh chamdel'a aumna diu ahiye.
\v 22 Chuteng Levi te chu Houbuh maicham’a sunglha diu kintheng natoh apat diu, Aaron le achaten akithopi diu ahiye. Amaho thunit dinga kipat jouse Pathen'in Levi te jui dinga Mose ahin hetsah ho chu anit sohkeiyun ahi.
\v 23 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose hengah hiti hin aseiyin ahi.
\v 24 Hiche dan hi Levi ten anit diu: kum-somni le nga alhin tengu leh Houbuh sunga chu kintheng natoh apatna diu,
\v 25 chule Levi te chu kum-somnga alhin teng ule kichol thei ding ahi tauve.
\v 26 Levi te chu akichol joulam teng ule a Levi chan khompiho khel a Houbuh vengtup a jong pangthei nalai diu, hinlah anatong jinglaiho banga vang pang thai talou diu ahi. Hiche hi Levi te kiman ding dan napeh ding chu ahi.
\c 9
\s1 Kalchuh Kut Nina
\p 
\v 1 Israel te chu Egypt a patna ahung kichon doh jou kum khat ahung lhin chun Sinai lhang a gamthip lah a chun Pakaiyin Mose kom'a thu ahin seiye. Chuche kum'a lha masapen achun aseijin, \x + \xo 9:1 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-13\x*
\v 2 “Kalchuh Kut kimanna ding phat kitepna a hi aman ding uvin Israel mite chu seipeh tan ,
\v 3 hichu lha masapen nisom le nili lhinna a khojin chip chep phat hi ding ahi. Hiche kipa thanop kibol ding dan thupeh ho leh dan umho phate a najui sah ding ahi.”
\v 4 Mose’n jong mipi henga Kalchuh Kut kipa golnop abol ding uvin aseipeh tan
\v 5 Sinai lhang gamthip lah a nisom le nili lhinna khojin chip chep hi ding ahi. Chule Pathen'in Mose athupeh bang bang chun ama hon jong kipa golnop chu abol tauvin ahi.
\v 6 Ahinlah amaho lah a mi phabep chun mithi long ana thamkhah jeh un, chonna ngai bangin akisuboh a ahitauvin, hiche nikho a Kalchuh Kut kipa golnop a chun alha thei tapouve. Hiche nikho chun Mose leh Aaron kom'a ahungun
\v 7 “Keihon mithi long ka tham khah tah jeh un, chonna ngai banga atheng louva kahi tauve. Hijongleh Israel mipin asem lenga keihon jong Pathen anga maicham kasem mo diu ham?” ahung tiuvin ahi.
\v 8 Mose chun adonbut, “Nangho dinga Pathen a konna hilchahna kamu kah in khongai un” ati.
\v 9 Pakaiyin Mose ahin donbutna chu hiche hi ahi.
\v 10 “Hiche hilchahna ho hi Israel mipi te seipeh in: Tukhang hihen lang khang hunglhung ding ho hijongleh chonna ngai banga akisuboh kha hihen, kholgam a chedoh ho hijongleh Kalchuh Kut kipa golnop a pangthei dingu ahi.
\v 11 Kalchuh Kut kipa golnop kichai lhakhat lhin teng Kalchuh Kut maicham thilto abol dingu ahi, hichu lhani lhinna a nisom le nili lhinna khojin chip chep phat hi ding ahi. Hiche teng chuleh Kalchuh Kut kelngoi sa chu anche kha le cholsolou changlhah toh aneh tha dingu ahi.
\v 12 Ama hon kelngoi chu jingkah khovah geija akoi theilou dingu, chuleh hiche agu jong asuhboh theilou dingu ahiye. Kalchuh Kut kimanna chung changa dan umho hi ajui cheh dingu ahi. \x + \xo 9:12 \xt Potdohbu 12:46; Jn 19:36\x*
\v 13 “Ahin Israel mi hiya chonna ngaiya aboh jong hilou, kholche a jindoh jong hilou, ahivanga Kalchuh Kut nahsah lou miho chu Israel nampi a konna kah lhah a um ding ahi. Pathen maicham jong aphat tah a ahin todoh louleh achonsetna jal a themmo changa um ding ahiuve.
\v 14 Nangho lah a namdang mi Kalchuh Kut golnop a jaonom aum leh, nit ding leh jui dinga kipe jouse hi anit angaiyin, hiche dan hin Israel nam chilhah a kon hihen lang gamdang chilhah a konna koi hijongleh akan sohkei ding ahi.
\s1 Meilom leh meikong
\p 
\v 15 Houbuh ahin phudoh nikho uchun, meilom in Houbuh chu atom tan ahi. Houbuh chunga meilom nilhah apat jingkah geiya um chu meikong lomtoh abang jengin ahi.
\v 16 Hiche meilom Houbuh chunga um, jan tengleh meikong alom a hung kilahji tobang chun aum jing tan ahi.
\v 17 Houbuh chunga meilom chu akihohdal jiteng, Israel mipi ten hiche amaicham ponbuh chu aphelha jiuvin meibol lom chu ajuiji uvin ahi. Chuleh hiche meilom akingah ngahna achun Israel mipi ten ngahmun akisem kit jiuvin ahi.
\v 18 Hiti chun che dinga Pathen thupeh amu dungjuiyun lam ajot un, ngahmun asa jiuvin ahi. chuleh Houbuh chunga meilom aum chan chun ngahmun dalha louvin aum jiuvin ahi.
\v 19 Hiche meilom chu Houbuh chunga nisot tah aumji teng Israel te chu akichol jiuvin Pathen Houna dinga atoh ding umho chu atong jiuvin ahi.
\v 20 Phat khat khat teng Pathen thupeh dungjuijin meilom chu Houbuh chunga ni chomcha bou akingaji in, amaho jong ni chomcha bou akichol jiuve. Chuteng Pathen thupeh dungjuijin ngahmun chu aphe lhauvin achejom kitji tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Phat chomkhat kit teng meilom chu jan khovah in aum'in jingkah teng akichon doh jin ahi. Ahinlah sun hihen jan hita jongleh hiche meilom chu ahung kihodoh teng ngahmun chu aphelha jiuvin achejom jingji un ahi.
\v 22 Houbuh maicham chunga meilom chu ni ni umhen, lhakhat umhen, ahilouleh kumkhat um jongleh Israel mipite chu ngahmun a chun akichol jing jiuvin apotdoh jipouvin ahi. Amavang meilom chu Houbuh chunga ahung kiho dal teng ngahmun chu aphet un achejom kitji tauvin ahi.
\v 23 Hiti chun Pakai thupeh bangtah in akichol un, akalsong jingun ahi, chule Pathen'in Mose a konin athupeh jouse chu abolkim soh jingun ahi.
\c 10
\s1 Dangka Sumkon ho
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseijin,
\v 2 “Mipi ho koukhomna ding leh ponbuh phetlhahna dinga melchihna a manchah din dangka sehcha a kikhengjol pengkul ni sem doh in.
\v 3 Hiche Pengkul teni chu ahung kimutji teng mipi ho chu Houbuh lutna kotphung a nangma masanga hungkhomji dingu ahi.
\v 4 Ahinlah pengkul khat bou chu ahung kimut tah vang leh lamkai ho bou - Israel phung lamkai jouse atahsa tah uva na masanga hung kilah cheh diu ahi.
\v 5 Nangman hiche gin a chu hetsahna nanei teng Houbuh a kon solam a ngahmun nei phung ho chun angahmun u chu aphet lhah uva malam a chu chejom ding ahiuve.
\v 6 Nangma in hiche gin a hetsahna anivei channa nanei teng lhanglam a ngahmun neihon ajui dingu ahi. Achejom jing dingu hetsahana a chu nangman chomcha a naginsah ding ahi.
\v 7 Ahinlah mipi kikhom khom hen nati teng, pengkul chu awgin chomjep in mut in.
\v 8 Aaron chilhah, thempu ho bou chun pengkul ho amut thei dingu ahiye. Hiche hi nanga dinga akhang akhanga aum den jing ding leh nit jing ding dan chu ahi.
\v 9 “Nangma ho gamsunga na hunglut uva, nangho doujing na melma teho sat dinga na kondoh ding tengu leh pengkul ho kigottupna dia nagin sah diu ahi. Hiche teng chuleh na Pakaiyin nahin geldoh ding, na melmate a konna na huhdoh ding ahi.
\v 10 Na pengkul ho chu kipa thanop phat a jong namut ging ding, kumsunga kipa golnop ho leh lha thah hung kisim pan phat ho a jong namut ging ding ahi. Hiche pengkul ho chu kipana maicham kisem phat hihen, pumgo maicham kibol sih hijongleh hiche maichamho chunga chu namut ging ding ahi. Hiche pengkul ho gin chun na Pathen a na kitepna nahin geldoh sah ding ahi. Keima na Pakai na Pathen chu kahiye.”
\ms1 Israel ten Sinai adalhah u
\m 
\v 11 Kumni jouva Israel te Egypt gam a konna ahungdoh nau alhani channa a nisomni alhinni chun meilom chu kitepna ponbuh akon chun akikhang doh tan ahi.
\v 12 Hijeh chun Israel mipi chun Sinai gamthip lah a kon'in ahungdoh un Paran gamthip lah aphah uva meilom akingah masang sen mun chom chom'ah ana kitolle le un ahi.
\v 13 Mose'n Pakaiya kon hilchahna amu bang tah a Israel mipi ho amasapen a dinga ahung kitol pan u chun,
\v 14 Judah phungin mipi kitol chu alamkaiyun ahi. Aponlap nung uva akitolun, chule alamkai uva chu Amminadab chapa Nahshon ahi.
\v 15 Amaho banjom chu Issachar te ahiuvin, ahin lamkai chu Nathanel kitipa Zuar chapa ahin,
\v 16 chule Zebulun chilhah hon ajom un, Helon chapa Eliab chun ahin lamkaijin ahi.
\v 17 Hichun Houbuh chu aphelha uvin Levi te sunga konna Gershon te le Merari te chun Houbuh apo uvin abanjom in acheuvin ahi.
\v 18 Abanin Reuben te akitol'un, aponlap u nung ajui uve. Shedeur chapa Elizur chun amaho ahin lamkai in ahi.
\v 19 Aban chu Simeon ten ahinjuiyun, amaho Lamkai pa chu Zunishadai chapa Shelumiel ahin,
\v 20 chule Gad phung chu Deuel chapa Eliasaph in ahin lamkaijin ahi.
\v 21 Hiche banjom chu Levi te lah a konna Kohath te ahiuvin Houbuh sunga manchah theng ho jouse ahinpo un ahi. Ngahmun thah a mipi lhun masanga Houbuh chu tundohsaa akoi diu ahi.
\v 22 Hiche banjom'a chun Ephraim te chu ahung kitol uve. Amaho lamkai a hung panga chu Ammihud chapa Elishama ahi.
\v 23 Amaho chu Manasseh phungin ahinjui un, Pedahzur chapa Gamaliel kiti pan ahin lamkai un,
\v 24 chuleh Benjamin phunga mipi chu Gideoni chapa Abidan in ahin lamkaijin ahi.
\v 25 Dan phung mite chu achaina ahiuvin, aponlap u nunga ahung kitolun chule phung jouse nunga angahtup in apang uve. Alamkai pau chu Ammishaddai chapa Ahiezer ahi.
\v 26 Amaho chutoh kilhonin Asher phung mite akitolun Okran chapa Pagiel in alamkaiyun,
\v 27 chuleh Naphtali phung mite jong Enan chapa Ahira in ahin lamkaiyun ahi.
\p 
\v 28 Hitia hi agol gol a Israel chilhah te, ama ama kihopkhen dol cheh a hung kitolji ahiuve.
\p 
\v 29 Nikhat chu Mose’n ajinu sopipa, Median mipa Reuel chapa Hobab kom'a aseiyin, “Keiho hi Pakaiyin eiteppeh nau lam chu jot jing kahiuve, ajeh chu Pakaiyin ‘ka peh ding nahiuve’ ati ahi. Hungin keihon nangma ngailu tah a kabol diu ahi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin chun Israel dingin kitepna aneijin kidangtah a phatthei aboh ding ahi!”
\v 30 Ahinlah Hobab in adonbut in, “Kanompoi, kache louding ahi. Keima ka gam le ka insung mite henga kile ding kahi,” ati.
\v 31 Mose ataovin, “Lungset tah in nei dalhah hih un,” gamthip a hoilaiya ngahmun kisong ding ham ti nangin nahet ahi. Hungin, nei lamhil uvin.”
\v 32 Kasei nei noppeh leh, Pakaiya kon phattheina kachan jouseu inei khom diu ahi' ati.
\v 33 Pakai molsang adalhah jou uchun nithum sung ana kitol’un, amasang uva Pakai thutep Thingkhong chun hoiya kinga a akichol diu chu avetsah un ahi.
\v 34 Hitia niseh a lam ajot jing lai un, Pakai meibol lom in akhu khum jingun apuile jing uve.
\v 35 Chule thingkong chu akitoldohji teng, Mose’n aw sangtah a, “Kipatdoh tan, O Pakai, na melma te kithe cheh uhen, nangma angsunga kon'in jammang uhen” tia asap ding ahi.\x + \xo 10:35 \xt Labu 68:1\x*
\v 36 Chule thingkong chu akikoi lhah teng, “Simsenlou asang sang umna Israel te henga hung kilekit tan Pakai” tia aman aseikit ding ahi.
\c 11
\s1 Mose kom'a mipi ho kiphinna
\p 
\v 1 Phat chomkhat jouvin mipi ho chun hahsat genthei jeh a lunglhai louna ahin phong doh tauvin, chule Pakaiyin aseidoh ho jouseu abonchan ajasohkeiyin ahi. Hiche Pathen lunghanna chu amaho chunga akoujah jengtan, amaho halvam ding meikong asoltan, chule ngahmun polam a um mi phabeppi chu asumang tan ahi.
\v 2 Hichun mite ho chu Mose henga kithopina ngaichan akap un amao tauvin, chuin Mose chun Pathen henga taona anei phat in meikong chu athiptai.
\v 3 Hiche jou chun, hiche lai lhang chu Taberah (Hichu 'mei kouna mun' tina ahi) tin akihetai, ajeh chu Pathen a konna meikong chun amaho lah a mi phabep ahal lhahna mun ahi.
\v 4 Israel mite toh lamjot khom namdang ho chun Egypt gam'a neh le chah ho chu ahin ngaicha tauvin, hichun Israel chate jong ahung kiphin kit tauvin, “Oh, Sa themkhat beh neipe un!” tin a eujah tauvin ahi.
\v 5 “Egypt gamsunga nga aman beija kaneh jiu ka lhangai jun ahi. Chule changmai ho, donkho ho, louthul ho, louthul atil neiho, chule changnam ho kangaicha uve.
\v 6 Ahinlah tuhin ka duchat hou aum tapoi. Phat jousea kamu jingu hiche Manna bou hi ahitai.
\v 7 Manna hi louthul amu neocha cha ho tobang ahin hichu ai-eng tobanga eng dup ahi. \x + \xo 11:7 \xt Potdohbu 16:31\x*
\v 8 Mipi chun tollhang a hichu akilokhom jiuvin ahi. Amahon hichu asuhbongna thei thil ahilouleh suhdu le kongphal a asubong jiuve. Chuteng ahon uva changlhah pheng ahin sodoh sah jiu ahi. Hiche changlhah pheng chu Olive thao toh kihal a nehthei kisanggep tuitah tobang ahi.\x + \xo 11:8 \xt Potdohbu 16:13-15\x*
\v 9 Manna chu janteng ponbuh chunga chu daitwi toh hung lhahtha ji ahi.
\v 10 Hichun Mose’n mipi ho ama ama ponbuh kotbul’a akiphin nau husa ajan, chule Pakai chu nasatah in alunghang tai. Mose’n jong nopmo asah lheh in ahi.
\v 11 Chuin Mose’n Pakai henga aseijin, “Ipidia nasoh hi hiti lom lom a hi nei gimbol hitam? Ka chunga khotona neijin! Bolkhel ipi kanei a hiche mite pohgih jouse kapoh ding naphal ham?
\v 12 Keiman amaho hi kahindoh sa hiuvem? Hiche vannoiya hi kahin pohlut hiuvem? Minun naosen ajenle banga ipi dia amaho hi kaban a kadople dinga nei seipeh ham? Apu apateu nana pehna gam a chu iti keiman amaho hi ka puilut jou ding ham?
\v 13 Keiman hoilam a hiche mipi ho neh dinga sa kalah ding hitam! Amaho akiphin phin jengun, “Neh ding sa nei peuvin!” atiuve.
\v 14 Keiman hiche mipi ho hi kachangin kajou tapoi! Hiche pohgih hi kapohjou kalval in agihtai!
\v 15 Hitobang tah a hi gimsah ding mong neitileh, kipat inlang nei that doh tan. Neihin khohsah inlang hiche gim genthei ho a kon hin nei hoidoh in!” ati.
\s1 Mose in alhendoh Upa mi somsagi
\p 
\v 16 Hichun Pathen'in Mose kom'a ahin seijin, “Keima angsung a Israel mipi te lamkai leh Upa ho somsagi hin puilut in. Hiche lamkai ho chu Houbuh a nang toh ding khom uhen.
\v 17 Keima hung kumlha ingting kahin houpi ding nahi. Keiman nanga um lhagao phabep khat la ingting amaho chunga hiche lhagao chu ka khumlut peh ding ahi. Ama hon mipi ho pohgih chu apohhu diu, nangin na changa napoh ngai louding ahitai.
\v 18 “Chule mipi ho chu seipeh un, 'Nangho kisutheng un, ajeh chu jing nikho teng nang hon sa neh ding nanei dingu ahitai. Nangho na kiphin un, chuleh Pathen'in naka nau ajatai.' 'Saphe themkhat jeh in Egypt a um kanom jouve! na tiuve' tua hi Pakaiyin nangho nahin peh diu naneh tei dingu ahitai.
\v 19 Hichu nikhat ahilouleh nini tina jong ahi tapon, ni nga, nisom chule nisomni tina jong ahi tapoi, ati.
\v 20 Nanghon lhakhat sunga na chimdeh tokah uva naneh diu ahi. Ajeh chu nang hon nakom uva um jing Pakai na pampai un, chuleh ama kom'a kiphinnan naseiyun, “Idia Egypt gam ihin dalhah mong mong uham” natiuve.
\v 21 Ahin Mose chun Pakai chu adonbut in, “Tua hi mihem sang jagup keima toh um kahiuve, ahin Pakai nangma in 'lhakhat sungse aneh diu kapeh ding ahi! nati.'
\v 22 Ka gancha neihou jouse kithat jongleh mihem hijat chun lung nachim sah nauvin tem? Twikhanglen’a um nga jouse kiman henlang hita jongleh hiche ho jeh a chu lhing mong ding hinam?
\v 23 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin, “Ka khut hi atha lhasam aham? Tua hi nangman ka thusei hi atah ahi alhem ahi na hetchen ding ahitai!” ati.
\v 24 Hichun Mose aga potdoh tan Pakaiyin ahenga asei bang chun mipi ho aga hetsah tan ahi. Mose’n Upa ho mi somsagi asukhom in amaho chu Houbuh kimvel'a chun adin sah tan ahi.
\v 25 Chuin meilom lah a kon chun Pakai ahung kumlhan Mose chu akihoulimpi tai. Hichun Upa somsagi ho chu Mose apeh bang bang Lhagao chu amaho jouse chunga apetan ahi. Chule lhagao ho chu mi somsagi ho chunga achuh phat un, gaovin thu aphongdoh tauvin ahi. Ahinlah hiche tobang thil umchan dol chu asohkit tapon ahi.
\v 26 Mipa ni Eldad le Medad chu ngahmun nunglam ah aum lhonin ahi. Amani chu upaho min kijih lutna a ajao lhonin, ahinlah amanin Houbuh chu adalhah lhon lou beh ahitai. Ahijeng vangin amani chunga jong chun Lhagao chu aum tan, hichun amani jong chun gaothu aphongdoh lhon e.
\v 27 Pasal gollhang khat alhaiyin Mose kom'a thu chu agah lhut tan, “Eldad le Medad in ngahmun sunga gaothu aphong doh lhon tai!” ahung ti.
\v 28 Nun chapa Joshua, aneo laiya pat a Mose kithopi a hung pang pa vang chun lunglhai louna aphong doh in “Mose kapu, Eldad le Medad khu suthip tan!” tin aseiye.
\v 29 Ahinlah Mose’n adonbut in, “Keima a ding ngaitona a ipi na thangsetpi ham? Keiman kadei pha kasah vang chu mijouse hi themgao hihen lang chuleh Pakaiyin alhagao chu amaho jouse chunga jong chun koi cheh le kati!” atin ahi.
\v 30 Hichun Mose jong chu Upa ho chutoh ngahmun kom langa akile kit tauve.
\s1 Pakaiyin Vamin ahinsol
\p 
\v 31 Hiti chun Pakaiyin Vamin pui dingin twikhanglen a huipi ahin nunsah tan, ngahmun chung leh akimvel jousea vamin akhehsah tan ahi. Amaho umna akon a avetna lamlam u mile phabep a gamla chan a chun tol a kon feet thum sang bou leng thei Vamim adimsoh tan ahi.
\v 32 Hichun mipi chu a potdoh un hiche vamim chu nilhum keijin aman un hiche ni jan khovah keijin jong chuleh ajing gei jong chun aloh khom nalaijun ahi. Bushel somnga chunglam jeng alohdoh uvin ahi! Ngahmun kimvel a chun vamin sa ho chu agotna dingin aphou un ahi.
\v 33 Ahinlah Israel ten saphe chu akam uva alhai’u aval lhah ding kontah u chun Pakai lunghanna achung uva ahung chutan, pul gimneitah alhunsah tan ahi.
\v 34 Hiti ahijeh chun hilaimun chu Kibroth-hattaavah (hichu milop ho lhankhuh) aki sahtai ajeh chu ama hon Egypt lamah saphe ngaicha jing miho avuinau chu ahi.
\v 35 Kibroth-hattaavah apat chun Israel mite chu Hazeroth gei chu ahung kitol un, phat chomkhat hilai mun achun ahung kichol uve.
\c 12
\s1 Miriam leh Aaron kiphin
\p 
\v 1 Hazeroth mun'a aum laijun, Mose in Cush mi numei khat akichenpi jeh in Miriam le Aaron chun ama demna thu asei lhon tai.
\v 2 Amanin hiti hin asei lhonin, “Pakai chu Mose henga bou kilah thei ham? Eini henga jong hung kilah hilou ham?” ati lhon e. Hilah amani thusei chu Pakaiyin ajasoh keijin ahi.
\v 3 (Tunvang Mose chu akineosah lheh jengin ahi- Leiset a akineosah penpa sang'in akineosah joh nalai in ahi.)
\v 4 Hichun gangtah in Pakaiyin Mose, Aaron chule Miriam chu akouloi in hitin aseipeh tai, “Nathum uvin Houbuh lama gache tauvin!” ati. Hichun amaho thumin jong Houbuh lam chu ajon tauvin ahi.
\v 5 Chuin Pathen chu meilom khom lim'in ahung kumlhan Houbuh lutna a chun ading denin, “Aaron leh Miriam!” tin ahinkou in ahileh amani jong ama chejep lhonin ahi.
\v 6 Chuin Pathen'in ahoulimpi lhonin tuhin ka thusei ho hi ngai lhonin:
\p “Nangma ho lah a themgao um ahileh,
\p Pakai, Keima hi, gaova kiphong ding kahi tai.
\p Ahilouleh manga kaki houlim pi ding ahitai.
\p 
\v 7 Hinlah kasohpa Mose vang hitobang chu ahipoi, Ka insung pumpi a
\p ama hi katahsan pentah ahi. \x + \xo 12:7 \xt Heb 3:2\x*
\p 
\v 8 Kicheh tah in, paolem mang louvin
\p Keiman ama toh kimaito in thu kaseije!
\p Aman Pakai chu ahina bang tah a amu ahi.
\p Chuti ahileh idia kasohpa Mose dem ding kicha lou nahi lhon ham?”
\p 
\v 9 Pakai chu amaho chunga chun alunghang lheh jeng tan, adalha lhon tai.
\v 10 Houbuh chunga meilhang akitol toh lhonin chu a ding Miriam chu tiphah natna jeh chun avun chu buhbang bangin abang tan ahi. Aaron in Miriam chunga thilsoh ijakai amusoh phat in,
\v 11 Mose henga akaptan, “Oh, kapu! Hiche ngol-hoitah chonsetna kana boldoh jeh lhonin gotna neipe lhon hihbeh in.
\v 12 Amanu jong hi naosen athisa a hung peng, apen lhah lhah a amonsa bangin koi hihbeh in,” ati.
\v 13 Hichun Mose Pakai anga akapjah jeng tan, “O Pathen, katao ahi, lungset tah in amanu hi damsah tan!” ati.
\v 14 Ahin Pakaiyin Mose jah a seitan, “Amanu hi apa chun achil aset khum hitaleh, nisagi sung chu aboh a um a jum le ja athoh louding ham? Hijeh chun amanu hi ngahmun pamlam a nisagi sung koidoh un lang, chujou teng lahlut kit thei hi ding ahi” ati. \x + \xo 12:14 \xt Minbu 5:2,3\x*
\v 15 Hiti chun Miriam chu ngahmun pamlam'ah nisagi aumsah un, chuleh akitol kit masang un, amanu chu ngahmun sunga ahung kit ding chu mipi ho chun angah un ahi.
\v 16 Hiti chun Hazeroth adalha tauvin ache peh un Paran gamthip munkhat a ngahmun khat akisemkit tauvin ahi.
\c 13
\s1 Som le ni in Canaan gam akholtoh
\p 
\v 1 Tun Pakaijin Mose heng’ah,
\v 2 “Canaan gam, Israel chate kapehna gam gakhol toh ding pasal ho sol in. Phung som le ni ho a kon a lamkai khat cheh sol tan” ati.
\v 3 Hichun Mose’n Pakai thupeh bang chun abol tai. Paran gamthip a angahmun uva kon chun phung lamkai cheh mi som le ni asol tan ahi.
\v 4 Hiche ho hi amin uleh aphung min cheh uchu ahi:
\s1 Phungmin Lamkai
\m Reuben sungkon Zaccur chapa Shammua
\m 
\v 5 Simeon sungkon Hori chapa Shaphat
\m 
\v 6 Judah sungkon Jephunneh chapa Caleb
\m 
\v 7 Issachar sungkon Joseph chapa Igal
\m 
\v 8 Ephraim sungkon Nun chapa Hoshea
\m 
\v 9 Benjamin sungkon Raphu chapa Palti
\m 
\v 10 Zebulun sungkon Sodi chapa Gaddiel
\m 
\v 11 Joseph chapa Manasseh sungkon Susi chapa Gaddi
\m 
\v 12 Dan sungkon Gemalli chapa Ammiel
\m 
\v 13 Asher sungkon Michael chapa Sethur
\m 
\v 14 Napthali sungkon Vophsi chapa Nahbi
\m 
\v 15 Gad sungkon Maki chapa Geuel
\m 
\v 16 Amaho chengse hi Mose’n gamkhol dinga alhendoh pasal ho chu ahiuve. (Mose’n Nun chapa Hoshea chu Joshua in akou e.)
\m 
\v 17 Mose’n hiche pasal gamve lhi dinga ngansena anei a soldoh ho chu thugahna aneiyin: “Sahlam Negev hopa thinglhang lam naho diu ahi.
\v 18 Gam chu itoh bang'am, hiche gam a um mihem ho chu hat uvem lhasam uvem, tam uvem lhom uvem ti nahin khol doh diu ahi.
\v 19 Gam chu itobang ham gaveuvin. Gam chu gampha ham phalou ham? Kulpi bang anei uvem, ahilouleh ngahmun mai mai a um uham?
\v 20 Leiset chu leithao hoina ham lhasam ham? Chu a chu thingphung tam am? Theitop hinso unlang agam gaasoh hettheina dingin thingga louga ho jouse hinpo un. (Hiche phat chu lengpiga masa lophat laitah ahi.)
\m 
\v 21 Hichun ache touvun Zin gamthip apat akhol chil un Rehob gam Lebo-hamath kom dung gei chu abonchan gakhol sohkeiyun.
\v 22 Sahlam ahouvin, Negev gamthip mun ajot pauvin chuin Hebron alhung tauve. Hikom mun chu Ahiman, Sheshai, chuleh Talmai (Anak chilhah ho) chen na ahi. (Hebron khopi chu Egypt khopi Zoan sanga kum-sagi masanga ana um ahitai.)
\v 23 Ama hon Eshcol phaicham ahin phah uchun lengpi thei boh khat ahin sat lhauvin, aletthei beh jeh chun moljol a minin ahin pu un ahi. Kolbuthei leh theichang ga ho jong vetchil dingin ahin ahinpo lhungun ahi.
\v 24 Hiche lai mun chu Eshcol phaicham akitin ahi. Ajeh chu gamve lhi Israel mihon hilai mun a chu lengpiga aboh a ahin satna mun u chu ahi
\s1 Gamve lhi ho thulhut
\p 
\v 25 Nisomli jen gam le go kholchilna anei jou phat un pasal ho chu ahung kileuvin
\v 26 Mose, Aaron chule Israel mipi ho kom Paran gamthip, Kadesh mun a ahung kinungle tauve.
\v 27 Hichun ama hon Mose jah a hiti hin aseiyun: “Keiho gam kholtoh dia nei nganse nauva kache uchun, agam chu anom in avethoi lheh jengin - Khoiju leh bongnoi lonna gam ahi. Hichengse hi gamsunga gasoh ho chu ahi.
\v 28 Ahinlah hilai gam'a umho chu athahat theiyun, chuleh a khopi hou jong chu alen thei in hoitah in aveng tup un ahi. Chuleh Anak chilhah milen ho jong chu kaga mu uve!
\v 29 Amalek mite chu Negev a acheng un, Hit mite, Jebus mite chuleh Amor mite ho jouse thinglhang lam a acheng un ahi. Canaan mite chu Jordan phaicham leh Mediterranean Dillen pang dunga acheng un ahi.”
\s1 Caleb in Pathen a konna thu asei
\p 
\v 30 Ahinlah Caleb in Mose angsunga thulhut miho chu suhthip ding angaiton, “Eiho cheu hitin gam chu gala jeng uhite,” “Eihon ijo tei tei diu ahi!” ati.
\v 31 Amavang Caleb toh gam kholle a che ho lah chu anom pouvin, “Amaho eiho sanga hatjo ahiuve! atiuve.
\v 32 Chuti chun lung lhahdaina thulhut joh chu Israel mite lah a ahin seiphong uvin: “Kache uva kakhol chil u gam leiset chun koi hileh hilai mun a gacheng ho chu avallhum diu ahi. Mi kahin mu hou jouse jong chu alen theiyun ahi.
\v 33 Chuleh keihon milen tah tah, Anak chillhah mite jong chu kamu uve. Amaho toh tedingin keiho chu khaokhoho tobang bep kahiuvin, amaho jengin jong hitia chu eigel'u ahiye!” atiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 13:33 \xt Semtilbu 6:4\x*
\c 14
\s1 Israel Te Canaan Gam Lut Ding Anop Lou
\p 
\v 1 Hichun Israel mite abonchauvin aw sangtah in akap un chuleh amaho chu jan khovah geijin akap un ahi.
\v 2 Hiche mipi awgin lakisa chu akithong jengin Mose le Aaron douna kibol ahi. “Egypt gam'a ana thidoh kihi le phajonte.” tin asam uve.
\v 3 Pakaiyin ipi dinga hiche gam lah a hi gal’a thi ding bep a eipuidoh uham ? Kaji te hou le numei chapang ho athigam bep dinga hung kipuidoh hitam! Egypt gamsunga kakile uva phachomjo louding ham? tin a sei uve.
\v 4 Hichun Amaho khat le khat akihou khomun eihon lamkai thah lheng uhitin Egypt lamah kinung le tau hite! akitiuvin ahi.
\v 5 Hichun Mose le Aaron chu Israel mite jouse masang tol lang ngan akunlha lhon tan ahi.
\v 6 Pasal mini gam kholla che teni chu Nun chapa Joshua le Jephunneh chapa Caleb chun aponsil lhon abotkeh lhon tai.
\v 7 Amanin Israel mipi te ho lah a asei lhon tan, keinin ka khol chil lhon gam ho chu kidang tah le loupi tah ahiye! tin asei lhon’e.
\v 8 Chule Pathen hi eiho dinga hiche gamsung khu eiphatsah peh uva ahileh, Pakai chun agamsunga ei puilut uvin tin eipeh diu ahi. Hiche gam chu gam phatah ahin khoiju le bongnoi lonna gam ahiye.
\v 9 Pakai chu douhih un, chule hiche gamsunga chengte jong kicha hih un. Eiho a dingin amaho khu apanpi ding umlou anchah a pang tobangbep ahiuve! Avengtup ding anei pouvin, hinlah Pakai chu eiho toh um ahi. Amaho khu kicha hih un!” \x + \xo 14:9 \xt Heb 3:16\x*
\v 10 Amavang mipi jouse chun Joshua le Caleb chu songa selih ding agong tauvin ahi. Chutah chun Houbuh a Israel te chungah Pakai loupina chu ahung kilah tan ahi.
\s1 Mose amite dia ataona
\p 
\v 11 Chuin Pakaijin Mose jah ah, “Hiche mite hin itih chan nahsah louva eikoi diu hitam? Alah uva thil kidang tampi kaboldoh nunga jong ei tahsan louhel diu hitam?
\v 12 Keiman amaho chu kapai uva chule natse a kasuh mang diu ahi. Ahinlah keiman nangma hi alenjo leh thahatjo a kasem ding nahi! ati.
\v 13 Ahinlah Mose anompoi. “Egypt miten hiche thil um dan hi ahet teng ule ipi agel diuvem?” tin Mose’n Pathen chu adong tai. Egypt a konna nangman na thahatna a Israel mite nahin puidoh a na huhdoh chu ahetchen u ahiye.\x + \xo 14:13 \xt Potdohbu 32:11-14\x*
\v 14 Tua Nangman hiche Israel mite hi na suhmang leh Egypt miten agam'a cheng ho lah a alhut diu, nangma toh kimaito ahiuvin chule jan teng meikonga napuiyun sun teng meilhang in na pui jiuve.
\v 15 Pakai nangman amaho hi ilou theh a na suhmang leh hiche nam mite na puidan kidangtah ana hesa nam mite chun sei uvin tin,
\v 16 'Pakaiyin amaho gamthip noiya asuhgamna ajeh chu ateppeh nau gamsung chu apuilhung jou tahlou jeh ahi,' ati diu ahi.
\v 17 “Pakai, lungset tah in, nangman nasei bangin na thaneina chu vetsah kit in. Nasei bangin,
\v 18 'Pakai hi lunghang vahlou chuleh ngailutna a dim jing ahi. Hinlah themmona nei mi mohvet lou ahi. Ama chu minu le mipa te chonsetna jeh a achate akhang thum le akhang li geiya gotji ahi.' \x + \xo 14:18 \xt Potdohbu 20:5,6; 34:6,7; Danbu Ni Na 5:9,10; 7:9,10\x*
\v 19 Na milungsetna nasatah, thon ngailou ngailutna chun lungset tah in hiche mite chonsetna ho hi Egypt ahin dalhah uva na ngaidam ji bangin ngaidam in.”
\v 20 Hichun Pathen’in aseijin, “Nangma ngehna bangin ngaidam tang’e,” ati.
\v 21 Hinlah Keima Kahin jing banga vannoi leiset hi ka loupina dim jing ding, \x + \xo 14:21 \xt Heb 3:18\x*
\v 22 hiche mite ho lah a hi koima jong ka teppehna gam lhung jou talou diu ahi. Ajeh chu amaho jousen ka loupina chu ahetsoh hel’u ahin, chule thil kidangtah melchihna Egypt gam’a chule gamthip lah a kabolin, ahinlah ama hon ka thusei angainom pouvin avel vellin eipatep uve.
\v 23 Keiman apute apateu ka teppehna gam chu itih hijongleh amu louhel diu ahi. Amaho lah a koi tobang eidou dal ho jouse chun imacha amu louhel ding ahi.
\v 24 Ahinlah ka lhachapa Caleb vang hi midang hotoh lunggel kibah louna aum'e. Caleb hin homtho tah in eihou jingin hiti ahijeh a chu agam kholna mun'a chu kapui lhung tei ding ahi, Caleb le achilhah te jousen hiche gam chu aboncha a alo soh hel diu ahi. \x + \xo 14:24 \xt Joshua 14:9-12\x*
\v 25 Tun nangma kiheile inlang, nangman Amalek mite le Canan mite ho chenna lang chu na jot louding ahi. Jing tengleh nangma kipatdoh in gamthip lam jon'a Twipi San langkaiya chu nakitol diu ahi,” ati.
\s1 Akiphin Ho Thi Dia Kithutep
\p 
\v 26 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron henga hiti hin aseiyin,
\v 27 “Hiche migilou nam leh ka chunga kiphin jing mite hi itih chan ka khongai jou ding ham? Henge, keima douna a akiphin jingu hi kajai.
\v 28 Tun amaho chu hiche hi seipeh un: Pakaijin aphongdoh in, Keima kahin jing banga nangman nasei chu kajan kaboldoh tei ding ahi.
\v 29 Nangho nabon uva gamthip a thiden ding nahi tauve! Ajehchu keima douna a kiphin, kum som nia pat chunglam sen thina ato ding ahi, ati. \x + \xo 14:29 \xt Heb 3:17\x*
\v 30 Katepna gamsung nalo tahlou diu, Jephunneh chapa Caleb le Nun chapa Joshua amani bou chun alo lhon ding ahi.
\v 31 Ahinlah nachate khangthah ho nang hon mi thagam ding bep a nagel hou chu keiman kapanpi ding agam leiset nadeimo sau gam chu atoupha diu ahi.
\v 32 Amavang nangho jouse na thilong uchu hiche gamthip nelgam a hi kivui lhum ding ahitai.
\v 33 Chule na chateu chu kelngoiching ho bang diu, gamthip noiya kum somli le li vahle diu ahi. Hitobang’a chu na kitahlou nau namu diu, hiche gamthip a hi nalah uva achaina pen jong thi a lum ding ahiye. \x + \xo 14:33 \xt Act 7:36\x*
\v 34 “Ijeh inem itileh, na lamkai hon nisomli jen lutna gam leiset kholla cheuva ahin na chonset jeh a kisu genthei ding nahitai nikhat lampi chu kum somli jen na jot dingu ahitai. Hiche teng chule nang hon Pathen toh melma a um hi itobang’a hahsa ham ti nahet doh diu ahi.
\v 35 Keima, Pakaijin kasei ahitai! Hiche mipi ho lah a eidou’a pang jing ho chu suh gentheiya umdiu ahi. Amaho chu hiche gamthip a hi kisumang diu, chule hilaiya hi thi diu ahi!”hinkho kicha soh hel diu ahi.
\v 36 Pasal som ho Mosen gamve lhi dinga asol Pakai douna a thu hinlhutpa ho chu
\v 37 Pakai angsunga pul in adengun athi tauve.
\v 38 Gam kholchin lah a pasal somle ni lah achun Joshua le Caleb bou asohcha lhonin ahi.
\s1 Gamla Din Akinim Vamphet Tauve
\p 
\v 39 Mose’n Pakai thucheng seidoh jouse chu Israel ho lah a aseipeh phat chun mipi ho chun nopmo asah thei lheh jengun ahi.
\v 40 Amaho chu ajing jingkah matah in aki thou un mol chungvum laitah a akaldoh un ahi. Amahon “Cheu hite,” atiuve. Pathen dounan ichonse tauve, ti ikihetdoh tauvin, hijeh chun tunvang Pakaijin eiteppeh nau gam chu jontau hite, akitiuve.
\v 41 Ahinlah Mose’n aseijin, “Ibola nanghon Pakai thupeh palkeh a gamthip a kile ding na kisah u baham? Phachom ponte.
\v 42 Tun hiche gam lam’a lut ding jong gotda tauvin. Na melmateu khut a naki suhchip bep diu ahi ajeh chu Pakaijin naumpi tapouve.
\v 43 Nanghon Amalek mite le Canaan mite toh nakidinte tengu leh, ama hon na satchop gamhel diu ahitai. Pakai nana dalhah tah jeh uva Pakaijin nangho jong na dalhah u ahitai.
\v 44 Hinlah Mose jong pang lou, Pakai thingkong jong jao talouhel in mipi chun thinglhang lam chu mano in atum tentun uvin ahi.
\v 45 Hichun molchung lam a pansan Amalek mite leh Canaan miten ahin bulhu tauvin hiti chun Hormah chan ahin del tauvin ahi.
\c 15
\s1 Anneh Thilto Leh Kilhanna Bol Ding Dan Thupeh
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin,
\v 2 “Keiman kapeh nau gam leiset mun chu na lhun teng uleh Israel mite chu hiche thuhil ho hi seipeh in,
\v 3 Nangman pumgo maichamn thiltoh gimnam tuisel Pakai henga napeh ding ahiye. Na gancha hon bong, kelngoi hon lah chule kelchal ho lah ajong ahoi cheh pumgo maicham thilto kumlhun sih a kibol banga chu napeh diu ahiye.
\v 4 Nangma hiche maicham ho hi bol ding tia nagel teng Pakai chu mim le changa konna changbong chu gopni hi ding chule Olive thao chu Hopkhat hi ding ahi.
\v 5 Kelngoi chu khat pumgo maicham thiltoa nakat diu pumgo maicham thil tona dia lengpitwi jong hop khat maicham nahinto ding ahi.
\v 6 Pumgo thilto chu kelngoi ahile changbong kipe dol chu gal a Pakaiya dinga gimnam tuitah hi ding ahiye.
\v 7 Chule lengpi thei twi chu khon thum tobang twija maicham din sem in hichu Pakaiya dinga gimnam tuitah ahi.
\v 8 Nangman bongchal nou pumgo maicham thilto nabol teng Pakaiya dia kipana maicham kisuh thengna nabolji ding,
\v 9 nangman mim le changbonga kisem hop gup napeh ding chule Olive thao jaona hop ni hi ding,
\v 10 chule nangman hopni lengpitwi napeh ding hichu Pakaiya dia gimnam tuitah hi ding ahi.
\v 11 Hiche maicham jouse aboncha kelchal, Kelpi, Kelnou, chule adang jong hitia chu na bolsohkei diu ahi.
\v 12 Nangman pumgo thilto napeh teng hiche thupeh ho hi najui ding ahi.
\v 13 Nangho Israel mite hiche mun a peng jousen Pakai henga gimnamtui maicham napeh teng ule hiche thupeh ho hi najui’u angaiye.
\v 14 Koi tobang nangho kom'a kholjin mi aum ham ahilouleh acheng den aum khah jongleh amaho jong chun hiche dan hi ajui cheh diu ahi.
\v 15 Israel mite agam leiset mun'a peng den hihen gampam a kon hung pemlut mi hijongleh Pakai mitmua thakhat cheh ahiuve. Hijeh a chu Dan khat noija um cheh ahiuve. Hiche hi nangho dia tonsotna jui dinga dan kisem ahin hichu najui diuva kipe ahitai.
\v 16 Nangho ding hihen gamchom mi hung pemlut ho hiu jongleh hiche thupeh jui ding’a kigong ho hi nabol cheh diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:16 \xt Thempu Dan 24:22\x*
\v 17 Pakaiyin Mose hengah aseijin,
\v 18 Israel te chu anoija thupeh ho hi seipeh tan. Nangho kapehna gam nalhun uva,
\v 19 hiche gamsung gasoh ho naneh teng ule Pakai maicham ding jong na khin doh cheh cheh diu ahi.
\v 20 Na lousoh mim le chang aga masapen chu changbong a nasuhdi ding changlhah lum a nasem ding hichu Pathen a dinga ga masapen ahijeh a napeh doh ding ahi.
\v 21 Ahunglhung ding khonung khang geija hiche maicham atheng Pathen henga pehdoh ding hi akumsih leh najui ding na lou gasoh amasapen chu na koidoh jing ding ahiye.
\s1 Hetkhel Jeh a Chonsetna Aum Teng Jui Ding Danpi
\p 
\v 22 I-ham tia Pakaiyin Mose henga athupeh chengse hi nahsahmo jeh hilouva, hetthem lou jeh joh a na suhmil khah uva,
\v 23 khonung’a na chilhah ho jengin jong Pakai thupeh ho asuhmil khah uva,
\v 24 hiche suhkhelna chu mipi jousen ana hetthem lou jeh ahi khah tah leh Israel mipi te chun bongchal nou khat Pakai heng’a gimnamtui thilto dia ato diu ahi. Chuleh Anneh ding thilto leh don ding thilto toh chonset thilto adia kelnou khat ato tha diu ahi.
\v 25 Hiche ho jouse toh hin thempu pan Israel mipi ho chu Pakai masang’a asuhtheng ding chuteng amaho chu ngaidam a um diu ahi. Ajeh chu ama hon achonset nau chu ana hetlou jeh u ahin, a maicham thilto jal uva kingaidam diu ahi. Pathen heng’a chonset thilto leh kilhaina abol jal uva chu ngaidam kichan diu ahi.
\v 26 Israel mipite leh gampam mi abonchauva ngaidam a um nahi tauve.
\v 27 Koi tobang khat in hetthem louva chonsetna ahin bol tah leh, amapa chun kelpi kumkhat lhingset khat a chonset thilto ahin todoh ding ahi. \x + \xo 15:27 \xt Thempu Dan 4:27-31\x*
\v 28 Thempu chun hiche pasal chu Pakai masanga asuhtheng ding chuteng amapa chu ngaidam a um ding ahitai.
\v 29 Hiche thuhil hin nangma ho Israel chilhah ho nahiuvin chule midang nagam uva khopem ho jouse jong ahop sohkei ahi.
\s1 Henasasa a Chonset Gotna Danpi
\p 
\v 30 Hinlah nangho lah a koitobang ahenasa a Pakai deilam bollou vang chu Pakai taitom kiti ding chule amaho chu Israel te lah a pat a chomkhen’a um ding ahiuve.
\v 31 Ama hon Pakai thupeh chu henasa a khohsah louva akoitah jeh un amaho jouse chu pum noa nomang ding ahi tauve chule achonset nau jeh a gim gentheina athoh diu ahi.
\s1 Sabbath Nitlou Jeh a Gotna Danpi
\p 
\v 32 Israel mite nikhat gamthip a akhosah laitah uchun mipi ho chun pasal khat in Sabbath nikhoa na atoh a thing achom pettah ahin tohkha tauvin ahi.
\v 33 Israel te lah a pasalpa thilbol mudoh jouse chun amapa chu Mose le Aaron chule mipi lah ahin puiyun ahi.
\v 34 Ama hon ipi lo ding ham atheilou jeh uvin munkhat a aumsah un ahi.
\v 35 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose chu ahoulimpi tan, “Hiche pa chu thina channa gotna chang ding ahi! Ama chu khopi pam lam a mipin song’a ase lih ding ahi,” ati.
\v 36 Hichun mipin amapa chu ngahmun pam lam’a akaidoh un songin aseplih tauve, hichu Pakaiyin Mose henga thu apeh bang banga abol’u ahi.
\s1 Kivonna Dan
\p 
\v 37 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseiyin,
\v 38 Israel te chu anoiya thucheng kihilna ding ho hi seipeh kit tan. Aponmang jouseu chu alum khat aba diu, alum lai chu ajem adum a nabol diu, hichu akhang akhanga akivon diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:38 \xt Danbu Ni Na 22:12\x*
\v 39 “Nangman hiche pon mangjem chu namu teng na Pakai thupeh sang’a tahsa ngaichatna joh nasuh bukim nomlouna diu ahi” ati.
\v 40 Hiche pon dum chun thupeh jui ding’a umho chu nahin geldoh sah diu Pathen atheng’a umpa toh na kinai sah jing diu ahi, ati.
\v 41 Keima Pakai na Pathen Egypt gam'a konna nahin puidoh pa chu kahi. Keima na Pakai na Pathen kahi!”
\c 16
\s1 Mose Leh Aaron Douna a Kiphinna
\p 
\v 1 Nikhat chun Izhar chapa Korah, ama chu Levi phunga kon Kohath insungmi ahin, ama chun Reuben phung’a kon mi akitep khomin, hiche teni chu Dathan le Abiram, amani chu Eliab chate ahin, chule Peleth chapa On jaonan, \x + \xo 16:1 \xt Jde 1:11\x*
\v 2 Israel chilhah jouse phung lamkai 250 jaonan Mose doumah in achon tauve.
\v 3 Amaho jouse thakhat tah in lungkhat in apang khom un Mose le Aaron henga hitin asei tauve. “Pakai mite dang ho sangin lenjo lhon jong lechun ipi bolna ding thaneina nanei lhon em?” tin asei uve.
\v 4 Mose’n amaho thusei ajah phat chun akaiku jeng tan ahi.
\v 5 Hichun Mose’n Korah te nungjui ho lah a chun hitin aseitai, jing teng Pakaiyin eihetsah diu ahi koi ho hi ama chate hiham tichu hetdohna um ding ahi.
\v 6 Vo Korah nangma nahin na nungjui ten jing teng maicham thaomei halna chu nahin kichoi diu ahi, ati.
\v 7 Chuteng Pathen masanga koi chu a thengjo ham ti chu ivet diu ahitai. Veuvin Levi chate ho nangho joh in nabol khel tauve, ati.
\v 8 Chuin Mose’n Korah henga asei in, Levi te insung injong ngai un,
\v 9 Pathen chun Israel mipi te lah a na lhendoh uva, ama jen ding leh akintheng natoh tong ding’a na ngense uhi, thil neocha a ngaito nahiu ham? ati.
\v 10 Korah, Pathen'in hitobang kintheng tong dia na sopite’u Levi te toh na ngense jinglai uva themputna jong na holbe uva na ngaichat nahlai diu ham?
\v 11 Nangho hin na doudal pentah uchu midang ahipon Pathen chu ahi bouve, Aaron chu koi nahisah uva ama chung chang’a lungphatmona na vetsah jing uham?
\v 12 Hichun Mose’n Eliab chateni Dathan le Abiram chu akou lhonin, ahinlah amanin adonbut lhonin, “Na masanga hung ding kanompoi! ati lhon'e.
\v 13 Egypt gamsung khoiju le bongnoi lonna gam'a patna eihin puidoh uva, hikom nelgam a thidoh dinga eikou uva tuchan geija keiho chunga lengpa vaipoh banga eipo jingu hi nang nahilou ham?
\v 14 Ipi seibe ding um nalaija ham? Nangman khoiju leh bongnoi lonna gam natina a lah neipui hih laiyun, keiho chenna ding gam la neipe pouvin, honlei lhosohga konna ding gam lah aumpon, mingol bolla bol jing ding neigot nahlai uham? atiuve.
\v 15 Chuin Mose chu nasatah in alunghang tan Pakai henga hitin aseije, “Alhosoh thilto’u sanpeh hih in! Amaho a konin thil neocha khat jong kalah aumpon, chule mi khat jengcha jong kasuhnat khah louhel’u ahi.”
\v 16 Chuin Mose’n Korah kom'a hitin aseijin jing nikho teng nangma nahin, na nungjui jouse hilai mun'a nahung kikhop cheh diu, Pakai masanga nadin diu, Aaron jong hikom'a hi hung ding ahi.
\v 17 Nangma nahin na nungjui mi jani le somnga ho jouse chun gimnamtui halnamna ding thaomei chu Pakai masang’a ahin kichoi cheh diu, Aaron thempu pan jong ama gimnamtui maicham halna ding ahin kichoiya hung ding ahi, ati.
\v 18 Chuin amaho jousen maicham meihalna chu akilah cheh un, meikong chu ahal'un Houbuh lutna phol lam a maicham phunga chun Mose le Aaron jong ading khom lhon’e.
\v 19 Hiche phat don laitah chun Korah in mipi tamtah ahin tildoh tan Mose le Aaron gotna pe dingin amaho jouse chu Houbuh maicham leitol lutna laitah a chun aki hom khom tauvin ahi. Hiche Pakai loupina chu mipi holah a hatah in ahung kilangdoh tan,
\v 20 chuin Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron henga thu aseijin,
\v 21 Mipi ho lah a kon'in kinung khindoh lhon tan ajeh chu amaho hi abonchauva gangtah a ka suhmang ding ahitai.
\v 22 Amavang Mose le Aaron chu tollham a amai anga lhon tan, O Pakai ati lhonin atao lhon tai. Pakai, Pathen nangma hinna nei jouse sempa chu nahi. Mikhat chonsetna jeh mai maiya mijouse na suhgam jeng ding hitam? ati lhon e.
\v 23 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseiyin,
\v 24 chuti ahileh mipi ho chu seipeh tan, Korah ahin, Dothan chuleh Abiram Houbuh a konna kichon doh dingin seipeh in, ati.
\v 25 Chuin Mose chu ading doh in Israel Upa ho jaona in, Dothan le Abiram kingahna mun a ponbuh lam achun alhai tauvin ahi.
\v 26 Mose’n mipi ho kom'a chun gangtah in hiche migilou ho henga pat chun kikhin doh un chule nangman amaho thil ho jouse na tham khah louding, na tham khah le achonset jeh uva gotna nachan thei diu ahi.
\v 27 Hichun mipi jouse chu Dothan le Abiram chule Korah khoilu pon in a kon'in akikhin doh tauvin ahi. Hichun Dothan, Abiram le ajite ho ahiuvin achate ho jouse jaonan khoilu ponbuh kisahna leitol a ahungun ahi.
\v 28 Chuin Mose’n aseijin, Pakaiyin eihin sol lona pentah katoh kabol ding ho hi keima chang’a kabol theilou ahi.
\v 29 Hiche miho hi thi ngaina a athi uva, kivui ngai bang’a akivui poupou uleh, kei hi Pakai hinsol kahi lou himai hen.
\v 30 Ahinlah iham tia Pakaijin thilsoh thah khat abol leh leiset in akam akah a amaho chu anei agou jouseu toh aval lhum diu, chuleh kotong sung’a chu khelut ding’u ahi. Chuteng chuleh hite ho hin Pakai alunghan sah tauve tihi nahet doh thei diu ahitai ati.
\v 31 Mose’n hiche thucheng ho seichai man loulaijin, leiset chu ahung pohkeh in amaho noilam a chun ajoplha gam tauve.
\v 32 Korah mite jouse jong aloi agol ho chuleh anei agou abonchauvin hiche leivui chun akam akah in abonchauvin avallhum sohhe ltai.
\v 33 Hichun amaho ahing lai pum in lhankhuh chu ajon tauvin anei agou hou jouse toh avuh khum tha tauve, chule amaho jouse chu Israel mipi te chilhah a kon'in agamla ahi tauve.
\v 34 Mipi avel’a um jouse chun amaho ka-le-mao awgin ajah phat un atija lheh jengun; “Eiho jong leiset hin eival lhum diu ahitai” atiuve.
\v 35 Pathen a kon'in mei ahung kong in, pasal jani le somnga chu ahalvam soh tai.
\v 36 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin,
\v 37 Aaron thempupa chapa Eleazar seipeh tan, amaho atheng ahijeh uchun kipat untin gimnamtui kihalna lhengkong ho chu mei-am lah a kon'in loidoh henlang, a mei-am ho jong chu thaijah tauhen,
\v 38 hiche ahing’a chonset bol hon amanchah kilhaina lhengkong ho chu chomkhom uvin lang, maicham khuna ding asin in sem un, ajeh chu ama hon Pakai lhaina dia atodoh sau ahin athenga kisim ahi. Chuleh hiche thilsoh hi Israel chate adin melchihna hi jing hen.
\v 39 Hichun Eleazar thempu pan mi meiyin akahvamho sum-eng lhengkong ho chu achom khom in, maicham phun khutupna sinkha din akheng tai.
\v 40 Hiche hin Israel mite jouse asuhchih ding, koi hita jongleh nganse’a um Aaron insung mite hilou chun Pathen angsung’a gimnamtui hal dia lut lou diu ahi. Ajuilou chu Korah leh achilhah te banga um ding ahi tihi Pakaijin Mose kom'a aseisa ahitai.
\s1 Mipi ho Kiphin
\p 
\v 41 Ahinlah ajing nikhon Israel mite chun Mose le Aaron chu a oimo pan kit tauvin, “Nang nin Pakai mite nathat lhon’e” atiuve.
\v 42 Hiti chun mipite ho chun Mose le Aaron doudalna a, Houbuh sung ano khum kigot laitah un Pakai loupina chu ahung kilang doh in, meibol in ahin tom tai.
\v 43 Mose le Aaron chu ahung lhon tan Houbuh masang’a ading lhon tan ahi.
\v 44 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseijin ahi.
\v 45 Hitobang mihem ho lah a kon'in kikhindoh lhon tan keiman amaho abonchauva ka suhgam diu ahitai. Mose le Aaron chu tol’ah abohkhup lhon tai.
\v 46 Chuin Mose’n Aaron kom'a aseijin nangman gangtah in maicham mei khat chu la inlang, Houbuh maicham sem inlang amaho din Pakai toh kihoucham loijin, ajeh chu gamna hise akipan tai.
\v 47 Aaron in Mose seibang chun abolin mipi te lah achun alhai lut in, gimnamtui ahal in mipi ho a din kilhaina abol in, alangsa gamna hise chu suh tang dingin agoi.
\v 48 Aaron chun mihem athi leh ahingho kikah ah palaijin adingin hichun pul chu atang tai.
\v 49 Ahinlah pasal sangsom-le-sangli leh jasagi chu athigamhel man tan hichu Korah chung chang jeh a thi ho kisim thalou ahi.
\v 50 Thina hise chu atan phat in, Aaron jong Houbuh lutna kom'a Mose heng lam chu ahin jon tan ahi.
\c 17
\s1 Tenggol Pahdoh
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseijin,
\v 2 “Israel mipi henga seijin, ama hon tenggol som le ni hin kisem uhen, insung leh aphungkhai cheh uvin khat cheh kisem uhenlang, aphung lamkai min cheh hin kisut sohkei uhen.
\v 3 Phung lamkai khat min cheh chu kijihlut ding ahijeh in Aaron min chu Levi te phung lamkai ding chun sunin.
\v 4 Hiche tenggol ho hi Houbuh sunga Kitepna songpheng ho kikoina Thingkhong masanga ikimutona mun a chun koijin.
\v 5 Keiman kalhen mipa Tenggol chunga chu ajihdon hung um ding ahi. Chuteng na chunga mipi kiphinna le phunchelna chu achaina kahisah ding ahitai.
\v 6 Hichun Mose’n Israel mipi chu hilchahna aneiyin chule Israel phungsom le ni lamkai ho jouse jong chu Aaron tenggol jong chu ahin choiyun ahi.
\v 7 Pakai umpina Houbuh sunga Kitepna achun Mosen tenggol ho chu akoitai.
\v 8 Mose chu ajingin Houbuh sung’a chun agalut a ahileh Levi te insung thakhel dia Aaron tenggol chu ana dondoh in, amum aum in, apahlha in, Jonmot ga minsa ana um tai! \x + \xo 17:8 \xt Heb 9:4\x*
\v 9 Mose’n tenggol jouse chu Pakai masanga ahin choidoh cheh in, aman hiche ho jouse chu mipi ho chu avetsah sohkeiye. Mijousen ama ama phungkhai tenggol chu akilah cheh uvin ahi.
\v 10 Chule Pakaijin Mose jah ah: Aaron tenggol chu Kitepna Thingkong chung’a chu a-itih a natun jing ding ahi, Hiche chu miphalou ho hilna a pang’a, Pakai douna a akiphin’u ajom ngam tahlouna diu leh a thilhamji nauva kon ahoidohna diuva hettohsah a pang jing ding ahi, ati.
\v 11 Chuti chun Mose’n jong Pakaijin ahil bang bang chun aboltan ahi.
\v 12 Israel mipi ten Mose kom'a hitin asei uvin: “Ven, keiho pihi amang thah ding bep a um kahi tauve. Keiho athisa kahi tauve, keiho akichai gam ding kahi tauve!
\v 13 Koihileh Pakai maicham nailut chan athi, athi chai ding bep kahiu hitam? ati tauve.
\c 18
\s1 Thempuho leh Leviho Mopohnaho
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Aaron heng'ah thu aseijin, nangma nahin na chapa te ahin, na insunga Levi te chilhah hon na boncha uva muntheng sung’a boina le suhkhel jouse chung’a mo napoh diu ahi. Chuleh Thempu natoh na chung chang’a mopohna jouse vang nang leh na chapa te chung’a bou chu ding ahi,” ati.
\v 2 “Na phung chanpi Levi chate ho chu nang leh na chapa te toh Houbuh sung’a kithokhom dingin hin puijin lang hungun, Kitepna Thingkong maija natoh diu kin hung tongpan tauvin,” ati.
\v 3 Ahin Levi te vang chu Houbuh maichama natonga ache teng ule, amaho chu ching thei tah a aum uva na atoh u angaije. Maicham muntheng lam'a thilkeo ho kom anailut loudiu ahi. Hiche ho chu atham khah tah uva ahile nangma nahin, na sopi ho abonna nathi sohhel diu ahi.
\v 4 Levi te tia kiminsah jouse Houbuh maicham semna natohna jousea jao cheh diu ahinlah midang vang nangma toh natong’a nakithopi dinga pang thei louding ahi.
\v 5 Houbuh maicham kintheng sunga natong, akimang cha ding ho ahin nangman hiche thupeh jouse hi chingthei tah a najui uleh Pakai lunghanna nangho Israel te chunga um kit talou ding ahi.
\v 6 Keima tah in Israel te lah a Levi te na natoh khompi ka lhendoh peh nahi. Amaho jouse chu nangma dia hung kipedoh diu Houbuh maicham a Pakai kintheng natong ding ahiuve.
\v 7 Ahinlah nangma nahin na chate jouse vang hiche kintheng maicham thempu natoh kiti jouse nang hon na tahsa tah uva nabol diu ahiye. Chuleh maicham phol sunga thil kimsel'a pondal nung lam’a um jouse jong jaona ahi. Keiman nangma hi atumtah a themputna natoh kapeh nahi. Koihileh hetpehna umlou mihem chun muntheng aganaival a ahileh thi ding ahi.”
\s1 Thempu Ho Chan Ding Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 8 Pakai thupeh jouse hi Aaron henga seipeh in hiche kinthenga Israel miten ahinto hou chu vetup dinga kinganse nahitai. Nangma nahin na chate ahin kinthenga hung kitohdoh jousea hi mopo jing ding nahi tauve.
\v 9 Meiya halvam louding thilto thengpen ho a chu mopo ding nahiuve. Hiche thilto thengpen ho chu – lhosoh thilto ho, chonset thilto ho, chule themmona thilto thengpen ho, chule hiche ho chu nang leh na chapa te chan ding ahi.
\v 10 Nangman hiche thilto thengpen chu naneh ding ahi. Pasal jousen aneh diu, hichu athengpen a nalah diu ahi.
\v 11 Israel miten maicham kintheng ahung kitoh jouse aboncha a nangma a hi ding ahi. Hiche ho jouse chu aboncha a na chanu te leh na chapa te jousen gouva na neiden diuva ka pehdoh ahitai. Na insung mite jouse koi hijongleh houdan a kisutheng jousen hiche maicham a hung kitohdoh jouse aneh thei cheh diu ahi.
\v 12 Keiman nangma hi mipiten lhosoh maicham Pakaiya ahin todoh jouseu - Olive thao, lengpitwi athah, chule lhosohga toh kapeh nahiuve.
\v 13 Gamsunga louga ahunglhung masa Pakaiya dia mipi hon ahinto jouse aboncha nangma ding ahi. Na insunga akisutheng jousen hiche maicham a hung kitoh doh jouse chu anehthei diu ahi.
\v 14 Israel gamsunga Pakai maicham adia hung kichom khindoh jouse aboncha a nangma nachan ding ahi. \x + \xo 18:14 \xt Thempu Dan 27:28\x*
\v 15 Minu a konna ahung pengdoh masa mihem a kon hihen gancha a kon hijongleh Pathen a dinga hung kipedoh jouse chu nangma a ding ahi. Ahinlah nangman nacha ahung pen masa chule hou thudol'a atheng loulai gancha jouse chu na lhatdoh jing ding ahiye.
\v 16 Amaho chu lhakhat ahung lhing tengleh na lhatdoh ding ahi. Hiche ho lhatdohna ding jat chu sum-eng peh nga hiding (inthenga thil tena dungjuiya shekel somni hiding, hichu gerah somni toh kibang ahi).
\v 17 Ahinlah, nangman kelcha, kelngoi chule bongnou apeng masa pentah ho chu na lhatdoh louding ahi. Hiche ho chu Pakai dia kichomkoi atheng ahi tauve. Athisan chu maicham a thekhum inlang, athao chu thilto hoitah kipe in meiya halvam in, agimnam chun Pakai alunglhai sah ding ahi.
\v 18 Thilpeh hoitah maicham a sa hin kitohdoh a omlhang le ajetlang mal chu nanga ding ahitai.
\v 19 Pakai henga Israel miten ahin todoh thilto theng ho hi Keiman nangma kapeh nahitai. Hiche ho hi nangma le na chapa te na chanu te chan hijing ding ahi.Hiche kitepna hi Pakai le nangma kikah a kitimatna akeh thei loubeh ding ahin, hichu na chilhah te jouse a ding jong ahi.”
\v 20 Chuin Pathen'in Aaron chu ahoulimpi tan, nangho thempu hon Israel mipi te toh gambeh hihen nei le gou kipehto na bollou dingu ahi. Keima hi nanei nagou u chu kahi, ati.
\s1 Levi Ho Chan ding Hopsom
\p 
\v 21 Nangma insung mite naphung chan khompi Levi te chun Houbuh maicham natoh ho jouse chu keima gam leiset anei khel uva Israel mipia konna gam leiset a konna hopsom kipe ding ahi. \x + \xo 18:21 \xt Thempu Dan 27:30-33; Danbu Ni Na 14:22-29\x*
\v 22 Tu apat Israel chilhah hijeng jongleh Levi phung chule thempu tilou koima chan Houbuh kom aphah theilou diu ahi. Amaho chun kinai tah a jong ahin nailut lou diu, ahin nailut uva ahileh thepmo chang ding’u chule thilo ding ahiuve.
\v 23 Levi te chilhah hon bou Houbuh mun'a na atoh thei dingu, chule iti ham khatna boina aum leh ama hon mopohna anei ding’u ahi. Hichu nangma dia a itih a jui ding’a longlou ding dan kipe ahi. Levi ten Israel te lah a gam aneilou diu,
\v 24 ajeh chu keiman Israel te chu hopsom kapeh sah ding, hichu ama hon maicham thenga ahin peh dingu ahi. Hiche ho jouse hi Levi te chanvou ding ahin ajeh chu Levi ten gamtum achombeh a anei theilou diu ahi.
\s1 Levi Te Hopsom Peh Ding Dan
\p 
\v 25 Pakaiyin jong Mose aseipeh in,
\v 26 Levi te chu hiche ho hi hetsah in; Israel mipite hopsom todoh ho chu keiman kana seipeh nang hon chanvou nasan dingu chu ahi. Hijeh a chu nanghon hiche ho chu hopsom a hopkhat napeh diu, som a khat a konna som a khat chu Pakaiya thilto theng ahi.
\v 27 Pakaijin hiche maicham na hin todoh ho chu nangma lou gasoh nato bang uva asim ding, na changphol a kivolha masa pen ahilouleh na Lengpitwi lhohlhah masapen bang’a asan ding ahi.
\v 28 Israel ten Pakaiya thil theng ahinto hou chu som a khat napeh ding ahi. Hiche hi Pakaiya dinga atheng chu ahin, chule hiche chu Aaron thempu napeh ding ahi.
\v 29 Thilpeh nakipeu chu nang hon jong Pakai chu apha pentah napeh teitei diu ahi.
\v 30 Chule hiche thupeh najui dinga kilom ho Levi te seipeh tan nangman na maicham ahoi pentah ho nahinto tengleh hiche ho chu nangma lousohga ahilou le nangma lengpilei laiya bang tah a naki simpeh ding ahiye.
\v 31 Levi te jouse nangma nahin na sopi na insung mijouse hiche na ankong hi hoikom hijongleh naneh thei cheh diu ahi. Ajeh chu Pathen Houbuh maicham na natoh jeh uva ahi.
\v 32 Thempu ho hi aphapen tah napeh leh Pakaiya dinga hopsom a hung kitoh chu naneh chun themmo nachan louding ahi. Ahinlah nangma chingtheiyin Israel miten thil theng tah ahin todoh hou chu imacha thenglou tah in geldan imacha na geldao khah le na thilo jeng thei ahiye.
\c 19
\s1 Kisuhthengna Twi
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseijin,
\v 2 Pakaijin dan thupeh aneiyin Israel mite seipeh un bongchal nou asan khat, tibah bukimsel natong khalou khat hi ding ahi.
\v 3 Hiche bongnou san chu Eleazer thempu chu petan chuteng ngahmun pamlam'a Eleazer thempupa masanga natha diu ahi.
\v 4 Eleazer thempu pan gan thisan chu akhutna anumat a Pakai Houbuh maicham masang lam'a sagi vei athe khum ding ahi.
\v 5 Eleazer thempupa chun hiche bongnou san chu athisan jaona a aboncha meiya ahalvam hel ding ahiye.
\v 6 Eleazer thempu chun cedar thing kha,t hyssop bah chule mojapat san themkhat chu alan bongnou meiya kihal lah achun aseplut in ahi.
\v 7 Chuteng thempu chun aponsil akisuh ngim ding twija kisil ngim ding, hiche ho akichai teng ngahmun'a hung kinung le ding kisuhthengna chu nilhah lam le anei thei ding ahi.
\v 8 Pasal koi tobang gancha gouvam a pang chun twija avon ho asoptheng selding ama tah jeng jong twiya kisil ngimsel ding chule nilhah khojin tokah a atheng louva um ding ahi.
\v 9 Chule koi tobang akisutheng sel'a umpa chun hiche bongnou chal asan chu achop khom'a, ngahmun pam muntheng lah a akoi tup ding, hiche meivam chu Israel miten kisuhthengna dia manchah dinga akikoi diu ahi. Hiche kintheng natohna ding hi chonset sopthengna a man chah ding ahi. \x + \xo 19:9 \xt Heb 9:13\x*
\v 10 Hiche pasal bongchal san kihalvamna aloh a pang pa chun avon jouse akisop theng cheh ding, chule nilhah khojin tokah geiya amapa chu aboh a um ding, hiche dan kisem hi Israel miten akhang akhanga ajui diu amaho lah a koitobang chidang namdang aching hon jong ajui cheh diu ahi.
\v 11 Koi hijongleh, thilong thamkha aum tah leh nisagi aboh a um ding ahi.
\v 12 Amaho chu hitobanga nithum le nisagi alhin teng twija kisuthenga um diu, amaho chu nisagi sunga chu akisuhtheng tahlou ule hapta khat le nisagi hung lhing tajongleh atheng louva um ding ahiuve.
\v 13 Koi hita jongleh mithilong atham khah tah a ahi ding lomtah akisuhtheng tah louleh Pakai Houbuh chu aja lou ahitan, amaho chu Israel mipi te lah a konna pampaija um diu ahi. Ajeh chu twi kithe khum a suhthengna aum tahlou jeh a achonsetna uva chu hitia chu kibol ahitai.
\v 14 Hiche danbu kisuhthengna dinga kisem hi hitia manchah ding, koi tobang ponbuh noija aum pettah uva ahung thi khah leh Houbuh sunga um jouse mithi longin adalpha chan chu nisagi atheng louva um jing diu ahi.
\v 15 Thilkeu kong le lheng ipi hita jongleh asin kisin loupetna kitung kha thil ponbuh sunga um jouse chu aboh a kisim ding ahi.
\v 16 Tollhang a um mihem long athisa ho, chemjam a kithat hihen, athikam hihen, mi thisa gu le chang ho hijongleh thamkha penpen chu nisagi sung’a aboh a um ding ahitai.
\v 17 Hiche mi kisubohpa suhtheng theina dia chu govam thilto a bongchal kigona vam chu nalah uva leibel a nakhum diu twitheng chu na sunkhum diu ahi.
\v 18 Chuteng aki subohlou mikhat chun Hyssop twi alah a twija adelut ding, hiche pa chun ponbuh ahin, bongbuh kiskonna jol ho ahin, ponbuh sung’a um miho ahin, mi thikam leh mithigu tongkha jouse ahin, ahilouleh lhan goh keu thamkha ho ham chu twitheng toh hyssop chu athin khum a asuhtheng ding ahi.
\v 19 Nithum lhinni jongleh athenga um jingpa chun aki suboh jouse chu athinkhum jing nahlai ding ahi. Nisagi alhinni leh akisuboh miho chu amaho leh amaho kisiltheng uva avon ho’u akisoptheng diu, abohna uva konna atheng hi diu ahitai.
\v 20 Ahinlah amaho lah a koi tobang aki suhbohna ho kisuh thenglou changse vang chu mipi lah a konna kichom khen ahi tauve. Ajeh chu ama hon Pakai Hou-In chu asuhboh u ahitai. Kisuhthengna dia twi kithin khum chu achung uva chukha talou ahijeh a, aboh a um jing ding ahi tauve.
\v 21 Hiche hi mipi ho dinga dan phat sottah a ding ahin koi hita jongleh twi kithe khum jouse jong avon le apon’u akisop theng cheh diu, koi tobang kisuhthengna twi thamkha aum jongleh nilhah lang geija atheng louva um ding ahiuve.
\v 22 Mihem hihen thilkeu hita jongleh akisuboh pan athamkhah jouse chu nilhah geija aboh a kisim ding ahi.
\c 20
\s1 Mosen songpi ajep
\p 
\v 1 Hiche kum lhamasa pen chun Israel mite Zin gamthip ahunglhung tauvin Kadesh mun'a akichol do uvin, hikom mun'a akicholdo laitah un Miriam chu athi’n hiche mun'a chun avui tauve.
\v 2 Hiche mun'a chun twi don ding aum tah lou jeh chun mipi ho chu Mose le Aaron dounan akiphin tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 20:2 \xt Potdohbu 17:1-7\x*
\v 3 Mipi ho chun Mose themmo achan un, hitin asei tauvin gamthip lah achun Pakai masanga kasopi teho toh ana thi khom taleuveng kanom uve, atiuve.
\v 4 Mose’n hiche Pathen chate mi hijat hi gamthip lah a athi chaikei ding’a keiho le ka gancha teu neipui uham, tin adong uve.
\v 5 Ipi dinga Egypt gam'a konna chu neihin puidoh uham hitobang gam leiset chavai tah mun ahi atiuve. Hiche leiset gampheng ahin agasoh jong aumpon, olive thei, kolbuthei chule lengpithei cha jong umlou chuleh twi don ding jong imacha aumpoi tin aseiyun ahi.
\v 6 Mose le Aaron chu mipi ho lah a kon'in aki nunghei lhon tan, Houbuh maicham jotna lam chu ahin nai lhon tai, hichun amani chu tolgo lam a amai asuto lhonin chuin Pakai mailhaisel kidangtah chu amani heng lamah ahung kilang doh in,
\v 7 chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng’a hiti hin aseijin,
\v 8 nang le Aaron in na tenggol lhon chu nachoi lhon ding Israel mipi chu aboncha nakhop tup lhon ding, mipi hon na umchan, nakhan chan lhon avet ding’u, songpi chu na thua na nunsah a na koudoh tho ding ahi. Chuteng twi don ding hung putdoh ding ahi. Nangman song chunga patna twi mipi te don ding kham na putdoh sah ding, mipi jouse chu na donva sah cheh diu ahi.
\v 9 Chuin Pakaiyin asei bang chun Mose’n jong aboltai. Aman Pakai masanga akikoina a konin atenggol chu alatan ahi.
\v 10 Hichun Mose le Aaron chun mipi chu songpi kom langa dingin akou lhon tai. Mose’n hitin asam tan, “Ngaijun sei ngailou milouchal ho! Songpi a konna hi twi kapotdoh sah lhon ding ham? ati.
\v 11 Chutah chun Mose’n akhut a tenggol chu adom sang'in songpi chu nivei ajep khum tan ahileh twi chu ahung kikhodoh tai. Hichun mipi jouse ahin gancha jousen jong adonva sohkei tauvin ahi.
\v 12 Ahinlah Pathen'in Mose le Aaron jah a aseijin nangni’n nei tahsan lhon hi alhing jou tapoi, Israel mipi hi ka themna namusah jou tapoi keiman ka teppeh nau gam leiset geija chu napuilut louding ahitai, ati.
\v 13 Hiche mun hi Meribah twi tin akihen (hichu “kinelna” tina ahi) hiche lai muntah ahin athenna chu akilangdoh deh in ahi.
\s1 Edom Galkaina Ding Kiphalpeh Lou
\m 
\v 14 Kadesh a Mose aum pet in Edom lengpa henga palai asolin hiche thu hi athot e:
\pmo 
\v 15 Ipateu Iputeu mi sagi phung lamkai ho Egypt gam lang nga ana kholjin un phat sottah jing jong ana khosa tauvin, pate pute ho jouse Egypt miten ana suh gam tahval uchu tin aseiye.
\v 16 Ahinlah keihon Pathen henglam kakou’un-ka mao-mao phat un Pakai, Pathen ama tah tah in eijah peh phat uva avantil eihin sol peh’uva Egypt a konna eihin pui doh’u ahi.
\v 17 Lungset tah in nagam sungah nei palsah un. Keihon chingthei tah a lam kajot diu mim le lengpi thei lah ka pallou diu ahi. Na twikhuh uva twi jeng jong kadonpa lou diu, nagam leiset ka dalhah kah sungse uva keiho lengpa lamlen lang bou kache diu ahi.
\b
\p 
\v 18 Ahinlah Edom lengpan hitin adonbut in, keima gamsunga kon'in kikhindoh un ahilouleh ka galsat hotoh ikimuto diu ahi! ati.
\v 19 Israel ten adonbut un, keiho lamlen a bou kaum diu ahi. Ka gancha teuvin twi adon ujongleh aman kapeh diu ahi. Na gamsung bou nei jotsah un. Hiche bou chu kangeh u ahi.” ati.
\v 20 Amavang Edom lengpan hitin ahin donbut in, “Kikhin doh un! Ka gamsung na hopa theilou diu ahi.” Hiche ahou lim jou chun agalsat hotoh akitolun Israel mite chu ano tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Ajehchu Edom in Israel ten agamsung ahopa diu anompon, Israel te chu hunam in akilehei sah tan ahi.
\s1 Aaron Thi
\p 
\v 22 Israel mipi chu Kadesh apatnin akinung le un Hor molsang chu alhung tauve.
\v 23 Chuin Edom gam ning lam ah chun Pathen'in Mose le Aaron heng'ah aseijin,
\v 24 Aaron dingin thina a apu apa tetoh akichol khomna ding phat ahunglhung tai. Keiman Israel te kapehna gam chu lut louding ahi, ajeh chu Meribah a twi chung changa ka thupeh dounan nangni na chon lhon tan ahi.
\v 25 Tun Aaron le achapa Eleazer chu Hor molsang lam ah puitou tan.
\v 26 Hiche mun a chu nangin Aaron athemputna von chu na sutlhah a achapa Eleazar na vonpeh ding ahi. Chumun’a chu Aaron thi ding apu apate toh kigom ding ahitai.
\v 27 Hichun Mose’n Pathen'in aseipeh bang tah chun abol tan ahi. Amaho thum chu Hor molchung lam'ah akaltou u mipin avetvin ahi.
\v 28 Molchung ah chun, Mose'n Aaron thempu von chu asutlhah peh in Aaron chapa Eleazer chu avonpeh tai. Chuti chun Aaron chu molchungah chun athi tan, chule Mose le Eleazer chu ahung nungkum lhon tai. \x + \xo 20:28 \xt Potdohbu 29:29; Minbu 33:38; Danbu Ni Na 10:6\x*
\v 29 Mipi hon Aaron athi tai ti ahetchen phat un, Israel miten ni somthum jen alunghempi tauvin ahi.
\c 21
\s1 Canaan Mite Chunga Galjona
\p 
\v 1 Negev a cheng Canaan mite lengpa Arad chun Israel miten Atharim ahin nai tauve ti ajadoh tan ahi. Hijeh chun Israel te chu alonkhumin mi phabep jong songkul’a akhum tai.\x + \xo 21:1 \xt Minbu 33:40\x*
\v 2 Chuin Israel miten Pakai angah akitem tauvin: “Nangman hiche mite hi keiho khutna neipeh doh ule keihon amaho khopi jouse aboncha ka suhmang diu ahi, atiuve.
\v 3 Pakaiyin Israel mite taona chu asanpeh tan Canaan mite chunga galjona anei tauvin, khopi jong abonchan ajousoh tauvin, chuleh hiche mun chu Hormah tin akihe jing tan ahi.
\s1 Gul Lim Kikhai Sang
\p 
\v 4 Israel te chu Hor Molsanga konna ahungpot uva Twipi San lam jonna akitol uvin Edom ahin vel uvin ahi. chun, hikom mun'a kon chun twisan lam ahin jon’un Edom gam ahin jotpa uvin. Hinlah mipi chu alamsao jotna uva chun athohhatmo deu deu tauvin, \x + \xo 21:4 \xt Danbu Ni Na 2:1\x*
\v 5 chule Pathen le Mose douna thu aseipan tauve. “Ipi dinga Egypt dalha a hiche gamthip a thi dinga hi neihin puidoh uhem?” tin akiphin uve. “Hilai mun hi don ding jong imacha umlou chule keiho hiche manna jong hi kachim tauve!” tin aseiyuve. \x + \xo 21:5 \xt 1 Crth 10:9\x*
\v 6 Hichun Pakaijin gunei tah gul ho alah uva asolin, chule mi tampi achun chule athi tauve.
\v 7 Chuin Israel mite chu Mose henga ahungun akap tauvin, “Keihon Pakai dounan thu kaseiyun ka chonse tauve. Pakaijin gul ho alahmang na dingin taovin” atiuve. Hijeh chun mipi dingin Mose atao tan ahi.
\v 8 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose aseipeh in, “Gullim sem inlang thingleh a bang doh in. Gul'in achuh jousen avet maimai ujongleh hing diu ahi!” ati.
\v 9 Hijeh chun Mose’n sum-eng in gullim asem'in thingleh a abangdoh tan ahi. Chuti chun koi hileh gul’in achuh khah chan chun aveuvin adam tauve. \x + \xo 21:9 \xt 2 Lengte 18:4; Jn 3:14\x*
\v 10 Chuin Israel mite Oboth jonin akitolun chule hiche a chun ngahmun akisem tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Abanin solam Moab gamgichin lam'a Iye-Abarim gamthip jonin akitol uve.
\v 12 Iye-Abarim apat in Zared luikhuh a akicholdo tauvin ahi.
\v 13 Hichun amaho akipat doh un Arnon Vadung, Amor mite chenna gamthip lam jonin achekit tauve. Arnon vadung chu Moab mite le Amor mite gamgi ahiye.
\v 14 Hiche jeh chun Pakai galbolna Lekhabun asei “Suphah gamkaiya Waheb khopi, chule Arnon Vadung thuh tah,
\v 15 chule vadung daamlhah letdan in ahop chu Moab gamgi langa Ar chenna chan ahi,” ati.
\v 16 Chu a kon chun Israel mite Beer jonin akitol'un, hiche twikhuh mun'a hi Pakaiyin Mose henga “Mipi koukhom’un, keiman adon diu twi kapeh diu ahi” atina mun chu ahi.
\v 17 Hiche mun'a chun Israel miten hiche la hi asauvin,
\b
\q1 “Hung put in, Vo twisam!
\q2 Heng'e, avahchoina sauvin!
\q1 
\v 18 Hiche twikhuh la sauvin,
\q2 lengnun alai chu,
\q1 lamkai pipu hon alaidoh uva
\q2 leng tenggol le moljol ho toh thoa.”
\b
\p Chuin Israel ten gamthip adalhauvin chule Mattanah lam amano uvin,
\v 19 Nahaliel, chule Bamoth ajonun ahi.
\v 20 Hiche jou chun Moab phaicham alhung tauvin hiche a kon a chu Pisgah Molting kigaldot ahitai.
\s1 Sihon Le Og Chunga Galjona
\p 
\v 21 Chuin Israel miten Amor mite lengpa Sihon henga palai asol'un hiche thu hi athot uve:
\v 22 “Keihon nagam leiset chu pal uvinge. Chingthei tah a ka lamlhah uva lengpilei lah a kache lou diu ahi. Na twikhuh uva jong twi kadon lou diu ahi. Nangho gamkai sunga hi lengpa lamlen bou kaho pa diu ahi bouve,” tin aseiyun ahi.
\v 23 Ahinlah Sihon Lengpa chun Israel mite chu agam ajotpa na diu chu aphal peh tapoi. Phalpih malah chun agalsat te chu akou khomin Israel te chu gamthip laitah achun abulu tan Jahaz kiti mun a chun akibulu to tauvin ahi.
\v 24 Ahinlah Isreal ten achemjam uvin asatchop un Arnon Vadung apat Jabbok Vadung chan alo tauve. Amon mite gamgi chan bou acheuve ajeh chu Amon mite gamgi chu kulbang a kigen ahi.
\v 25 Chuti chun Isreal miten Amon mite khopi jouse Heshbon le akimvel a kho jouse jaonan alonvuh un achenpha tauvin ahi.
\v 26 Heshbon khopi chu Lengpa Sihon le Amor mite dinga akhopiu ahi. Aman Moab mite lengpa anajo a Arnon Vadung geiya ana lah ahi..
\v 27 Chujeh chun, gollui laiya jaila sem hon ama chung changa jaila ana sun'un:
\b
\q1 Heshbon a hungin chule kisa thah hen!
\q2 Sihon khopi chu kiledoh kit hen.
\q1 
\v 28 Heshbon a kon'in meikong ahung kong doh in,
\q2 Sihon a kon'in mei ahung kadoh e.
\q1 Moab gam'a Ar khopi chu akihal lhatan;
\q2 Arnon vaihom te boltheina chu akisumang tai. \x + \xo 21:28 \xt Jeremiah 48:45,46\x*
\q1 
\v 29 Vo Moab mite, itobang lhaset nan nalhun khum'u hitam!
\q2 Akichai nahi tauve, Vo Chemosh hou ho!
\q1 Chemosh in achapa te galjam'in adalhan,
\q2 achanu te chu Amor leng Sihon in gal hingin songkul a ahen tai.
\q1 
\v 30 Eihon amaho chu isumang tauve
\q2 Heshbon apat Dibon geijin,
\q1 eihon amaho abonun ithehngim tauve
\q2 Nophah apat Medeba chanin.”
\b
\p 
\v 31 Hiti ahijeh chun Isreal miten Amor mite chenna gam alo tauvin ahi.
\v 32 Mose’n phat chomkhat jouvin Jazer gamkol kholchil dingin mi pasal phabep asolin, Isreal miten hiche vel'a khopi um jouse chu atoupha tauvin hikom'a cheng Amor mite chu abonchauvin anodoh tauve.
\s1 Og Lengpa Ajo’u
\p 
\v 33 Hichun Isreal mite akinunghei uvin Bashan akitol'un, amavang Bashan lengpa Og le anam mite jousen Edrei mun'ah ana bulhu uvin ahi.
\v 34 Pakajin Mose henga thu aseiyin, “Ama chu ging hihbeh in, ajeh chu keiman ama chu nangma khut a amite le agam ka pehdoh ding ahi. Heshbon vaipopa Amor mite lengpa Sihon nabolna bang tah in ama jong bolkit in.”
\v 35 Chule Isreal in Og lengpa ahin, achapa te ahin, akimatpi jouse ahi; koima ahing doh umlouvin athat sohkei tai. Chuti chun Isreal in gam leiset chu alo tan ahi.
\c 22
\s1 Balak In Balaam Kou Dia Mi Asol
\p 
\v 1 Hichun Israel mite Moab phaicham langa akitol un Jordan solam Jericho mun’a chun abusa tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Moab mite lengpa Zippor chapa Balak in Isreal miten Amor mite chunga anatoh jouseu amu sohkeije.
\v 3 Chule Moab miten Isreal mitampi ahung kitol'u amu phat uchun tijatnan adimset tauvin ahi.
\v 4 Moab lengpa chun Midian lamkai ho kom'ah aseijin, “Hiche mipi khun bongchal in hampa abahgam banga amu chan'u abahgam diu ahi!” ati. Hijeh chun Moab lengpa Balak in,
\v 5 Thupole ho jah a Beor chapa Balaam henga thu athot in, ama chu Ephrates Vadung koma Pethor gam'a cheng mi ahi. A thu thot chu: “Veuvin, hiche mipi ho hi Eygpt apat ahunglhung tauve. Amaho hin leiset pumpi alo dim tauvin chule amaho eigih uvin ahi. \x + \xo 22:5 \xt Minbu 31:8; 2 Pet 2:15,16; Jde 1:11\x*
\v 6 Lungset tah in hungin lang Isreal mite hi hung gaosap in ajeh chu keiya dingin ahatval un ahi. Hiche teng chule keiman amaho chu kajo a hiche gam'a konna hi kadel mang thei ahi. Na phatthei bohte aphatheiyun, chule na gaosap mite chunga hamsetna achuji e ti ken kahei.
\v 7 Balak thu thot pole Midian le Moab upaho chun sum le pai apo uvin Balaam chu peh a Israel te gaosap sah dingin akondoh athupoh uchu aga lhut tauvin ahi.
\v 8 Balaam in adonbut in “Tujan hikom'ah gehden tauvin,” ati. “Jingkah teng Pakaijin iti eilamhil kaseipeh diu ahi,” ati. Hijeh chun Moab upaho chu Balaam kom'ah aumden tauvin ahi.
\v 9 Hiche jan chun Balaam hengah Pathen ahungin, “Nahungvil uva hiche miho hi koiba hitam?” tin adong'e.
\v 10 Balaam in Pathen hengah, “Zippor kitipa chapa Moab lengpa Balak in hiche thu ho hi eihin thot e:
\v 11 'Vetan, Eygpt apatna hung kipat doh mihon hijat aum uvin chuleh ama hon vannoi pumpi alo dim tauve. Hiche mipi ho hi hung gaosap in, hung temin chuti leh keiman amaho chu ka nodoh jou thei khat leh tia eihung tep ahiuve,' ahiuve ati.
\v 12 Ahinlah Pathenin Balaam chu ahin houlimpi tan, “Amaho toh nakilhon louding ahi. Hiche mite hi Pathen phatthei chang ahi tauvin amaho na gaosap louding ahi!” ati.
\v 13 Ajing jingkah in Balaam in Balak mi hung lamkai ho kom'ah, “Nangho in lam a che tauvin! Pathenin nangho toh chekhom din ei phal poi,” atitai.
\v 14 Hichun Moab lamkai milun ho chu Balak lengpa kom'a din akinung le tauvin chule thu alhut un, “Balaam chu keiho toh hung lhon khom dingin anompoi,” atiuve.
\v 15 Balak in khatvei apatep kit e. Hiche chunga hin Balak in amasa a sangin migun tamjo asol'in ahi.
\v 16 Amaho chu Balaam heng'ah acheuvin hiche thu ho hi aga lhut tauve: “Hiche hi Zippor chapa Balak sei ahi: “Lungset tah in ka kom'a nahunga nei kithopina din imachan nasuboi hihhen.
\v 17 Keiman nangma hoitah a tohman ka bolpeh ding nahin chule ipi hita jongleh nangman bollin nati chan chu kabol peh ding ahi!” ati.
\v 18 Ahinlah Balaam in Balak thupole ho chu hitin adonbut in, Balak in aleng-in dim'a sana le dangka toh eipehtha ding hijongleh Pakai ka Pathen douna a thil boltheina ding ima thaneina kaneipoi.
\v 19 Hijongleh jan khat umbe nalaiyun, Pakaijin kahenga ipi seibe ding anei nahlai em ve ing'e,” ati.
\v 20 Hiche jan chun Balaam heng a Pakai ahungin, “Hhiche milun ho hi naheng’a dinga hung kholjin ahitah jeh un, nangma kipatdoh inlang amaho toh chekhom tan. Ahinlah nangman Ka sei bou nabol ding ahi, ati.
\s1 Balaam Leh A Sangan
\m 
\v 21 Chuti chun ajingin Balaam athoudoh in, asangan a atoudoh in Moab mite lamkai ho chutoh akipat doh tauvin ahi.
\v 22 Hinlah Balaam in alhonpiu jeh chun Pathen alunghang in, hijeh chun Pakai Vantil asol in lamlen laitah a Balaam alamtin tan ahi. Balaam chu asoh mini toh kilhon ahin,
\v 23 Balaam sangan chun Pakai Vantil lamlen na adin a chemjam akhut a achoi chu amudoh tan ahi. Hichun lamlen a kon'in phailei lam'ah achomlha tan, ahin Balaam in sangan chu ajep in lamlen'ah ahin puilut kit tan ahi.
\v 24 Chuti chun Pakai vantil chu lengpi lei teni kikah a leibang kichi lai achun ana ding tan ahi.
\v 25 Sangan chun Pathen vantil chu amu phat in, aki toldoh kigon Balaam keng le bang chu anombeh khatai. Hijeh chun Balaam in sangan chu ajep kit tan ahi.
\v 26 Chuphat in Pakai Vantil chu agamla jep a akichi chehna mun sangan lhaidoh thei louna ding mun achun ading kit tan ahi.
\v 27 Hiche ahin Sangan in Pakai Vantil chu amu phat in, Balaam noija akol tan ahi. Balaam chu alunghang lheh in sangan chu ajep kit tai.
\v 28 Hichun Pakaiyin sangan chu thusei theina apetai. Balaam chu ahin dongin, “Thumvei jen nei jepna dia ipi suhkhel kanei hitam?” ati.
\v 29 “Nangin kei angol banga neiso tah hila!” tin Balaam akisen e. “Chemjam chu kako hileh katha ding nahi tai!” ati.
\v 30 Sangan chun adonbut in, “Na damsung’a natou jingna sangan chu kahi, keima nidanga chu hitobanga hi kaum khah em? ati. Balaam in adonbut in “Naum khapoi,” ati.
\v 31 Chuin Pakaijin Balaam mit chu ahin hadoh sah tan, hichun Balaam in Pakai vantil lamka laiya adin’a chemjam akhutna akichoi chu amu tan ahi. Balaam akunlhan Pakai angah abohkhup tan ahi.
\v 32 Pakai Vantil chun, “Ipi bolla na sangan chu thumvei jen navoh hitam?” tin adong tan ahi. “Ven, Keima nalampi subing'a hunga kahi ajeh chu nangman louchal tah in nei deh tai.
\v 33 Sangan chun thumvei jen eimu ei peldohji; chutilou leh, Keiman Sangan hi kahing hoiya nangma hi katha doh ding nahitai.” ati.
\v 34 Hichun Balaam in Pakai vantil kom'a chun ngaidam athum tan, “Keima kachon khel tai. Keiman ka lampia neina tin chu ka hetdoh lou ahi. Ka chena hi na deilou ahin keima kile tang'e,” ati.
\v 35 Ahilah Pakaijin Balaam chu aseipeh in, “Hiche miho toh hin kilhonin, ahinlah Ken seijin kati bou nasei ding ahi.” ati . Hichun Balaam chu Balak milun ho chutoh achekhom tan ahi.
\v 36 Balak Lengpa in Balaam chu ahung ahet phat in, gamgi ningchong pen mun Arnon Vadung a Moab te khopi a chu kimupi din akondoh tai.
\v 37 Balak in Balaam thudoh aneitan “Keima henga gang tah a nahung na dinga kahin kou hilou ham? Ibol’a nahung jeng louham?” ati. “Keiman kipaman tamtah peh dia kasei chu na tahsan louham?” ati.
\v 38 Balaam in adonbut in, “Ven, keima ka hung tai, ahinlah keiman kanop nop seitheina tha kaneipoi. Pathen'in ka kam a akoi bou kasei doh ding ahi bouve,” ati.
\v 39 Hichun Balaam in Balak chu Kiriath-huzoth chan akilhon pin,
\v 40 hilai mun a chun lengpan kelngoi le bongchal atohdoh e. Aman hiche sa themkhat chu Balaam toh alhonpi ho chu apen ahi.
\v 41 A jing jingkah chun Balak in Balaam chu Bamoth-baal molchunga apuidoh in ahi. Hiche mun apat a hi lhang langa Israel mite hung kitol chu kimu ahi.
\c 23
\s1 Balaam In Israel Phatthei Aboh
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Balaam’in Balak lengpa kom'ah, “Pumgo thilto maicham mun-sagi hiche mun ahin nei sahpeh inlang, chuleh bongchal sagi le kelngoi chal sagi neigon tup peh tan,” ati.
\v 2 Balak in Balaam thupeh ho chu angaijin chuin bongchal le kelchal pumgo thilto chunga atohdoh cheh lhon tai.
\v 3 Hichun Balaam'in Balak kom'a aseijin, “Hikom'a pumgo maicham kihalna ahin ana um tadin, keima Pathen'in eiki houlimpi hinam ti kaga kholchil ding, chuteng hiche ho chu nangma ka seipeh ding nahi,” ati. Hichun Balaam chu molchung gei achangin akal tan,
\v 4 hilai achun Pathen'in Balaam akimupin a sei pehtai, “Keiman maicham sagi cheh kabolin, chuleh bongchal nou khat cheh le kelngoi chal khat cheh ka lhandoh tai,” ati.
\v 5 Hichun Pathen'in Balaam chu ahoupin Balak seipeh ding thu apen ahi. Chuti chun aman, “Nangma Balak henga hiche ka thusei hi seipeh tan,” ati.
\v 6 Chuti chun Balaam chu akile tan ahileh Balak lengpa chu Moab mi a milunho chutoh pumgo maicham mun'a ana din'u amun ahi.
\v 7 Hiche hi ahi Balaam aseipeh chu:
\b
\q1 Aram mun a kon'in Balaam in ei koudoh in;
\q2 Moab lengpan solam thinglhang apat in eihin puidoh e.
\q1 'Hungin'! 'Kei din Jacob hung gaosap in!
\q2 Hungin chule Israel te manthahna ding hung phong doh in.
\p 
\v 8 Ahinlah iti themmo kachan ding ham
\q2 Pakaiyin themmo achan lou ho chu?
\q1 
\v 9 Keiman molchunga pat amaho kamun,
\q2 Molvum apat in kaveuvin ahi.
\q1 Amaho achang uva ahin u kamun,
\q2 Namdang te akon lhenchom ahiu kamu doh e.
\q1 
\v 10 Koiham Jacob chilhah ho simjou ding, simseng lou neldi ja khu?
\q2 Israel mipi jat li chu kon asimjou ding ham?
\q2 Chonpha te bangin kei jong thi ingting;
\q2 Ka hinkho jong amaho bang chun kichai hen.”
\b
\p 
\v 11 Hichun Balak Lengpan Balaam heng’a aseijin, “Ipi neilo hitam? Ka melma te gaosap dinga kakou nahi. Chusangin, nangin phatthei naboh jotai!” ati.
\v 12 Ahinlah, Balaam chun adonbut in “Keiman vang Pakaijin ka kamsunga thucheng akoi ho bou ka seidoh ding ahi bouve” ati.
\s1 Balaam Thusei Nina
\p 
\v 13 Hichun Balak Lengpan aseijin, “Hungin mun chom'a che hite. Khulam'a khu Israel nam abon u hi hih jongleh namu ding ahi. Atam behseh uve amaho beh chu gaosap in!” ati.
\v 14 Chuin Balak in Balaam chu Zophim kiti lhaang kikhang laiya Pisgah molchunga apui touvin ahi. Hilai mun achun maicham phung sagi atungdoh in bongchal leh kelngoi khat cheh chu akatdoh tan ahi.
\v 15 Balaam in lengpa kom'a aseitan, “Keima Pakai toh kaga kimuto kah in nangma na pumgo thil tona mun ahin ana dingin,” ati.
\v 16 Chule Pakaiyin Balaam akimupin chule thu ahinpen ahi. Aman aseijin, “Balak henga kilen chule ka thusei chu gaseipeh in,” ati.
\v 17 Hijeh chun Balaam chu akinung le in Balak le Moab migun ja-um ho chu maicham mun'a ana din uchu amun ahi. “Pajaijin ipi aseiyem? tin Balak chun thanom tah in adong'e.
\v 18 Balaam in athupoh asei chu hiche hi ahi:
\b
\q1 “Thoudoh in, Balak, chule ngaijin!
\q2 Kasei ngaijin, Zippor chapa.
\q1 
\v 19 Pakai hi mihem ahipon, hijeh chun aman jou aseipoi.
\q2 Ama mihem ahipon, hijeh chun aman lung akhelpoi.
\q1 Aman aseidohsa chule aboldoh lou um kha em?
\q2 Aman kitepna aneiya abulhit lou um kha em?
\q1 
\v 20 Ngaijun, phatthei bohna thupeh kamui;
\q2 Pathenin phatthei aboh tan, chule keiman kalehei theipoi!
\q1 
\v 21 Aman Jacob manthahna ding tohgon imacha agong pon;
\q2 Israel din hamsetna akoipoi.
\q1 Ajeh chu Pakai a Pathen uvin amaho aumpin;
\q2 a leng diuva phondohsa ahitai.
\q1 
\v 22 Pathenin Egypt a konin ahin puidoh un;
\q2 amaho din ama chu bongchal hattah tobang ahi.
\q1 
\v 23 Gaosap nan Jacob sukha pontin;
\q2 Israel douna din doi thanei tah umponte.
\q1 Hijeh a chu Jacob dinga hitia kisei ding,
\q2 'Israel dinga Pathenin itobanga thil kidang abol hitam!'
\q1 
\v 24 Hiche mite chu sakei bangin athou doh un,
\q2 thahat tah sakei bangin achamin ading doh tai.
\q1 Choldo ding anompoi
\q2 anchah akimu masang sen,
\q2 a satha thisan adon masang sen!”
\b
\p 
\v 25 Hichun Balak lengpa chun Balaam henga asei tan, “Aphai, amaho hi na gaosap louding ahitah leh phatthei jong bohda jeng tan!” ati.
\v 26 Ahin Balaam in Balak chu adonbut in, “Pakaijin eiseipeh bou ka bolthei ahi tia kana sei hilou ham?” ati.
\s1 Balaam Thusei Thumna
\p 
\v 27 Chuin Balak lengpan Balaam jah a aseijin, “Hungin, mun chom khat a napuibe inge. Iham tia Pathenin pha asah leh hiche mun a chu amaho na gaosap sah thei ahi.”
\v 28 Hiti chun Balak in Balaam chu Peor molchung sangpen, gam ong tamtah ahung kisuh vetna mun'ah chun apuijin ahi.
\v 29 Balaam in Balak aseipeh in, “Maicham mun-sagi hiche mun ahin nei sahpeh inlang, chuleh bongchal sagi le kelngoi chal sagi neigon tup peh tan,” ati.
\v 30 Hichun Balak in Balaam sei bangin abol'in bongchal sagi le kelngoi chal sagi chu maicham chung cheh a atohdoh tai.
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 Balaam Israel mite phatthei aboh leh Pathen alunglhai chu ahet phat chun phat dang laiya bang’in doithu ho mangcha din akigong tapoi. Chusangin akiheijin gamthip lam agalvet len,
\v 2 hitia Balaam a dadoh a avetpet chun Israel mite ama phung cheh a angahmun u amun ahi. Chutah chun Pathen Lhagao chu achungah ahung chu tan,
\v 3 chule hiche hi aseidoh chu ahi:
\b
\q1 Beor chapa Balaam in asei doh thu chu,
\q2 kicheh tah a mit a mupa sei ahin,
\q1 
\v 4 Pathen thu kicheh tah a japa'n asei,
\q2 Hatchungnung a konna gaova mu a,
\q2 mit koulep a dilsu pa chu:
\q1 
\v 5 Vo Jacob, na ponbuh ho iti hoiya hitam!
\q2 O Israel, na in ho iti lungset um hitam!
\q1 
\v 6 Vadung panga honlei kibol'a,
\q2 ka masanga tum thing ho jaodeh bangin akimui.
\q1 Pakaiyin aphudoh thingphung sang ho toh abangin,
\q2 twipang’a keh Cedar phungho toh abang jeng’e.
\q1 
\v 7 Twibel akon atwiyu hung let lhan tin;
\q2 achilhah uvin angaichat jouseu anei diu ahi.
\q1 A lengpau jong Agag sang'in thupi jo intin;
\q2 alenggam’u jong choisanga um ding ahi.
\q1 
\v 8 Pathen in Eygpt a kon ahin puidoh un;
\q2 amaho din Ama chu gam bongchal hattah abang'e.
\q1 Amaho douvah nam jouse Aman avallhum sohtan,
\q2 agu achang jouseu asuhchip peh in,
\q2 athalpi hon akap e.
\q1 
\v 9 Sakei bahkai bangin Israel chu akitaulen alumji e;
\q2 Sakai banga kon ama aga thodoh ngam ding hitam?
\q1 Vo Israel, nangma phatthei naboh ho chu ahampha uvin,
\q2 chule nangma na gaosap ho chu gaosap chang ahiuve,” ati.\x + \xo 24:9 \xt Semtilbu 49:9; \xt Semtilbu 12:3\x*
\b
\p 
\v 10 Balak lengpa chu Balaam chunga hatah in alunghang tai. Aman lunghang tah in akhut teni abengin chule apengin , “Keiman kamelma te gaosap dinga kakou nahi! Chusangin, nangman thumvei phatthei naboh jotai.
\v 11 Tun hiche a kon hin potdoh tan! Na in'ah kile tan! Keiman kipaman tampi peh dia kitem kahin, hinlah Pakaijin na kipaman san ding chu akipel sah ahitai,” ati.
\v 12 Balaam in Balak jah ah, “Thupole nahin sol ho jah a kasei chu na geldoh lou hitam?
\v 13 Sana le dangka aleng insung dimset eikipe ding hijongleh, keiman Pakai thupeh kalval seina ding tha kaneipoi, Pakaijin eihetsah bou kasei ding ahi tia kaseisa ahi!.
\v 14 Tua keima ka mite koma kile ding kahi tai. Ahinlah khonunga Israel ten na mite ipi ahin bolpeh diu chu naseipeh masat inge,” ati.
\s1 Balaam Thusei Chaina
\p 
\v 15 Hiche thu hi Balaam in aseije:
\b
\q1 “Hiche hi Beor chapa Balaam thusei ahin,
\q2 amit tenia muchenset pa thusei chu,
\q1 
\v 16 a thu hi Pathen thu ho japa a kon,
\q2 Chungnungpen a kon hetna neipa,
\q2 mit koulep a dilsu pa chun:
\q1 
\v 17 Ama chu kamui, hinlah hilai hi ahipon chule tuhi ahipoi.
\q2 Ken kahei, ahivangin ahunglhung ding phat a ahi.
\q1 Jacob a konin valpa hung soh intin;
\q2 Israel apat leng tenggol hung peng ding ahi.
\q1 Hichun Moab mite luchang asuhchip ding,
\q2 Sheth mipi lugu avohkeh ding ahi.
\q1 
\v 18 Edom toupha a um ding,
\q2 chule Seir, adoupa chu, jo in um intin,
\q2 amavang Israel chu galjou in akitol e.
\q1 
\v 19 Jacob a vaipo hung pengdoh intin
\q2 ama chun Ir hinsah ho asuhmang ding ahi.”
\b
\m 
\v 20 Chuin Balaam in Amalek mipi lam chu aven hiche thu hi aseijin ahi:
\b
\q1 Amalek hi nam jouse lah a athupi penin,
\q2 ahinlah achaina chu manthahna ahi!”
\b
\m 
\v 21 Chuin aman Ken mite lam aven hiche thu hi aseijin ahi:
\b
\q1 Na in chu abit nai;
\q2 na buh chu songpi ho lah a kisa ahi.
\q1 
\v 22 \f * \fr 24:22 \ft Hebrew \fqa Asshur; \ft also in 24:24.\f* Hinlah Assyria in gal hingin nakai intin
\q2 Ken mite chu kisumang ding ahi.”
\b
\m 
\v 23 Balaam in athusei khumkhana in:
\b
\q1 “Kaden, Pathen lungtina louva
\q2 koi hingjou ding ham?
\q1 
\v 24 Cyprus twipang ah kong-innei ho hungun tin;
\q2 Assyria abolgim uva chule Eber chu asuh genthei diu,
\q2 ahin, ama ni chu, akhonna kheh a kisumang lhon ding ahi,” ati.
\b
\p 
\v 25 Chuin Balaam in adalhan a inlam'a akile tan, chuleh Balak jong alampia akile tan ahi.
\c 25
\s1 Moab in Israel apuimang
\p 
\v 1 Israel mite chu Acacia Grove mun’a abusah laiyun, pasal phabep Moab mite numeiho toh ajong tauvin ahi.
\v 2 Hiche Moab numei te chun a pathen kom uvaaum laitah uchunh akilhan nau kin a lha dingin atem uvin, Israel mite chun aneh khompi uvin Moab te pathen ahou tauve.
\v 3 Hiti pichun Israel miten Peor a Baal kiti ahou uchu ajop tauvin; Pathen lunghanna chu ahung deu jah jeng tai.
\v 4 Pathen'in Mose chu a houlimpin hiche mite lamkai ho hi koukhom un Pathen masang ah; sunkim laitah leh amaho hin khom in alamkai nau lahdoh pehtan, hiche jeh a chu Israel mite chunga Pathen lunghanna akichon mang theina dingin, ati.
\v 5 Hichun Mose’n Israel te thutan lamkai ho agahchah in, “Nanghon na thanei nau noiya um ho lah a koi hijongleh Peor mun a Baal hou tapou na thadoh diu ahi, ati.
\v 6 Hichun Israel mi khat in ama insung mite masanga Midian numei khat Mose masang laitah achun ahin puilut e; Hichu Israel mipite chu Houbuh masanga kap le maova aum laitah u ahiye.
\v 7 Chuin Phinehas kiti Eleazer chapa Aaron thempu pa tupa chun amu phat in, Israel mipi kikhopna chu adalhan, achom doh phut in, akhutna tengcha akichoijin ahi.
\v 8 Aponbuh sunggei ajuilut in, a tengpi hin choi chun pasal pa tahsa leh numeinu oipoh chu asun paijin akilbeh tha jeng tai. Hiche jeh chun Israel mite chunga gotna hise lang chu atang tan,
\v 9 ahinlah mi 24,000 athi jou uvin bou atang'e.
\v 10 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseiyin,
\v 11 Eleazer chapa Phinehas kiti Aaron thempu tupa ama tah hin Israel chate chunga ka lunghanna jouse eisuh mang peh a; ei kipasah ahitai. Ajeh chu amapa hi keima dinga thangtom tah leh gunchu tah in apang in, hiche ho jeh a chu Israel chate ka suhmang louding ahitai, tin a seije.
\v 12 Tun ama gaseipeh un; Israel te chungah cham le lungmon anei tah diuvin kitepna kabol e.
\v 13 Ka kitepna ahin keiman Ama ahin Ama chilhah ho chunga atonsot na thempu phunga ka semdoh ding ahi ajeh chu Phinehas chu a Pathen ding’a thangtom tah a pang ahitan Israel chate dinga kisuhthengna maicham semdohpa kiti ding ahitai.
\v 14 Midian numei toh thikhom Israel pasal pa chu Salu chapa Zimri akitin, Simeon phunga kon insung lamkaipa ahi.
\v 15 Numeinu chu Cozbi ahin; Midian mite phung lamkaipa Zur chanu ahi.
\v 16 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga aseiyin,
\v 17 Midian mite chu lonvuh inlang sumangun,
\v 18 ajeh chu Peor mun a Baal houna dia ama hon jou le lungthimbol a na suhgim u ahin, chule Peor thilsoh jeh a natse a thi Midian lamkai pa chanu Cozbi jeh ahi,” ati.
\c 26
\s1 Israel Sepai Jat Kisim Niveina
\p 
\v 1 Gamna hise kichai nung chun, Pakaiyin Mose le Aaron thempu pa chapa Eleazar jah a, \x + \xo 26:1 \xt Minbu 1:1-46\x*
\v 2 “Israel mite jouse lah a ama insung dungjuiyun gal-hang ho min jihdoh un. Pasal kum somni ahilouleh somni chunglam galkon thei jouse,” ati.
\v 3 Chuin Mose le Eleazer thempu pa’n Moab phaicham Jordan kom'ah Jericho gal langa aum laitah un, Israel lamkai ho hengah hiche thu ho apelhon'in ahi:
\v 4 “Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bangin Israel mite kum som nia pat chunglam min jihlutna neiyun,” Hiche hi Egypt a konna hung potdoh Israel chilhah jouse kijihlut chu ahi.
\s1 Reuben Phung
\p 
\v 5 Hiche hi Jacob chapa te lah a atahpen Reuben phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Hanoch mite phung min chu apuluiyu Hanoch a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Pallu mite phung min chu apuluiyu Pallu a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 6 Hezron mite phung min chu apuluiyu Hezron a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Carmi mite phung min chu apuluiyu Carmi a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Hiche ho hi Reuben phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 43,730 ahi
\v 8 Pallu chu Eliab hung kondohna ahin,
\v 9 chule Eliab chu Nemuel, Dathan le Abiram pa ahi. Hiche Dathan le Abiram hi Korah toh guthim'a kiloiya Pakai douna a Mose le Aaron ana dou u ahi.
\v 10 Ahinlah leiset in akam akah in amaho chu Korah toh avallhum tauvin, chule anungjui mi 250 meikong in abahgam tauvin ahi. Hiche thilsoh hi Israel nam pumpi dinga gihna thilsoh ahi.
\v 11 Hijeng jongleh chu che nikho chun Korah chapa te vang chu athi pouvin ahi.
\s1 Simeon Phung
\m 
\v 12 Hiche ho hi Simeon a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Jemuel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jemuel a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Jemuel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jemin a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Jakin mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jakin a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 13 Zohar mite phung min chu apulauiyu Zohar a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Hiche ho hi Simeon phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 22,200 ahi
\s1 Gad Phung
\m 
\v 15 Hiche ho hi Gad a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Zephon mite phung min chu apuluiyu Zephon a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Haggi mite phung min chu apuluiyu Haggi a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Shuni mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shuni a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 16 Ozni mite phung min chu apuluiyu Ozni a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Eri mite phung min chu apuluiyu Eri a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 17 Arodi mite phung min chu apuluiyu Arodi a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Areli mite phung min chu apuluiyu Areli a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Hiche ho hi Gad phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 40,500 ahi.
\s1 Judah Phung
\m 
\v 19 Judah chun chapa ni aneijin, Er le Onan ahin, Canaan gam'ah ana thi lhon tai.
\v 20 Hiche hohi Judah chapa teni a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Shelah mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shelah a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Perez mite phung min chu apuluiyu Perez a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Zerah mite phung min chu apuluiyu Zerah a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 21 Hiche ho hi Perez a konna kikhailha phung bahkai ho ahiuve:
\li1 Hezron mite phung min chu apuluiyu Hezron a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Hamul mite phung min chu apuluiyu Hamul a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 22 Hiche ho hi Judah phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 76,500 ahi.
\s1 Issachar Phung
\m 
\v 23 Hiche ho hi Issachar a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Tola mite phung min chu apuluiyu Tola a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Puah mite phung min chu apuluiyu Puah a konna kiminsah ahi.\f * \fr 26:23 \ft As in Samaritan Pentateuch, Greek and Syriac versions, and Latin Vulgate (see also 1 Chr 7:1); Hebrew reads \fqa The Punite clan, named after its ancestor Puvah.\f*
\li1 
\v 24 Jashub mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jashub a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Shimron mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shimron a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 25 Hiche ho hi Issachar phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 64,300 ahi.
\s1 Zebulun Phung
\p 
\v 26 Hiche ho hi Zebulun a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Sered mite phung min chu apuluiyu Sered a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Elon mite phung min chu apuluiyu Elon a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Jahleel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jahleel a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 27 Hiche ho hi Zebulun phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 60,500 ahi.
\s1 Manasseh Phung
\p 
\v 28 Joseph a konin Masasseh le Ephraim phung ahung kikhailhan ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Hiche ho hi Manasseh a konna kikhailha phung ho ahiuve:
\li1 Makir mite phung min chu apuluiyu Makir a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Gilead mite phung min chu apuluiyu Makir chapa Gilead a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 30 Hiche ho hi Gilead a konna kikhailha phung ho ahiuve:
\li1 Iezer mite phung min chu apuluiyu Iezer a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Helek mite phung min chu apuluiyu Helek a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 31 Asriel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Asriel a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Shechem mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shechem a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 32 Shemida mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shemida a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Hepher mite phung min chu apuluiyu Hepher a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 33 (Hepher chilhah Zelophehad chun chapa aneipon, ahin achanu te chu Mahlah, Noah, Hoglah, Milcah, le Tirzah ahiuve.)
\b
\m 
\v 34 Hiche ho hi Masasseh phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 52,700 ahi.
\s1 Ephraim Phung
\m 
\v 35 Hiche ho hi Ephraim a konna kikhailha phung ho ahiuve:
\li1 Shuthelah mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shuthelah a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Beker mite phung min chu apuluiyu Beker a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Tahan mite phung min chu apuluiyu Tahan a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 36 Hiche hi Shuthelah a konna phung bahkai ahi:
\li1 Eran mite phung min chu apuluiyu Eran a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 37 Hiche ho hi Ephraim phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 32,500 ahi.
\b
\m Manasseh le Ephraim a konna phung ho chu aboncha Joseph chilhah ahiuve.
\s1 Benjamin Phung
\m 
\v 38 Hiche ho hi Benjamin a konna kikhailha phung ho ahiuve:
\li1 Bela mite phung min chu apuluiyu Bela a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Ashbel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Ashbel a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Ahiram mite phung min chu apuluiyu Ahiram a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 39 Shupham mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shupham a konna kiminsah ahi.\f * \fr 26:39 \ft As in some Hebrew manuscripts, Samaritan Pentateuch, Greek and Syriac versions, and Latin Vulgate; most Hebrew manuscripts read \fqa Shephupham.\f*
\li1 Hupham mite phung min chu apuluiyu Hupham a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 40 Hiche ho hi Bela a konna phung bahkai ho ahiuve:
\li1 Ard mite phung min chu apuluiyu Ard a konna kiminsah ahi.\f * \fr 26:40 \ft As in Samaritan Pentateuch, some Greek manuscripts, and Latin Vulgate; Hebrew lacks \fqa named after their ancestor Ard.\f*
\li1 Naaman mite phung min chu apuluiyu Naaman a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 41 Hiche ho hi Benjamin phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 45,600 ahi.
\s1 Dan Phung
\m 
\v 42 Hiche ho hi Dan a konna phung bahkai ho ahiuve:
\li1 Shuham mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shuham a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 43 Hiche ho hi Dan a konna Shuham phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 64,400 ahi.
\s1 Asher Phung
\m 
\v 44 Hiche ho hi Asher chapa te a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Imnah mite phung min chu apuluiyu Imnah a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Ishvi mite phung min chu apuluiyu Ishvi a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Beriah mite phung min chu apuluiyu Beriah a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 45 Hiche ho hi Beriah a konna phung bahkai ho ahiuve:
\li1 Heber mite phung min chu apuluiyu Heber a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Malkiel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Malkiel a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 46 Asher in jong chanu Serah kiti khat aneije.
\b
\m 
\v 47 Hiche ho hi Asher a konna phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 53,400 ahi.
\s1 Naphtali Phung
\m 
\v 48 Hiche ho hi Naphtali chapa te a konna phung khailhah ho ahiuve:
\li1 Jahzeel mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jahzeel a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Guni mite phung min chu apuluiyu Guni a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 
\v 49 Jezer mite phung min chu apuluiyu Jezer a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Shillem mite phung min chu apuluiyu Shillem a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 50 Hiche ho hi Naphtali a konna phung ho chu ahiuve. Galsat thei kijihlut jat chu 45,400 ahi.
\s1 Galsat thei jouse kihihlut jat
\m 
\v 51 Lahgom'in, Israel galsat thei jouse chu abonin 601,730 ahiuve.
\v 52 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseiyin, \x + \xo 26:52 \xt Minbu 34:13; Joshua 14:1,2\x*
\v 53 Hiche gam leiset hi aphung, ami jat kilah dungjuiya atam alhom'u dungjuijin hoppeh tan.
\v 54 Mitam ho chu atam dungjuiya gam lenjep napeh ding, alhom ho chu alhom dungjuiya gam neojep napeh ding ahi.
\v 55 Ahinlah gam leiset ho chu vang asan diu, chule atam alhom dungjui uleh ama ama hung kondohna phung min dungjuiyaa nahop ding ahi.
\v 56 Hitia chu atam hon alenjep chuleh alhom hon aneojep dungjui uva vang akisan diu ahi.
\s1 Levi Phung
\m 
\v 57 Hiche hi aphung dungjui uva kisunlut Levi mite chu ahiuve:
\li1 Gershon mite phung min chu apuluiyu Gershon a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Kohath mite phung min chu apuluiyu Kohath a konna kiminsah ahi.
\li1 Merari mite phung min chu apuluiyu Merari a konna kiminsah ahi.
\b
\m 
\v 58 Libni mite, Hebron mite, Mahli mite, Mushi mite, chule Korah mite chu abon uva Levi phung bahkai ho ahiuve.
\p Tun Kohath chu Amram dia mibul ahin,
\v 59 chule Amram inneipu min chu Jochebed ahi. Amanu jong chu Levi chilhah ahin, Eygpt a Levi insunga peng ahi. Amram le Jochebed chu Aaron, Mose, chule asopinu Miriam dinga anu le apa ahi.
\v 60 Aaron in Nadab, Abihu, Eleazar chule Ithamar ahing uve. \x + \xo 26:60 \xt Minbu 3:2\x*
\v 61 Ahinlah Nadab le Abihu chun thupeh banga bol louva Pakai angsunga dihlou tah a mei ati lhon jeh in athi lhon tai. \x + \xo 26:61 \xt Thempu Dan 10:1,2; Minbu 3:4\x*
\v 62 Levi phung ho a konna pasal chapang lhakhat apat chunglam jouse chu mi 23,000 ahiuve. Ahinlah Isreal te mijat kisimna achun Levi te akisim tha pouve ajeh chu Israel te gam kihopna a chu amaho chan ding gam kipelou u ahi.
\v 63 Israel miho chu Moab phaicham a Jordan gallam a Jericho pang lah a Mose le Aaron Thempupa in mi jat asim lhonna ga chu hiche ho hi ahi.
\v 64 Sinai gamthip noiya Mose le Aaron thempu pan Israel te ana sim chun amaho jouse hi khatcha ana pang pouvin ahi.
\v 65 Ajeh chu Pakaijin aseijin, “Amaho jouse hi gamthip noiya thi diu ahitai.” Jephunneh chapa Caleb le Nun chapa Joseph tailou koima hing lou dingu ahi, ati.\x + \xo 26:65 \xt Minbu 14:26-35\x*
\c 27
\s1 Zelophehad Chanu Te
\p 
\v 1 Nikhat Zelophehad chanu te Mahlah, Noah, Hoglah Milcah chule Tirzah chun thumna aneiyun ahi. Apau Zelophehad, Gilead chapa Hepher chilhah ahin, Makir chapa, Manasseh chapa, Joseph chapa ahi.
\v 2 Hiche numei ho chu Mose, thempu Eleazar, japi lamkaiho chule mipi jouse angsunga Houbung kotbul achun adingun ahi.
\v 3 Ama hon, “Ka pau gamthip noiya thi ahi. Ama chu Pakai doupa Korah nungjui ahipoi; ama chu ama chonset jal a thi ahi. Ahinlah ama chapa neilou ahiye,” atiuve.
\v 4 Ipi jeh a kapau min chu chapa aneilou jeh maiya aphung sunga kon mang jeng ding ham? Ka sopi teu bangin chan neipe uvin, atiuve.
\v 5 Hijeh chun Mose’n amaho chungchang thu chu Pakai heng'a apolut tan ahi.
\v 6 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose hitin ahin donbut in,
\v 7 Zelophehad chanute thil thum hi ahi ding mong ahiye. Apa sopi te banga amaho hi gam napeh diu ahi. Apau peh ding nei le gou chu suhtup peh tan, ati. \x + \xo 27:7 \xt Minbu 36:2\x*
\v 8 “Chule Israel mite chu anoiya hilchahna ho hi seipeh tan: Mipa khat athi a chule chapa anei louva ahileh, agou ho chu achanu te chang ding ahi.
\v 9 Chule amapa chun anei louva ahile anei le agou hou chu asopi pasal ho henga na chon ding ahitai.
\v 10 Iham tia amapan sopi pasal ho anei louva ahile, agou ho chu apa sopi ho pen. .
\v 11 Ahinlah iham tia apan chun sopi pasal ho anei louva ahile, aphung sunga akinai pipen chu napeh ding ahi. Pakaijin Mose athupeh banga hiche hi Israel mite lamlhahna ding dol chu ahi.
\s1 Israel Te Lamkai Dia Joshua Kilhen
\p 
\v 12 Nikhat Pakaijin Mose kom'ah aseijin, “Vadung solam'a molchung khat pen ah kal touvin, chule keiman Israel te kapeh ding gamsung khu vetemin. \x + \xo 27:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 3:23-27; 32:48-52\x*
\v 13 Navet jouteng, na sopipa, Aaron banga nathi ding,
\v 14 ajeh chu Zin gamthip noiya ka thupeh ho banga nabol lhon lou jeh ahi. Israel mipi ho akiphin laitah un, twi mun a kathen dol amaho kom'a phongjal lhonin kati chu nabol lhon tapoi.” (Hiche hi Zin gamthip noiya Kadesh mun a Meribah twi chu ahi.)
\v 15 Chuin Mose’n Pakai henga hiti hin aseijin,
\v 16 “O Pakai, nangma thilsem jouse haina pe Pathen nahi. Lungset tah in japi lamkai ding mithah lhen peh tan.
\v 17 Pakai mite chu aching bei kelngoi tobang ahilouna diuvin achena chan uva avengtup diu le galmun a alamkai diu koiham khat pen.\x + \xo 27:17 \xt 1 Lgt 22:17; Ezekiel 34:5; Matt 9:36; Mk 6:34\x*
\v 18 Pakaiyin Mose adonbut in, “Nun chapa Joshua, ama Lhagao neipa, kou inlang achungah nakhut ngam in. \x + \xo 27:18 \xt Potdohbu 24:13\x*
\v 19 Eleazer thempu pa leh mipi jouse masangah dinsah inlang chuleh mipi jouse het in ama chu mipite puihoi din thupeh nei in.
\v 20 Chule Joshua chu nangman thaneina chu napeh ding hiche jeh a chu Israel mipi ten ajabol diu ahi.
\v 21 Pakaiya konna hetsahna angaichat teng Eleazer thempu pa masanga Joshua ding ding, aman Urim amanchah a, Pakai lunglam ahol ding ahi. Hitia hi Joshua le Israel miten abol diu jousea pan alah diu ahi. \x + \xo 27:21 \xt Potdohbu 28:30; 1 Samuel 14:41; 28:6\x*
\v 22 Hichun Mose’n jong Pakai thupeh dungjuijin aboltai. Mose’n Joshua chu Eleazer thempu pa masang leh Israel mipite masangah adinsah tan ahi.
\v 23 Pakaijin n Mose athupeh bang bangin akhut chu Joshua chunga angam in mipi lamkai dingin phatthei abohtan ahi. \x + \xo 27:23 \xt Danbu Ni Na 31:23\x*
\c 28
\s1 Niseh Thilto
\p 
\v 1 Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin,
\v 2 Israel mite hiche hilchahna hi pen: Thilto hoitah natodoh uchu keija dinga gimnamtui tah ahin; hiche ho chu ka an ahi. Hiche ho chu ka hilchah nau banga aphat cha nahinto diu ahi.
\v 3 “Mipi ho seipeh in: Hiche hi nang hon Pakai dinga govam thilto hoitah nisih le nabol diu ahi. Nang hon nolnabei kum khat lhingsa kelngoinou achal ni na todoh diu ahi.
\v 4 Kelngoi khatpen chu jingkah lama nato doh diu, khatma chu nilhah lam'a na todoh diu ahi.
\v 5 Kelngoi khat cheh chutoh lhosohga thilto a pang dia changbong neldisel khon dim khat le olive thao kihehlha khon dim khat toh kihal hi ding ahi.
\v 6 Hiche thilto hi bol jing ding pumgo thilto hoitah Sinai molchunga kibulphu, Pakaiya dia gimnamtui tah ahi.
\v 7 Kelngoi khat cheh chutoh lengpitwi thilto khamna theiya kidon khon dim khat Muntheng'a Pakaiya dia na suhlhah diu ahi.
\v 8 Kelngoi anina pa jong nilhah tengleh chutobangma a lhosoh leh lengpitwi toh nato ding ahi. Hiche, jong chu, thilpeh hoitah ahin, Pakai dinga gimnam tuitah ahi.
\s1 Sabbath Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 9 Cholngah nikho seh le kelngoi achal ni kumkhat lhingsa cheh nolnabei na todoh diu ahi. Hichu lhosohga thilto olive thao a kisunou changbong neldisel khon dim li, chule lengpitwi thilto hi ding ahi.
\v 10 Niseh a pumgo thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon a pumgo thilto hi Sabbath niseh a todoh ding chu ahi.
\s1 Lhaseh Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 11 Lhaseh a nikho masapen ni leh, Pakai dia thilto bongchalgol ni, kelchal khat, chule kum khat lhingsa kelngoi chal sagi, aboncha nolnabei na todoh diu ahi.
\v 12 Chule bongchal khat cheh toh to tha dinga lhosohga thilto ding olive thao a kisunou changbong neldisel khon dim gup, khon dim li leh kelchal,
\v 13 khon dim ni leh kelngoi khat cheh hi ding ahi. Hiche pumgo thilto hi thilpeh hoitah, Pakai dia lunglhaisah gimnam tui hi ding ahi.
\v 14 Nangman lengpitwi thilto jong na todoh ding: bongchal khat cheh chutoh lengpitwi khon ni, kelchal a dinga twipai thum, kelngoi khat cheh le khon dim khat cheh hi ding ahi. Hiche thilto hi kum lhunga lhaseh le nikho masapen nikho a pumgo thilto na todoh ding ahi.
\v 15 Chule lhaseh a nikho masapen ni leh, kelchal khat Pakai henga chonset thilto a na todoh ding ahi. Hiche hi boljing ding pumgo thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon a todoh ding chu ahi.
\s1 Kalchuh Kut Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 16 Chule lhamasa pen nisom leh nili lhin nikho leh Pakai Kalchuh Kut nabol ding ahi. \x + \xo 28:16 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-13; Danbu Ni Na 16:1,2\x*
\v 17 Hiche lha nisom le ninga lhinni hi thanop umtah, nisagi kimang ding kipatni ahin, ahinlah chol kisolou changlhah jeng naneh diu ahi. \x + \xo 28:17 \xt Potdohbu 12:14-20; 23:15; 34:18; Danbu Ni Na 16:3-8\x*
\v 18 Kut nikho masapen nile khoppi theng kibol ding, hiche nikho teng natoh nabol louhel diu ahi.
\v 19 Pumgo thilto hoitah Pakaiya na todoh nikhou hi ding ___ bongchal ni, kelngoi chal khat, chule kumkhat lhingsa cheh kengoichal sagi, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahi.
\v 20 Hichengse toh totha ding chu bongchal khat cheh le lhosohga thilto olive thao a kisunou changbong neldisel khon dim gup, kelngoi chal khat dinga khon dim li,
\v 21 chule Kelngoi chal sagi lah a khat cheh chutoh khon dim ni hi ding ahi.
\v 22 Nangma le nangma chonset kithoidamna thilto a pang dinga kelchal khat na todoh ding ahi.
\v 23 Jingkah seh le tantih nei louva thilto sim louva hichengse jong hi todoh ding ahi.
\v 24 Nisagi sunga jingkah seh leh anneh thilto hoitah na todoh uchun agimnam a Pakai alunglhai sah ding ahi. Hiche hi boljing ding pumgo thilto leh lengpitwi thilto chung chon a todoh ding chu ahi.
\v 25 Nisagi lhinni chu khoppi theng adia nikho loupi tah khat hi ding, hiche nikho a chu natoh dang nabol louhel diu ahi.
\s1 Lholhun Kut Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 26 . \x + \xo 28:26 \xt Potdohbu 23:16; 34:22; Danbu Ni Na 16:9-12\x* Lholhun Kut teng, Pakai dia na tohga masa na todoh teng, khoppi thenga dinga nikho poimo khat nagon ding, hiche nikho a chu natoh nabol lou diu ahi.
\v 27 Pakai dia lunglhai umtah gimnamtui dinga pumgo thilto hoitah na todoh diu ahi. Hiche lah a chu bongchalgol ni, kelchal khat, chule kelngoi chal kum khat lhing cheh sagi hi ding ahi.
\v 28 Hiche ho nungjuiya chu lhosoh thil ho lah a olive thao a kisunou changbong neldisel khon gup leh bonchalgol khat cheh, kelchal khat leh khon li cheh,
\v 29 chule kelngol sagi ho khat cheh chuleh khon ni cheh hi ding ahi.
\v 30 Chujongle, nangho le nangho Pakaiya na kisuhtheng na diuva kelchal khat na todoh diu ahi.
\v 31 Niseh a thilto ho chung chonin lhosoh thilto ho toh lengpitwi thilto pumin pumgo thilto hoitah ho kigonun. Gancha thilto nato hou chu nolnabei hitei ding ahi.
\c 29
\s1 Sumkon Kut Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 1 Kmseh a chavang kipattil nikho masapenni leh Sumkon Kut naman diu ahi. Khoppi theng adia nikho poimo tah hiding chule hiche nikho a chu natoh dang na bollou diu ahi.
\v 2 Nanghon Pakai dinga gimnamtui pumgo thilto nahinto cheh diu, hichu bongchal gol khat kelngoi chal khat, kumkhat lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal sagi jaona nolnabei hi ding ahi.
\v 3 Hicheng jouse toh totha ding chu olive thao a kisunou lhosoh changbong neldisel khon gup leh bongchalgol, khonli le kelchal,
\v 4 kelngoi chal sagi ho khat cheh chutoh khon ni cheh hiding ahi.
\v 5 Hiche chung chon'a chu chonset thilto Pakai anga nangho le nangho na kisuhthengna diuva kelchal khat na todoh diu ahi.
\v 6 Hiche thilto hoitah ho hi lhaseh le niseh a pumgo thilto ding ho chung chon'a to ding ho chu ahin, chule akiminphah lhosoh thilto leh lengpitwi thilto jong peh ding ahi. Hiche thilto ho hi Pakai dia thilpeh hoitah, alunglhaina gimnamtui hi ding ahi.
\s1 Lhatdohna Nikho Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 7 Nisom jou, chuche lha nisom lhinni teng, khoppi theng adang khat nakou ding ahi. Hiche nikho, Lhatdohna Nikho teng chuleh, mipi chu an nelouva che diu chule natoh dang atohlou diu ahi. \x + \xo 29:7 \xt Thempu Dan 16:29-34\x*
\v 8 Pakai lunglhai sahna gimnamtui dinga pumgo thilto na todoh diu ahi. Hiche dinga chu bongchalgol khat, kelchal khat, chule kumkhat lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal sagi, aboncha nolnabei hi diu ahi.
\v 9 Hiche thilto ho toh totha ding chu olive thao a kisunou lhosoh changbong neldisel khon gup leh bongchalgol, khonli le kelchal,
\v 10 kelngoi chal sagi ho khat cheh chutoh khon ni cheh hiding ahi.
\v 11 Chonset thilto adia kelchal khat jong na todoh ding ahi. Hiche hi lhatdohna dia chonset thilto le niseh pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto, chule lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\s1 Lhambuh Kut Thilto Ho
\p 
\v 12 Ni nga jou, chuche lha ni som le nga lhinni leh, nangman mijouse dia khoppi theng khat nakou ding, chule hiche nikho a chu na natoh lou diu ahi. Hichu Lhambuh Kut kipatna ahin, Pakaiya nisagi nanit diu ahi. \x + \xo 29:12 \xt Thempu Dan 23:34; Danbu Ni Na 16:13-15\x*
\v 13 Nikho masapenni leh, Pakai lunglhai sahna gimnamtui dinga pumgo thilto nabol diu ahi. Hiche thilto dinga bongchalgol som le thum, kelchal, chule kumkhat lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal som le li hi ding, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Hiche thilto ho toh totha ding chu bongchalgol som le thum ho khat cheh chutoh olive thao a kisunou lhosoh changbong neldisel khon gup, kelchal ni khat cheh chutoh khonli,
\v 15 kelngoi chal som le li khat cheh chutoh khon ni hi ding ahi.
\v 16 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 17 Nikho ni lhinni leh, bonchalgol som le ni, kelchal ni, chule kum khat lhingsa kelngoi chal som le li na todoh diu, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahi.
\v 18 Hiche thilto bongchal ho, kelchal teni, chule kelngoi chal hotoh totha ding chu lhosohga thilto le lengpitwi thilto toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 19 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 20 Nithum lhinni leh, bongchal som le khat, kelchal ni, kumkhat lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal som le li na todoh diu, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahiye.
\v 21 Hiche bongchal ho, kelchal teni, chule kelngoi chal ho chu lhosohga le lengpitwi toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 22 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 23 Nili lhinni leh, bongchalgol som, kelchal ni, kumkhat lhingsa cheh kelngoichal som le li na todoh diu, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahiye.
\v 24 Hiche bongchal ho, kelchal teni, chule kelngoi chal ho chu lhosohga le lengpitwi toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 25 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 26 Ninga lhinni leh, bongchalgol ko, kelchal ni, kum khat lhing sa cheh kelngoi chal som le li na todoh diu, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahiye.
\v 27 Hiche bongchal ho, kelchal teni, chule kelngoi chal ho chule lhosohga le lengpitwi toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 28 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 29 Nigup lhinni leh, bongchalgol get, kelchal ni, kum khat lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal som le li na todoh diu, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahiye.
\v 30 Hiche bongchal ho, kelchal teni, chule kelngoi chal ho chu lhosohga le lengpitwi toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 31 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Nisagi lhinni leh, bongchal sagi, kelchal ni, kum khat lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal som le li na todoh diu, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahiye.
\v 33 Hiche bongchal ho, kelchal teni, chule kelngoi chal ho chu lhosohga le lengpitwi toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 34 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi.
\p 
\v 35 “Niget lhinni chu, nikho theng dang khat din phongdoh in. Hiche nikho a chu na natoh lou diu ahi.
\v 36 Pakai lunglhai sahna gimnamtui dinga pumgo thilto nato diu ahi. Hiche thilto dinga bongchalgol khat, kelchal khat, chule kum sagi lhingsa cheh kelngoi chal sagi hi ding, aboncha nolnabei hi ding ahi.
\v 37 Hiche thilto jouse chutoh lhosohga le lengpitwi toh todoh tha ding ahi.
\v 38 Chonset thilto dia kelchal khat na todoh ding, hiche hi niseh a kibol pumgo thilto dia lhosoh thilto le lengpitwi thilto chung chon'a todoh ding chu ahi..
\v 39 Hiche thilto jouse hi kumlhah seh thilto a na todoh diu ahi. Hiche ho hi kitepna ahilouleh kipehna tah a to ding, pumgo thilto ho, lhosing thilto ho, lengpitwi thilto ho, ahilouleh chamna thilto ho dungjuiya to ding ahi,”
\v 40 Chuti chun Pakaiyin Mose henga athupeh bang bang chun Mose’n jong Israel chate jouse henga aseipeh sohkei tan ahi.
\c 30
\s1 Kitepna Thua Dan
\p 
\v 1 Mose’n Israel chate phung upaho akouvin aseipeh in, hiche hi Pakai thupeh ahiye:
\v 2 Na lah uva pasal khat touvin Pakaiya kitepna aneiya ahilouleh kihahselna noiya kitepna anei leh apalkeh thei louhel ding ahi. Aman aseidohsa bang bang’a chu abol ding ahi. \x + \xo 30:2 \xt Danbu Ni Na 23:21-23; Matt 5:33\x*
\v 3 Chule numei khat in apa insunga achen laiya Pakaiya kitepna anei khah a,
\v 4 chule apan akitepna chu ajah a phamo asah louleh akitepna bang bang'a um ding ahi.
\v 5 Ahinlah hiche numei nun kitepna anei chu apan ajah a alunglhai louleh, akitepna thulah louva um ding ahi. Apan abulhit dia pha asahlou jeh a Pakaiyin amanu chu angaidam ding ahi.
\v 6 Tun avetsahnan numei khangdong khat in kitilkhouna thei tah kitepna neijin akikan gah in chujou chun ajinei tan ahi.
\v 7 Khonung’a ajipan hiche kitepna chu ahin hetdoh a phamo asah louva ahile, amanu kitepna chu kisudet jing ding ahitai.
\v 8 Ahinlah amanun kitepna asemdohsa chu ajipa’n ajahdohni nia adeipeh louva ahile, Pakaiyin ahile hiche akitepna thudol'a chu amanu angaidam ding ahi.
\v 9 Iham tia meithai ahilouleh aji in ada ahileh, akitepna chu asuh bulhit ding ahi.
\v 10 Ahinlah tekah khat in numei chun ajineina insunga kitepna neijin kikan gehna anei tan ahi.
\v 11 Ajipan ajinu kitepna chu ahetdoh nung jenga jong phamo asah louva ahile, akitepna chu keh theilou ding ahi.
\v 12 Ahinlah ajipan adeisah peh louva ahile hiche akitepna thudol'a chu Pakaijin amanu angaidam ding ahi.
\v 13 Hijeh a chu ajipan aphatsah peh thei adeimo peh thei dungjuiya amanu aum thei ngai ahi.
\v 14 Ahinlah ajipan ahin jahdohni a phamo asah louva ahile amanu kitepna jouse chu anoppeh ahitai.
\v 15 Ama pan amanu kitepna ho manmo sopehna dinga nikhat val anga nalaiya ahile, amanu themmona theiya chu amapa joh gotna chang ding ahi.
\v 16 Hiche dan ho hi Pakaijin Mose apeh pasal le ajinu kah, chule mipa le achanu toh insunga achenkhom laiya chon dan apeh ho chu ahi.
\c 31
\s1 Midian Te Chung’a Galjona
\p 
\v 1 Chuti chun Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin,
\v 2 “Israel mite jouse thalhengin Midian mite chunga phulahna neijin ajeh chu alim semthu u houvin apuilut tauve. Chujou teng, nangma nathi ding chule napu napa te lah a najao ding ahitai,” ati.
\p 
\v 3 Chuin Mose’n mipi ho henga aseijin, mi phabep lhengdoh un, chule Midian mite chunga phulahna Pakai galsat dingin galvonin vonun.
\v 4 Israel phung ho a konin mi 1000 cheh galmun'a asol uvin, ati.
\v 5 Chuti chun Israel phung sung’a kon mi 1000 cheh alhengdoh tauvin, abonchan mi 12,000 galmun'a din gontup ahitai.
\v 6 Chuti chun Mose'n aphungkhai a mi 1000 cheh chu asoldoh tan, chule Eleazar thempu pa chapa Phinehas in galmun'a alamkai uve. Amahon muntheng a thilkeo ho akichoiyun chule mutging dingin sumkon ho jong akiken'un ahi.
\v 7 Pakaiyin Mose athupeh bang chun amahon Midian mite chu alonvuh uvin, pasal jouse athat tauvin ahi.
\v 8 Midian mite leng nga ho — Evi, Rekem, Zur, Hur, chule Reba—galmun achun athi tauve. Amahon Beor chapa Balaam jong chemjam in athat un ahi.
\p 
\v 9 Hiti chun Israel miten Midian numei le chapang ho chu ahin pui tauvin, a gancha hou ahin, athilkeo jouse’u abonchan ahin chom gamhel tauve.
\v 10 Midian mite chenna khopiho le kho jouse abonchan ahalvam tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Gal a achom jouseu, mihem hihen gancha hijongleh asuhkhom nungun,
\v 12 abonchan Mose le Eleazer thempupa, Israel chate khopi pumpi, Moab phaicham, Jordan vadung pang, Jericho a ngahmun asemna uva chun abonchauvin ahin kai sohkei tauvin ahi.
\v 13 Mose leh Eleazer thempupa chule khopi sunga lamkai jouse chu polama ache tauvin, amaho chutoh aga kimuto tauve.
\v 14 Ahin Mose chu galmun a konna hung kile aja ja chunga thunei lamkai ho chunga chun alunghang tan ahi.
\v 15 “Ipi dinga numei jouse na hinghoi uham?” tin angeh in ahi.
\v 16 Hiche numei ho jeh leh Balaam thuhil jeh a Peor chung chang thu’a Israel chate jouse Pakai adia thet umtah a ana chon ahiuvin, hiche jeh chun Pakai mite chunga gamna hoise ana lansah ahi. \x + \xo 31:16 \xt Minbu 25:1-9\x*
\v 17 Hijeh chun tun pasal chapang jouse le numei hija pasal toh ana kitimat sa jouse jong that jeng tauvin.
\v 18 Numei chapang pasal toh kitimat khaloulai chengse chu nangho dingin hing hoiyun.
\v 19 Chule nangho jouse lah a gal a mithat ahin, mithi tongkha chan chu, ngahmun polam a nisagi sung naum diu ahi. Nangho jouse na hiuvin, gal hinga nahin kai jouseu nithum lhinni le nisagi lhinnia na kisuhtheng sohkei diu ahi.
\v 20 Na ponsil u, kelvun a kisem ahin, savun a kisem, chule thing them a konna kisem manchah jouse aboncha na suhtheng sohkei diu ahi.
\v 21 Eleazer thempu pan galsat akon ho henga aseijin, “Pakaiyin Mose a thupeh sa danthu a kisem chondan chu apen:
\v 22 Sana, dangka, sum eng, chule hahngeh jaona a kisem jouse—
\v 23 thih hiya meijin akahvam theilou chengse chu meiya naleo diu chuteng athenga nasim bep diu ahiye. Chule twiya nasop kit diu ahi.
\v 24 Nisagi lhinni tengleh na ponsil jouseu nasop uva na kisuhtheng diu ahi. Chujou lebou ngahmun a nakile bep diu ahi,” ati.
\s1 Gal A Kichom Thil ho Kihop Khen
\p 
\v 25 Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin a seipeh in,
\v 26 “Nang leh Eleazer thempu chule phung jousea insung lamkai hon gal hinga nahin puiyu mihem ho leh gancha ho jouse abonchan simtoh tem’un.
\v 27 Chuteng galsatna a konna kichomdoh thil ho chu hopni naso diu, akehkhat chu galsat miho napeh dingu chule akehkhat chu mipi napeh diu ahi.
\v 28 Galsat miho chan a kon chun, amasan thil kichom ho chu Pakai dingin mihem ahin, bongchal ahin, sangan ahin, kelngoi ahin 500 lah a khat cheh napeh dingu ahi.
\v 29 Galsat sepai ho chan lah a akehkhat chu Pakaiya kilhaina dinga Eleazar thempu napeh diu ahi.
\v 30 Israel chate jouse chan ding lah a konna somnga lah a khat chu mihem ahin, sangan ahin, kelcha ahin, kelngoi ahin, chule gancha dang hijongleh na lahdoh ding ahi. Hichengse chu Pakai Houbuh kinbolna mun’a natong Levi mite nahop diu ahiye.
\v 31 Chuti chun Pakai thupeh bang chun Mose leh Eleazer thempu pan jong abol lhon tan ahi.
\p 
\v 32 Gal mun'a kon galsat mihon ahin chomdoh u gal thil jouse chu agomin, kelcha le kelngoi 675,000,
\v 33 bong 72,000,
\v 34 Sangan 61,000
\v 35 chule nungah theng 32,000 ahi.
\p 
\v 36 Gal a kichomdoh akehkhat chu galkon sepai achangun ahi. Agom'in kelcha le kelngoi 337,500 ahin,
\v 37 hiche ho lah a 675 chu Pakaiya din apeuvin,
\v 38 bong 36,000 lah a 72 chu Pakaiya din apeuvin;
\v 39 sangan 30,500 lah a 61 chu Pakaiya din apeuvin,
\v 40 chule nungah theng 16,000 lah a 32 chu Pakaiya din apeuvin ahi.
\v 41 Pakaiyin athupeh bang chun, Mose chun Pakai dinga athilto chu Eleazer thempupa henga abonchan apedoh tan ahi.
\p 
\v 42 Gal a kichom galsat miho chan le Israel chate chan akon akeh khat cheh chu Mose’n achom'a akoidoh in ahi.
\v 43 Agom gom'in kelcha le kelngoi 337,500,
\v 44 bong 36,000,
\v 45 sangan 30,500
\v 46 chu nungah theng 16,000 ahi.
\v 47 Chan akehkhat Israel chate chan akon chun mihem ahin ganchalah akon hileh somnga lah a khat cheh alheng doh in, hichengse chu Pakai Houbuh a lhacha a pang Levi mite ho chu apen ahi. Hiche ho jouse hi Pakaijin athupeh banga Mosen abol ahi.
\p 
\v 48 Chuti chun asang sang chunga vaihom thuneiya pang, aja ja chunga vaihomma pang ho chu Mose henga ahungun,
\v 49 chule aseiyun, “Na lhacha a pang, keihon, ka thuneina noi uva um galsat miho abonchan ka sim toh sohkei un, mihem khat jeng cha jong kalah uva alhasam le amang thai aumpoi!.
\v 50 Pakai ding’a thilto chu keihon mihem ama ama kipehdohna cheh in, sana kol a kisem chaokol ahin, chao jang, mohor numna khut jem, bilba ho, khi vui ho, hichengse a kon'in Pakai angsunga keiho kithoidamna dingin kahin choi tauve. Hiche hin kahinkhou Pakai anga asuhtheng a chule midih a eisem diu ahi,” atiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 51 Chuin Mose leh Eleazer thempu pan galsat lamkai hon ahin choi thil le lo jouse chu asang lhon tan ahi.
\v 52 Agomin, galsat lamkai hon Pakaiya atodoh u chu pound 420 ahi.
\v 53 Galkon sepai jouse gal thil kichom themkhat chu ama ama chan dingin akilah sohkeiyun ahi.
\v 54 Chuin Mose leh Eleazer chun asang le aja chunga galsat lamkai ho a kon chun sana tampi chu asang lhonin Israel mite hi Pakaiya kon ahi bouve ti geldoh a aum jing na diuvin Houbuh sung lam achun ahin choilut lhon tan ahi.
\c 32
\s1 Jordan Solam’a Phung Ho
\p 
\v 1 Reuben leh Gad chilhah ten bong hon tampi anavul un ahi. Chuin Jazer gam leh Gilead gam amudoh tauvin ahile, hiche mun chu bong honte vahna ding’a kilem tah asohdoh tan,
\v 2 Mose leh Eleazer thempupa leh khoppi lamkai ho jouse hengah ahungun ahi. Amahon aseiyun,
\v 3 Ataroth, Dibon, Jazer, Nimrah, Hershbon, Elealeh, Sibmah, Nebo chule Beon khopi ho hi
\v 4 Pakaiyin Israel te dia ana lah ahin, chule hiche gamsung chu ka gancha teu vahna dingin apha lheh e.
\v 5 Namitmu a lunglhaina ka chan uva ahile, Jordan gal lam'a gam neipeh sangun hiche gamsung hi nalhacha keiho chanvou in neisem peh tauvin,” atiuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 6 Mose’n jong Gad leh Reuben chate henga aseijin, “Jordan gal a na sopi teu galsat khoh laitah a hi nanghon um den ding na lhen joh diu ham?
\v 7 Pakaijin apeh hiche gamsung galkaiya galsat nasopiu Israel mite chu ipi dinga nasuh thaset got uham?
\v 8 Kadesh Barnea apat gam velhi dinga kasol uchun napu napa teuvin tunia nabol'u bang hi ana bol'un ahi. \x + \xo 32:8 \xt Minbu 13:17-33\x*
\v 9 Eshcol phaicham alhun uva Pakaiyin Israel chate apehna gamsung alut diu chun Israel mipi ho chu ana lungthoi sah uvin ahi.
\v 10 Chuti chun achung uva nasatah in Pakai alunghang in chule akihahsel in, \x + \xo 32:10 \xt Minbu 14:26-35\x*
\v 11 'Egypt gamsung’a konna hung potdoh kum somni a lhah chunglam sen Abraham, Isaac leh Jacob henga ka kitepnasa gamsung chu amu louhel diu ahi, ajeh chu ama hon alungthim pumpiuvin eijabol pouvin ahi.
\v 12 Amaho tailouva Ken mi Jephunneh chapa Caleb leh Nun chapa Joshua bouvin alungthim pumpin Pakai ajui lhonin ahi.'
\p 
\v 13 Israel chung’a Pakai alunghang jeng tan ahile, chuin Israel mite hiche khang mite ho chu Pakai mitmua thilse bol jouse athigam kahsen kum som li sung in gamthip noiya avale sah tan ahi.
\v 14 Nangho jong napu napate hou a konna chonsetna chun nahin jui peh tauvin! Hijeh chun Israel mite chunga Pakai lunghanna chu asangjo cheh a lunghan sah ding nagel uve.
\v 15 Chule Pakai nung najuina uva konna na kiheimang hel uva ahile, aman hiche mite ho hi gamthip noiya don louva ahin koi ding, chuteng hiche mite ho chunga hi manthahna alhunsah teitei ding ahitai! ati.
\v 16 Chuin Gad leh Reuben chate Mose angsung’a asei uvin, “Hiche mun'a hin kelngoinou tampi kanei uvin, hijeh chun kelngoi kul ka sempeh uva, chule kacha kanao te hou dinga jong kulpi nei khopi phabep kasah peh diu ahi.
\v 17 Khat cheh in manchah kapat uva, Israel mite gal lamkaiya kapan diu, amaho jouse chenna ding mun kamu kahse uva kigosa dem'a um jing ka hiuvin, ahinlah agamsunga cheng teho jal a hi numei chapang ho kulpi kaikhum'a venbit ding katiu ahi.
\v 18 Chule Israel chaten khat cheh a chen mun anei kahseuva keiho inlam'a hung kile louding kahi tauve.
\v 19 Ajeh chu amaho toh Jordan vadung gal lam'a khu gou kalo khom theilou diu ahi. Solam gamkai Jordan lam hi keiho goulo dinga hung kisep doh ahitai,” atiuve.
\p 
\v 20 Chuin Mose’n jong aseijin, “Pakaiya galsat dinga hitia hi na khutchoi utoh na dindet uva,
\v 21 Pakaijin na galmi teu adelmang masangsea na galsat houvin Jordan galkaiya gal asat jing uleh,
\v 22 Pakaijin gam chu ajo tengleh nahung kile diu ahi. Pakai le Israel mipi jouse chunga nakin'u na suh bulhit diu ahi. Chule Jordan solam'a gam chu Pakaiya konna natou u hi ding ahi.
\v 23 Hitobang’a hi nabol lou uva ahile, nangho jouse jong Pakai doumah a chon nahi diu, hiche na chonset nau hin nahin holdoh tei diu ahi.
\v 24 Na numei chapang ho dingin chen mun phabep sahpeh unlang, na kelngoi teu kul jong sem peh uvin, amavang na kitepnau aboncha nabol sohkei diu ahi,” ati.
\p 
\v 25 Chuin Gad leh Reuben miten adonbut un, “Keiho, nasoh ten, nei thupeh bang bang uva kajui diu ahi.
\v 26 Ka chateu, jiteu, gancha hon ho hiche Gilead khopi ahin anaum tauvinte.
\v 27 Ahinlah galkon thei jousen nasei banga agal manchah toh Pakaiya galsat dinga galkai ding kahiuve,” atiuve.
\p 
\v 28 Chuin Mose’n Eleazer thempupa, Nun chapa Joshua, chule Israel phung khailhah lamkai ho henga thu apetan ahi. \x + \xo 32:28 \xt Joshua 1:12-15\x*
\v 29 Mose’n aseijin, Gad chate le Reuben chate galmanchah choi jousen Pakaiya galsat dinga Jordan vadung galkai diu ahi. Chutia chu abol uva agam chu alah uleh Gilead gam chu amaho gou dingin petan.
\v 30 Ahinlah amaho hin gal manchah choi nom louva nangho toh agalkai uleh, amaho hin Canaan gamsung’a nangho jouse toh chengkhom diu ahi,” ati.
\p 
\v 31 Chuin Gad chate leh Reuben chaten aseikit un, “Keiho nasoh te kahiuvin, chule Pakai thupeh bang banga keihon kabol diu ahi!
\v 32 Keiho galmanchah thalhingset toh Pakaiya gal kasat diu, ahin kagou diu chu Jordan a hilangkai hi ding ahi,” atiuve.
\p 
\v 33 Chuin Mose’n jong Gad phung, Reuben phung, chule Joseph le Manasseh phung akehkhat chu gam apetan ahi. Aman Amor mite lengpa Sihon lenggam leh Bashan lengpa Og lenggam—akhopi ho le akimvel a gam ho chu apeuvin ahi.
\p 
\v 34 Gad chaten khopi atundoh hou chu Dibon, Ataroth, Aroer,
\v 35 Atroth-shophan, Jazer, Jogbehah,
\v 36 Beth-nimrah, chule Beth-haran ahi. Hiche khopi jouse chu kul akai khum sohkeiyun, kelngoite umna ding mun jong tampi asem doh peh tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 37 Reuben chaten khopi atundoh hou chu Heshbon, Elealeh, Kiriathaim,
\v 38 Nebo, Baal-meon, chule Sibmah ahi. Amahon alah u khopi phabep min akhel'un athahsah uve.
\p 
\v 39 Chuin Manasseh chapa Machir chate acheuvin Gilead agasat uvin ahile ahin jou tauve, agamsunga ana cheng Amor mite chu abonchauvin adel jam gamhel tauvin ahi.
\v 40 Mose’n jong Gilead chu Manasseh chapa Machir henga apedoh tan, chule hicheva chun acheng tauvin ahi.
\v 41 Jair mite, Manasseh sunga phungbah khat chun Gilead khopi ho abulu jou uvin hiche lhaang chu Jair Khopi ho asah tauvin ahi.
\v 42 Hiti chun, Nobah kitipan Kenath khopi le akimvel kho ho abulu in, athah in hiche ho chu minsahna aneijin Nobah asah tan ahi.
\c 33
\s1 Israel te Egypt Akon Ahung Kitol Dan Nungvet Kitna
\p 
\v 1 Hiche hi Egypt a konna Israel te Mose leh Aaron lamkaina a ahung kitol nau lampi ahi.
\v 2 Pakai thupeh bangin Mose’n bannei chan ana jihlut in ahi. Hiche ho hi amun kikhel dungjuiya akitol nau, akingahna hou chu ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Khal kipattil'in Rameses khopi a konin ahung kitoldoh un—lhamasa pen, nisom le ninga lhinni jingkah Kalchuh Kut masapen kichai ahi. Israel mite chu Egypt mite jouse mitmu tah a hung kitoldoh ahiuve.
\v 4 Hiti chun, Egypt miten achapau peng masa jouseu avuiyun, Pakaiyin janlhah a athau ahi. Pakaijin Egypt pathen ho chunga thutanna lentah aneijin ajou tai!
\b
\li1 
\v 5 Rameses ahin dalhah jouvun, Israel te Succoth a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 6 Chuin Succoth adlhauvin gamthip chin'a Etham a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 7 Etham mun'a kon'in Baal-zephon gal a Pi-hahiroth lam mano'n akileheiyun, chule Migdol a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 8 Pi-hahiroth adalha uvin chule gamthip gal'a Twipi San agalkaiyun ahi. Chuti chun Etham gamthip noiya nithum sung ahung kitol'un Marah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 9 Marah a konin Elim a abusa uvin, hiche mun'a chun twinah som-le-ni toh tom phung somsagi aum'in ahi.
\li1 
\v 10 Elim adalha uvin Twipi San panga abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 11 Twipi San pang adalha uvin Sin gamthip noiya abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 12 Sin gamthip noi adalha uvin Dophkah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 13 Dophkah adalha uvin Alush a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 14 Alush adalha uvin Rephedim a abusa uvin, hiche lai mun achun mipi don ding twi aumpon ahi.
\li1 
\v 15 Rephidim adalha uvin Sinai gamthip noiya abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 16 Sinai gamthip adalha uvin Kibroth-hattaavah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 17 Kibroth-hattaavah adalha uvin Hazeroth a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 18 Hazeroth adalha uvin Rithmah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 19 Rithmah adalha uvin Rimmon-perez a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 20 Rimmon-perez adalha uvin Libnah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 21 Libnah adalha uvin Rissah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 22 Rissah adalha uvin Kehelathah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 23 Kehelathah adalha uvin Shepher Mol a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 24 Shepher Mol adalha uvin Haradah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 25 Haradah adalha uvin Makheloth a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 26 Makheloth adalha uvin Tahath a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 27 Tahath adalha uvin Terah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 28 Terah adalha uvin Mithcah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 29 Mithcah adalha uvin Hashmonah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 30 Hashmonah adalha uvin Moseroth a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 31 Moseroth adalha uvin Bene-jaakan a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 32 Bene-jaakan adalha uvin Hor-haggidgad a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 33 Hor-haggidgad adalha uvin Jotbathah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 34 Jotbathah adalha uvin Abronah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 35 Abronah adalha uvin Ezion-geber a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 36 Ezion-geber adalha uvin Zin gamthip noiya Kadesh a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 37 Kadesh adalha uvin Edom gamgichin a Hor Molsang a abusa uvin ahi.
\v 38 Hor Molsang aum laiyun, Pakai thupeh bangin Aaron thempu chu molchunga akal touvin, chu achun ama athi tan ahi. Hiche hi nipi laitah ahin, Israel ten Egypt adalhah jou uva lha nga lhinna nikho masapen ni ahi.\x + \xo 33:38 \xt Minbu 20:22-28; Danbu Ni Na 10:6; 32:50\x*
\v 39 Hor Molchung’a Aaron athi chun kum 123 alhing tan ahi.
\li1 
\v 40 Hiche laitah chun Canaan gam a Negev a cheng Canaan mite lengpa Arad chun Israel miten agam ahinnai u thu ajadoh tan ahi. \x + \xo 33:40 \xt Minbu 21:1\x*
\li1 
\v 41 Chuti chun, Israel ten Hor Molsang adalha uvin Zalmonah a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 42 Chuin Zalmonah adalha uvin Punon a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 43 Punon adalha uvin Oboth a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 44 Oboth adalha uvin Moab gamgi a Iye-abarim a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 45 Iye-abarim adalha uvin Dibon-gad a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 46 Dibon-gad adalha uvin Almon-diblathaim a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 47 Almon-diblathaim adalha uvin Nebo Mol kom'a vadung solam mol a abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 48 Vadung solam mol adalha uvin Jericho gal, Moab phaicham a Jordan Vadung panga abusa uvin ahi.
\li1 
\v 49 Jordan vadung pang adalha uvin Moab phaicham a Beth-jeshimoth apat Acacia thinglei chanin abusa uvin ahi.
\b
\p 
\v 50 Moab phaicham a Jericho toh kigalsai Jordan vadung pang a abusah laiyun, Pakiajin Mose henga thu aseijin,
\v 51 Israel chate heng’a hiche thupeh ho hi pen: Canaan gam'a Jordan Vadung na galkai teng uleh,
\v 52 chu a cheng miho chu aboncha na nodoh diu ahi. Songa a ki-atdoh lim hihen thih kisongtuiya kisem lim hileh chule a milim hou nau in ho aboncha na suhmang diu ahi.
\v 53 Agamsung khu nalo uva na chen diu ahi, ajeh chu hiche gamsung hi nalo diuva ka pehdoh sau ahitai.
\v 54 Ama phung cheh in chenna ding’a gam hi anei thei ding vangsan na jong na nei diu, phung sung’a mitamte agam jeng jong na keh let peh diu, mi lhom deu phung sung chu agamlo jeng jong neojo hi ding ahi. Thulhuh chaina chu vangsan chu hi ding ahi. Hitia chu, na pului u phung dungjuiya agam chu nakihop diu ahi. \x + \xo 33:54 \xt Minbu 26:54-56\x*
\v 55 Amavang agam sunga cheng te khu na delmang lou uva ahile, namit uva bohhal aningsih hem toh nadiuva ling tobang hi diu ahi. Na chenna gam uva nasugim uva hung pang diu ahi.
\v 56 Chule achung uva bol ding ka tohgon chu nangho chunga kabol ding ahi,” ati.
\c 34
\s1 Gamgi Ho
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Pakaiyin Mose heng’a thu aseiyin,
\v 2 “Hiche hilchahna ho hi Israel te pen: Keiman nagoulo diuva kapeh nau Canaan gam chu nalhun tengu leh, agamgi ho chu hiche ho hi hi ding ahi.
\v 3 Lhanglam a gamgi ding chu Edom lhaang chin'a Zin gamthip a hung kilhung pan ding ahi. Lhanglam gamgi chu Twipi Thi solam hi ding ahi.
\v 4 Chu a pat lhanglam Aipi Paltan a kilhungsuh Zin langkai hi ding ahi. Alhanglha pen mun chu Kadesh-barnea hi ding, chu apat a kilhung a Hazar-addar, chule Azmon chan'a kilhung ding ahi.
\v 5 Azmon apat gamgi chu Egypt vadung langa kihei ding chule akingahna chu Mediterranean Twipi hi ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 6 “Lhumlam na gamgi diu chu Mediterranean Twipi pang chin hi ding ahi.”
\v 7 “Sahlam gamgi ding chu Mediterranean Twipi kipan ding chule Hor Molsang solam chan kilhung ding,
\v 8 chu a konna Lebo-Hamath, chule Zedad
\v 9 le Ziphron apat Hazar-enan chan kilhung ding ahi. Hiche hi sahlam na gamgi diu chu ahi.”
\p 
\v 10 “Solam gamgi chu Hazar-enan a kipan ding chule Shepham langa kilhungsuh ding,
\v 11 hitia chu Ain solam gamkaiya um Riblah chan geija kilhung lut ding ahi. Chu a konna agamgi chu solam Galilee Dillen pang geiya gamgi kilhung ding,
\v 12 Chuban leh gamgi chu Jordan vadung apat kilhungsuh peh ding Twithi Dillen chan geiya kilhung lha ding ahi. Hiche ho hi na gamgi diu chu ahi.”
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 34:13 \xt Joshua 14:1-5\x*Chuin Mose’n Israel chate henga hiti hin aseijin, “Hiche gam hi nangho le nangho kah a vang nasan uva nakihop diu nagam uchu ahi. Pakaiyin thupeh chu phungko leh phung kehkhat ho kihom diu ahi. \x + \xo 34:13 \xt Minbu 26:52-56\x*
\v 14 Reuben phung, Gad phung, chule Manasseh phung kehkhat hon gam kiphalpeh chu anei sohkeiyun
\v 15 Jordan Vadung solam lang, Jericho gal apat nisona lam chu ahi.”
\s1 Gam homtoh ding lamkai ho
\p 
\v 16 Pakaiyin Mose henga hiti hin aseiyin,
\v 17 Thempu Eleazar leh Nun chapa Joshua chu mipi ho dia gam homtoh ding teni ahi lhon'e.
\v 18 Aphung cheh a lamkai khat cheh le atoh ding semtoh lhonin.
\v 19 Hiche ho hi phung ho le lamkai ho min ahi:
\b
\tr 
\th1 Phungmin
\th2 Lamkai
\tr 
\tc1 Judah
\tc2 Jephunneh chapa Caleb
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 20 Simeon
\tc2 Ammihud chapa Shemuel
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 21 Benjamin
\tc2 Kislon chapa Elidad
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 22 Dan
\tc2 Jogli chapa Bukki
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 23 Manasseh son of Joseph
\tc2 Ephod chapa Hanniel
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 24 Ephraim son of Joseph
\tc2 Shiphtan chapa Kemuel
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 25 Zebulun
\tc2 Parnach chapa Elizaphan
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 26 Issachar
\tc2 Azzan chapa Paltiel
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 27 Asher
\tc2 Shelomi chapa Ahihud
\tr 
\tc1 
\v 28 Naphtali
\tc2 Ammihud chapa Pedahel
\b
\m 
\v 29 Amaho hi Canaan gamsung a Israel chaten alo diu gam homtoh ding’a Pakaiyin angense ho chu ahiuve,” ati.
\c 35
\s1 Levi Te Khopi Ho
\p 
\v 1 Israel te Moab phaicham Jordan vadung pang Jericho mun a abusah laiyun Pakaiyin Mose henga thu aseijin, \x + \xo 35:1 \xt Joshua 21:1-42\x*
\v 2 “Isreal chaten agou uva konna akhopiu phabep leh akimvel'a hamhing kena gam ho Levi te apeh diuvin thu pen.
\v 3 Khopi ho a chu Levi te cheng diu, hamhing kena gambeh chengse chu bong ho, kelcha ho chule agancha dang hou vahna a anei diu ahi.
\v 4 Levi mite gancha ho vahna dinga napeh diu gambeh chu khopi pal apat feet 1,500 kimvel hi ding ahi.
\v 5 Khopi baang apat solam, lhanglam, lhumlam, sahlam a feet 3,000 cheh na tedoh diu alaiya chu khopi um ding ahi. Hiche gamkol chu khopi mite dinga hamhing gam hi ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 6 “Khopi gup Levi te napeh diu hichu kiselna khopi hi ding, hiche khopi ho chu mi khat in adang khattou suhkhel jeh a atha khah leh akihuhhingna dia ajamlutna khopi hi ding ahi. Achung chon'a, khopi dang somli le ni jong napeh diu ahi.
\v 7 Aboncha, khopi somli le get toh akimvel a hamhing gam ho Levi te napeh diu ahi.
\v 8 Khopi ho hi Israel chate gamsunga konna hung ding ahi. Phung lenjep hon Levi te dinga khopi ho apeh tamjep diu, phung neojep hon apeh lhom jep diu ahi. Phung jousen ama ama gam neo le let dungjuiya gou apeh diu ahi.”
\s1 Bitna Khopi Ho
\p 
\v 9 Pakaiyin Mose henga aseijin, \x + \xo 35:9 \xt Danbu Ni Na 19:2-4; Joshua 20:1-9\x*
\v 10 “Israel chate jah a anoiya hilchahna ho hi pen.
\p “Jordan na galkai uva Canaan gam nalut teng uleh,
\v 11 suhkhel jeh a akitha khah uleh ajamlut uva akihuhhingna diuvin bitna khopi ho lhengdoh un.
\v 12 Khopi chengse hi nangho ding’a phulapa akon kiselna leh kihuhhingna mun'a pang ding ahi. Ajeh chu koi hileh mithat penpen chu athu kicheh tah a akikhol doh masangse a kithat louhel ding ahi.
\v 13 Na kihinsona diuvin bitna khopi gup lhengdoh un,
\v 14 thum chu solam Jordan Vadung a chule thum chu lhumlam a Canaan gam hi ding ahi.
\v 15 Hiche khopi ho chu Israel te, nalah uva cheng gamdang mi, chule sumkolvei kholjin miho dinga hoidohna ding ahi. Na lah uva koi hileh mi that a khutsoi aum khah leh abitna dinga jamlut ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 16 “Ahinlah koi ham khat in thih a mi avoh a atha khah a ahileh, hichu toltha ahin, chule mithat pa chu athepmona jeh a tha ding ahi.
\v 17 Ahilouleh koi ham khat in akhut a song achoiya midang khat atalih khah a ahileh, hichu toltha ahin, chule mithat pa chu tha ding ahi.
\v 18 Ahilouleh koi ham khat in thingtum mangcha a midang khat asuhlih khah a ahileh, hichu toltha ahin, chule mithat pa chu tha ding ahi.
\v 19 Athipa kinaipi pen pa chu mithat pa thana dinga amopo hi ding ahi. Akimuto teng uleh, aphu la ding pa chun mithat pa chu atha ding ahi.
\v 20 Mi khat touvin mihem khat chu achan lhih a, asotlhuh ham thil khat a ase a chule ama chu athi leh, hichu toltha ahi.
\v 21 Ahilouleh koi ham in mi khat chu avetda a chule akhuttum'a asuh a chule ama pa chu athi khah leh, hichu toltha ahi. Chutobang thu ho a chu, phula pa chun mithat pa chu amu muna a atha ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 22 “Ahinlah avetsahnan koi ham khat in kitomona masa jong umlouva mi khat chu asot a, ahilouleh ipi ham khat a tupten hilouva asekhah a ahileh,
\v 23 ahilouleh songtum a midang khat ase khah a, amani chula kidou hilou, chule akisepkha pa chu athi tai.
\v 24 Hitobang chu aso khah leh, mithat pa leh aphula ding pa kikah, athi pa kinaipi pen pa chunga thutanna chu mipin asem uva ajui diu:
\v 25 Mipi chun mithat pa chu phula ding pa a konna aven diu chule mithat pa chu ajamlutna ding khopi a ahin pui diu ahi. Hiche mun a chu thao theng kinu pa, thempulen thi kahsea mithat pa chu um ding ahi. “
\p 
\v 26 Ahinlah hiche mithat pa chu bitna khopi akon chun ana chedoh taleh,
\v 27 chule phula ding pa chun mithatpa chu khopi pam a ana that jeng taleh, phula pa chu tolthat a kisim louding ahi.
\v 28 Mithat pa chuthempulen thi kah a bitna khopi a chu um jing ding ahi. Ahinlah thempulen thi jou tengleh, mithat pa chu ama gou umna a kile ding ahitai.
\v 29 Hiche hi hoiya cheng jong leu chun akhang khanga chonna dan a na nei jing diu ahiye.”
\p 
\v 30 Mithat jouse chu tha a um ding, hinlah hichu ahetoh mikhat sanga atamjoh le bou hi thei ahi. Mikhat bou hettohna a koima kithat louding ahi.\x + \xo 35:30 \xt Danbu Ni Na 17:6; 19:15\x*
\v 31 Chujongle, mikhat tha theina dia achunga dihloutah a thutan bolna dia aman nakilah louhel ding ahi; tolthat a chu itih hijongleh tha ding ahi.
\v 32 Akihuhhingna dinga khopia jamlut tolthatpa jal'a longman jeng jong thempulen thi masanga nakilah louhel diu ahiye.
\v 33 Hitia hi na gamsung’u na suhboh thei loudiu, ajeh chu toltha jeh a gamsung bohji ahi. Tolthat chu tha ding tilou gamsung suhthengna dingin thilto bol ding aumpoi.
\v 34 Hijeh chun nachen nau gamsung suboh hih un, hiche gam achun keima ka cheng'e. Keima Pakai kahin, Israel mipi ho lah a ka cheng'e,” ati.
\c 36
\s1 Goulo Ding Chanu
\p 
\v 1 Chuin Gilead phung ho a lamkai ho—Makir chihlhah ho, Manasseh chapa, Joseph chapa—chule Israel insung lamkai ho chu Mose henga thumna nei dingin ahung uve.
\v 2 Amahon aseiyun, “Pu, Israel mipi ho vang sanna a gam na hoppeh dingin Pakaijin na hilchah in ahi. Ka sopipau Zelophehad in agam achanu te apeh dinga na phatsah peh dingin Pakaijin na seipeh e. \x + \xo 36:2 \xt Minbu 27:7\x*
\v 3 Ahinlah amahon phung dang mi akichenpi uleh, akiphal peh gam chu ajinei nau phunga che tha ding ahitai. Hitia hi, keiho goulo ding gamsung hi neojep jep ding ahitai.
\v 4 Chutileh Jubilee ahung lhun tengleh, agambeh chu phung thah a chutoh kigom ding ahitan, kapu kapa teu gam chu a itih a mang den ding ahitai.”
\p 
\v 5 Hijeh chun Mose’n Pakaiya kon hiche thupeh hi Israel te apeuvin: “Joseph phung mite thusei hi ahi ding dol ahi.
\v 6 Hiche hi Zelophehad chanu te chung chang a Pakai thupeh ahiye: Pu le pate phunggui sunga ahi pouleh, adei deiyu toh kicheng tauhen.
\v 7 Koima a konna gam hi phungkhat a konna phung dang changson thei louding, ajeh chu ama ama phung kipe cheh gam chu akipeh dungjuiya um den cheh ding ahi.
\v 8 Hijeh a chu Israel chanu te a konna apa goulo chanvou chang hon apa phung sunga konna mi akichenpi ding, hitia chu Israel chate hon apu apa te khang uva pat agoulo chengseu chu amahon achenpi jing diu ahi.
\v 9 Goulo gam hi phungkhat a konna phung dang a kichon thei louhel ding, ajeh chu Israel chaten ama ama chenna gam cheh chu kitup tah a akivet kol cheh ding ahi.”
\p 
\v 10 Zelophehad chanu ten Pakai thupeh bang bangin abol uvin ahi.
\v 11 Mahlah, Tirzah, Hoglah, Milcah, chule Noah abonchauvin apa sopi pasal hotoh akicheng tauve.
\v 12 Amaho chu Joseph chapa Manasseh phunga ajinei uvin ahi. Chuti chun, agoulo gam’u abonchan apau phung sungah aum jing tan ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Hiche thupeh ho hi Moab phaicham, Jordan vadung pang Jericho a Pakaijin Israel chate chonna dinga Mose ana peh ho chu ahi. 
